Nu gorna lee Ches nrep leen yoo ler nu lee xkaw kwaan nlu kwenta tub mdun ndok nzo roo yoo ler paro nzhedizh Xaa Tubka Nak kwaan Ches.
Nu gorna ne re xaa yezh lee xkaw kwaan nlu kwenta mdun ndok nzoli roo yoo ler, zee nkichxub xaa roo yoo ler cheen xaa, axta nla lachuzh xaa lo yo, nu nzholl xaa lo Xaa Tubka Nak.
Zee lee Xaa Tubka Nak ngunii lo Ches snee sneepa modxa nzhedizh xaa kwaan wechxinn xaa, zeera mbare xaa pa nzhi re xaa per lee tub xaa mad le Josué, xgaan Nun, xaa nle yud xaa, nu tira nanroot leen yoo ler.
