Tub xoop yaaya nkanoya choya: chona tub ta nu chona stub ta.
Nu tub lad yaaya nkanoya chon kop kwaan nak mod yeey cheen almendro kwaan dub xana, nu sbaaka stub yaaya nkanoya xchon kop kwaan nak mod yeey cheen almendro kwaan dub xana, nu sbaa lee bruj nkano xoop yaa.
