Lach jwer roo li Xaa Tubka NakNu sbaaka msaaw xaa roo lach jwer li Xaa Tubka Nak. Lee naz ta yat mkee xaa tub lee ler kwaan non doo kwaan noll tub gayoo zhit yaa xaa.
