Nu lee naz ta ya, mkee xaa ler non doo, kwaan noll tub gayoo zhit yaa xaa, nu noka mdexkwaa xaa tub gal yiso nu tub gal kwaan mzo xana kwaan nak brons; nu lee yiib kwaan nkenga ngench lo nu ngench nak plat.
Nu noka ta nyaaz mbizh mkee xaa tub lee ler non doo kwaan noll choobchii zhit yaa xaa; nu chii yiso, nu chii kwaan mzo niiya; nu lee yiib kwaan nkenga ngench lo nu ngench ngok plat.
