Nu kwaan mzo nii yiso mdexkwaa xaa kwaan brons, nu lee yiib kwaan nkenga ngench lo nu ngench ngok plat; nu yek re yiso ngok plat. Nu rese yiso kwaan mzo roo lach jwer yoo mkano ngench kwaan nak plat.
