Tub tap yiso cheena nu stub tap kwaan mzo niiya ngok brons, nu lee yek yiso, nu yiib kwaan nkenga ngench lo, nu ngench ngok plat.
Nu rese stak kwaan mzen ler cheen li Xaa Tubka Nak nu kwaan myaaw roo lach jwer li xaa ngok brons.
