Nu rese kwaan nzhaw xaa kwaan mchuun nis kwaan nzho leen yas cho, noka leeya gak beed, nu rese nis kwaan nzho leena noka gak beed.
Nu rese ma ngut kwaan la cho tub kwaan gak beed; chol naka gor o garde, nkin luux xaaya nel naka tub kwaan beed lo gu. Nu sbaa nzhaal le guya.
Nebse xlen o pa ngozhaw gu nal nis, nebse kwaan baa lake nzhul. Per lee xaa kwaan gal cho ma ngut gak beed xaa.
Nu chelee tub re ma ngut la cho bizh kwaan xeen xaa lo yo seetaka gaka kwaan nzhul;
per cheleeya bizh ngulola ngok bsiiya nu la ma ngut choya, ngulola ngok beeda.
Nu cheleeya tub ma kwaan nzho mod gaw gu yet, xaa kwaan gal cho ma noka lee xaa gak beed axta la yalnakaw;
nu xaa kwaan gaw baal cheen ma ngut, nzhaal zet xaa xab xaa per gak beed xaa axta la yalnakaw; nu seeka xaa kwaan koo ma ngut, noka lee xaa zet xab per noka xaa gak beed axta la yalnakaw.
Nu nagawt gu nik tub re ma kwaan nze lextoo lo yo; nel nak ma ma beed.
Nik tub re ma kwaan nze lextoo lo yo, nagawt gu chol naka ma kwaan ngobxex lextoo lo yo o ma kwaan nkano tap nii o ma nkano zyen nii, nel nak ma ma beed lo gu.
Nu gak beed gu gu kwaan re ma ne, ma beed kwaan nze lextoo lo yo,
nel na nak Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa nak Xtios gu. Gok nambey gu, nel nambey nak na. Nu nalebeedt gu gu kwaan tub re ma kwaan nze lextoo lo yo.
Na nak Xaa Tubka Nak xaa kwaan mloo gu yizhyo Egipto zee gak na Xtios gu. Gok gu xaa nambey, nel na nak xaa nambey.
Kwaane nak ley cheen re ma, re myin, nu rese ma mban nu re kwaan nzho leen nis nu rese ma kwaan nze lextoo lo yo,
zee gakbeyy kwaan nzhul nu kwaan beed lo re ma kwaan nzho mod gaw xaa nu re ma kwaan nyent mod gaw xaa.
Xomod gak nambey ngwnaa me nzan madNgunii Xaa Tubka Nak lo Ches nu nzhé xaa:
“Guzh lo re xaa Israel kwaane: Gorna lee tub ngwnaa weey xinn nu zan me tub madbyi, dubse tub gazh mbizh zo beed me, modxa nzo beed me leezha nded ren lextoo me.
Nu lee mbizh gazh ko xaa mad beey cheen re xaa Israel.
Per lee me seetaka kwaz me, axta yilo yixoob galbchiibchon mbizh zee gak nambey me lo ren. Nu nixa nyent mod zen me nik tub kwaan nambey nu nixa nyent mod ya me roo li na, pa nambey, axta yilo gak nambey me.
Per chelee me zan tub madnaa, gak beed me chop sman, modxa leezha nded ren lextoo me, nu zo beed me stub chongal nzho xoop mbizh zee gak nambey me lo ren.
Gorna yilo zhin mbizh kwaan gak nambey me, nexa chol xaabyiya o madnaaya, zee wee me tub mbakxiil yeen, ma nzho tub liin zee yek ma lo mdo, nu wee me tub palom o tub ngog lo ngwleyy mod gon kwaan zaa me zee gak nambey me, lo Xaa Tubka Nak.
Zee lee ngwleyy teed ma lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, Nu zee gak nzhul me lo ren.” Kwaane nak ley cheen ngwnaa me nzan mad nexa chol xaabyiya xa me o chol madnaaya.
Chelee me nankanot me kwaan zii me tub mbakxiil yeen, zee nzho mod zaa me chop ngog o chop palom, tub ma gak gon kwaan zeek xaa lo mdo, lee stub ma zaa me zee gak nzhul me; zee lee ngwleyy teed ma kwent cheen me zee gak nzhul me.
Ley cheen yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaaNgunii Xaa Tubka Nak lo Ches nu lo Aarón, nu nzhé xaa:
“Gorna lee tub xaa nzeki cho o nzhiib tub yeezh cho xaa o zhiib kwaan rus cho xaa, nkin wee xaa xaa lo ngwleyy Aarón o lo tub lo re xgann xaa.
Lee ngwleyy wii nel cho yeezha, chelee yich kwaan nzeeb lo yeezh nguna rus nu nzha reepa leen baal, telise naka yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa. Nu gorna ne ngwleyy nel cho yeezh nzeb cho xaa, gorzee yé xaa xaa beed xaa.
Chelee yeezh kwaan nzho lo baal na rus, nu nanzhareepta leen baal, nu nixa yich nanzhanat rus, zee lee ngwleyy sebyoo xaa tub gazh mbizh.
Gorna yilo yixoob gazh mbizh zee wii xaa stuba zee nel xomod nzhaka nu cheleeya seetaka nluya, zeera sebyoo xaa xaa stub gazh mbizh.
Yilo yixoob gazh mbizh stuba zee wii xaa nel xomod nzhaka, cheleeya nzhayetloya nu nanzhaxonnta lo baal, zee lee ngwleyy yé nzhul ngok xaa ne, sbaasa nak tub yeezh kwaan mzhib lo baal. Zee lee xaa ngok ne, zet xaa xab xaa zee gak nzhul xaa.
Per chelee kwaan mzhiib lo baal seetaka nzhaxonn gorna ngulo mwii ngwleyy loya, nu nzhéla xaa lee xaa ngok nzhul, kwaanzee nkin ya xaa lo ngwleyy stub welt zee wii xaa lo yeezh stuba.
Gorna lee tub xaa nkano yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa, nkin wee xaa xaa lo ngwleyy.
Zee wii ngwleyy lo xaa, chelee kwaan nzeki lo baal na rus, nu mleya zee nguna rus yich nu cheleeya nyun baal mban kwaan nzeki,
zee naka yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa kwaan nayakwentra. Zee lee ngwleyy yé: ‘Beed xaa’. Nu nankintra sebyoo xaa xaa, nu ngok beed xaa.
Nu chelee yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa liger doo mxen dubse nii xaa nu axta yek xaa, axta paro le ngwleyy gan yun a lo xaa,
zee lee ngwleyy wii lo xaa; zee nel che dub cho xaa ngulo mzhaal yeezh, zee lee ngwleyy yé: ‘Nzhul xaa’. Nel lee yeezh kwaan nyal cho xaa nguna rus nu lee xaa ne ngok nzhul.
Per mbizh kwaan yun kwaane cho baal cheen xaa kwaan mban gak beed xaa.
Zee lee ngwleyy wii nel che yun baal cho xaa nu yé xaa: ‘Beed xaa’. Nel nyun baal leen yeezh. Nel yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa nkano xaa beed xaa’.
Per chelee baal cheen xaa kwaan mban nyun na rus, zee ya lo ngwleyy,
zee wii xaa cho xaa, chelee ngwleyy ngune leeya na rus, zee yé xaa: ‘Ngok nzhul xaa’.
Gorna lee tub xaa mkano tub yeezh, nu gakwen xaa
nu cho xaa pa mlen yeezh mlake kwaan nzeki nu rus naya, o naxne naya, nkin ya xaa lo ngwleyy.
Chelee ngwleyy wii lo kwaan nzho len yezh cho xaa, nu lee yich nguna rus, zee yé xaa: ‘Beed xaa’. Nel kwaan nkano xaa nak yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa.
Per cheleeya pa mlen yeezh nangunat yich rus nu nixa nanzhota axta leen baal, sinka nzheyak wena, zee sebyoo xaa xaa tub gazh mbizh.
Cheleeya seetaka nzhaxonna leen baal, zee lee ngwleyy yé: ‘Beed xaa’. Nel nkano xaa yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa.
Per chelee yeezh rus mlake nebse paro mlena, nu nebse mlake bde cheen yeezh, zee lee ngwleyy yé: Nzhul nak xaa’.
Cheleeya nzho tub xaa zhoog cho nu zhiib yeezh rus loya o naxne,
zee lee ngwleyy wii lo xaa. Chelee yich kwaan nzeeb loya na rus nu lee kwaan nawent na nzho axta leen baal, kwaanzee pa mzhoog mle yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa; zee lee ngwleyy yé: ‘Beed xaa’. Nel yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa nkano xaa.
Cheleeya gorna yilo wii ngwleyy loya nu nyent yich rus loya, nu nixa nanzhota leen baal nu nzhaluxa, zee lee ngwleyy sebyoo xaa tub gazh mbizh.
Yilo yixoob gazh mbizh zee lee ngwleyy wii loya, chelee kwaan nawent nzhaxonn leen baal, zee yé xaa: ‘Beed xaa’. Nel nkano xaa yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa.
Per chelee kwaan nawent seetaka nzho loya nu nanzhaxonnta leen baal, nu nzhaluxa, zee naka nebse bde cheen kwaan mzhoog. Zee lee ngwleyy yé: ‘Ngok nzhul xaa’. Nel nebse bde mke pa mzhoog.
Gorna lee tub xaabyi o tub ngwnaa nkano yeezh yek o xanchii,
zee lee ngwleyy wii lo yeezh. Cheleeya tira nzhoya leen baal nu nzeb yich nayech loya nu cheepse yich, zee lee ngwleyy yé: ‘Beed xaa’. Nel nkano xaa yeezh kwaan nzoxbab kwaan nyall yek xaa o xanchii xaa.
Per chelee ngwleyy wii lee yeezh kwaan nzob yek xaa kwaan nzoxbab nanzhota leen baal nixa nanzebt yich nagaas loya, zee sebyoo xaa xaa gazh mbizh.
Gorna yilo yixoob gazh mbizh, lee ngwleyy wii lo yeezh cheen xaa stuba, cheleeya nanzhaxonnta, nixa nyent yich nayech loya, nixa nanzhareepta leen baal,
zee lee ngwleyy nabeyy xaa ne zee yachub xaa yek xaa per nachubt xaa pa nzeb yeezh nu sebyoo xaa xaa stub gazh mbizh.
Yilo yixoob stub gazh mbizh zee lee ngwleyy wii lo yeezh kwaan nzoxbab, nu chelee kwaan nzoxbab nanzhareept leen baal, zee lee ngwleyy yé: ‘Nzhul xaa’. Zee zet xaa xab xaa, zee gak nzhul xaa.
Per chelee yeezh kwaan nzoxbab nzhaxonn lo baal, gwluzh gorna ngulo ngok nzhul xaa,
zee lee ngwleyy wii lo xaa ne stuba. Chelee yeezh kwaan nzoxbab nzhaxonn lo baal nu ngulo nguna nayech yich yek xaa, ngok Beed xaa.
Per chelee xaa nzak xaa nanzhaxonnt yeezh kwaan nzoxbab yek xaa, nu mzhib yich nagaasa, nel ngokwena nu lee xaa ne ngok nzhul. Zee lee ngwleyy yé: ‘Nzhul nak xaa’.
zee wii ngwleyy lo baal cho xaa. Cheleeya luu kwaan rus lo xaa nu kwaan nagaas cheep naka nebse tub kwaan mzhiib lo baal, cheleeya nebse sbaaya, nzhul nak xaa.
Chelee tub xaabyi gab yich yek nu lake yed yek xaa, nzhul xaa zee.
Nu cheleeya yich lachuzh xaa gab nu lakeya neb yed, noka nzhul xaa zee.
Per cheleeya nzho kwaan rus o naxne lo pa neb yed na, chol naz yek xaa o naz lachuzh xaaya, yeezh kwaan nyall kazhiiba.
Zee lee ngwleyy wii lo xaa chelee paro yed na nzeki nu na rus nu naxne, mod na yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa,
zee lee ngwleyy yé: ‘Beed xaa’. Nel nyal yeezh kwaan nzeb yek xaa’.
Xaa kwaan nkano yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa nkin gak xaa ler kwaan mraz cho nu laa xaa yich yek xaa, nu saaw xaa cheep garlo xaa nu kozhe xaa nu yé xaa: ‘¡Beed na! ¡Beed na!’
Nu gorna nkano xaa yeezh ne nak xaa xaa beed; nkin yo techo xaa naz jwer pa mbaz re xaa.
Ley cheen kwaan mke byopGorna lee ler kwaan nak yich led mbakxiil o kwaan nak ler wen doo,
o yil, o re kwaan nak yed,
nu cheleeya ke byopa zee na nayeya o naxneya, cho ler o cho yed o cho re yil, zee nzhaal yalu xaaya lo ngwleyy.
Zee lee ngwleyy wii loya, nu kozhaw xaaya tub gazh mbizh.
Nu gorna yixoob gazh mbizh zee wii xaa loya, zee nel che nzhaxonna lo yil cheen ler o lo stub kwaan nak yed, nu cheleeya nzhaxonna, zee mke byop kwaan nakapa: zee leeya gak beed.
Zeek xaa dubse ler zee, kwaan nak yil, o ler kwaan nak yich led mbakxiil o ler kwaan wen doo o kwaan nak yed, nel mke byopa; nkin yeka lo ki.
Per chelee ngwleyy ngulo mwii xaa loya nu nanzhaket byop cho re yil, o cho re ler o cho re kwaan nak yed,
zee lee ngwleyy nabeyy zee yazet xaaya nu kozhaw xaaya stub gazh mbizh.
Gorna yilo koo xaaya, zee lee ngwleyy wii loya, nu chelee xaa ne xaa lal nzhaka nixa nanzhakeet byopa. Ngok beeda zee zhaal zeek xaaya lo ki, nel mkee byop naz leena o naz ticha.
Per gorna yilo yeta, chelee ngwleyy wii leeya nguna mor, zee choog xaa cho ler o yed o re yil.
Per cheleeya nyuna cho ler stuba nu cho re yil o cho re kwaan nak yed nu nzhake byopa stuba zee zeek xaaya lo ki nel mkee byopa.
Per chelee ler nu re yil o re kwaan nak yed zet xaaya nu yiib re kwaan mke byop choya, zee bare xaa zet xaaya stuba, zee gak nzhula.”
Kwaane nak ley leezha kee byop cho ler kwaan nak yich led mbakxiil o ler kwaan wen doo nu re yil o re kwaan nak yed zee yé ngwleyy beeda o nzhula.
Yalnzhul cheen xaa kwaan nyall choNgunii Xaa Tubka Nak lo Ches nu nzhé xaa:
“Kwaane nak tub ley kwaan gak cheen xaa nkano yalyizh kwaan nyall cho xaa: gorna gak nzhul xaa stuba zee nzhaal luu xaa xaa lo ngwleyy.
Zee wee xaa ngwleyy zit paro mbaz re xaa zee wii xaa lo xaa. Nu chelee ngwleyy ne lee yalyizh kwaan nyall cho xaa ne nzak ngokwenla,
zee lee ngwleyy xaal xaa yaxii chop mbyin ma mban ma nzhul, nu yag sedr nu ler naxne nu tub ram yix hisopo kwent cheen xaa nkano yalyizh kwaan nyal cho xaa.
Zeera lee ngwleyy xaal xaa zee gut xaa tub mbyin roo tub yas yo kwaan nzho nis xlen leen;
zeera zen xaa yag sedr nu ler naxne nu tub ram yix hisopo nu le bsii xaaya tubka kwaan mbyin mban leen ren cheen mbyin ngut lo nis xlen.
Zeera chuun xaa ren tub gazh welt cho xaa kwaan gak nzhul lo yalyizh kwaan nyall cho xaa nu yé xaa: ‘Ngok nzhul xaa ne’. Nu lee mbyin mban sela xaa naz wen.
Lee xaa kwaan gak nzhul zet xaa xab xaa nu chub xaa rese yich dubse xaa nu gaz xaa zee lake nzhul xaa. Zeera zeeb xaa paro mbaz re xaa, per lake xaa naz jwer yoo ler cheen xaa tub gazh mbizh.
Lee mbizh xon zen xaa chop mbakxiil yeen ma wen, nu tub mbakxiil yeen ma gol, ma nzho tub liin nu ma wen; noka xoop kil arin kwaan wen doo, kwaan nak gon cheen yalgon kwaan guch kwaan nseyt nu tub part lo chon part lo tub litr nseyt.
Zee lee ngwleyy xaa kwaan nle nzhul xaa, wee xaa xaa lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa kwaan ngok nzhul lo yalyizh kwaan nyall cho xaa.
Zee lee ngwleyy zen tub mbakxiil yeen ma mach nu teed xaa ma mod gon kwaan zere xaa gorna nlewann xaa, kwaan tub part lo chon part lo tub litr nseyt nu kun xaaya mod gon kwaan nkun xaa lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak.
Zee choog xaa yenn mbakxiil yeen pa nambey pa nchoog xaa yenn ma kwaan nted xaa zee gak nambey xaa, nu lee ma kwaan nzek xaa tira lo mdo lee ma nak gon kwaan le zee bare xaa gak xaa mod yilo nu gon kwaan nle nzhul xaa mdo ropse kwaane nak kwaan nyalzo ngwleyy gaw xaa nel naka kwaan nambey doo.
Gwluzh zeera zen ngwleyy cheep ren cheen ma kwaan nak gon kwaan zere xaa gorna nlewann xaa nu teeb xaaya lad li xan nzha xaa kwaan gak nzhul, nu kwen yaa xaa kwaan nachaa lad li nu kwen nii xaa kwaan nachaa lad li.
Nu sbaaka zen ngwleyy tub part lo chon part lo tub litr nseyt nu teeb xaaya lozhya xaa lad beg,
nu le bsii xaa kwen yaa xaa lad li kwaan nseyt kwaan nzho lozhya xaa lad beg, nu chuun xaa nseyt kwaan kwen yaa xaa tub gazh welt lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak.
Lee nseyt kwaan lake kwaan nzho lozhya ngwleyy, teeb xaa lad li xan nzha xaa kwaan gak nzhul nu kwen yaa xaa kwaan nachaa lad li nu kwen nii xaa kwaan nachaa lad li, leeka paro mteeb xaa ren cheen ma kwaan nak gon kwaan zere xaa gorna nlewann xaa.
Lee nseyt kwaan lake lozhya xaa xo xaa yek xaa kwaan gak nzhul. Snee le ngwleyy zee gak nzhul xaa lo na, Xaa Tubka nak.
Zeera lee ngwleyy teed ma nak gon kwaan gak nzhul xaa, zee lee xaa na beed gak nzhul; zeera choog xaa yenn ma kwaan zeek xaa lo mdo,
nu zeek xaa ma lo mdo tubka kwaan gon cheen yalgon. Nu snee lee ngwleyy zee gak nzhul xaa.
Chelee xaa prob xaa, nankanot xaa kwaan zii xaa ma, zee zen xaa tub mbakxiil yeen ma mach, mod gon kwaan kun xaa, lo kwaan nzere xaa gorna nle wann xaa zee kwii wen xaa kwaan na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nu chop kil arin kwaan wen doo kwaan guch kwaan nseyt, kwaan nak gon cheen yalgon nu tub part lo chon part lo tub litr nseyt,
nu chop ngog o chop palom, mod nzho moda lo xaa, tub ma zaa xaa zee gak nzhul xaa, lee stub ma zeek xaa lo mdo.
Lee mbizh xon gorna ngulo ngok nambey xaa wee xaa rese kwaane lo ngwleyy roo li na, Xaa Tubka Nak.
Zee lee ngwleyy zen mbakxiil yeen ma nak gon kwaan zere xaa gorna nlewann xaa nu tub part lo chon part lo tub litr nseyt nu kun xaaya mod gon kwaan nkun xaa lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak.
Zeera choog xaa yenn mbakxiil yeen, ma nak gon kwaan zere xaa gorna nlewann xaa, zee lee ngwleyy zen cheep ren cheen mbakxiil nu teeb xaaya lad li xan nzha xaa kwaan gak nzhul nu kwen yaa xaa kwaan nachaa lad li nu kwen nii xaa kwaan nachaa lad li.
Zee lee ngwleyy zhiib nseyt lozhya xaa lad beg,
nu kwaan kwen yaa xaa lad li chuun xaa nseyt kwaan nzho lozhya xaa lad beg gazh welt lo na Xaa Tubka Nak.
Zee noka ngwleyy teeb nseyt lad li xan nzha xaa kwaan gak nzhul nu kwen yaa kwaan nachaa lad li nu kwen nii xaa kwaan nachaa lad li leeka paro mteeb xaa ren cheen ma nak gon kwaan nzere xaa gorna nlewann xaa.
Lee nseyt kwaan lake kwaan nzho lozhya ngwleyy teeb xaa yek xaa kwaan na beed zee gak nzhul lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak.
Nu sbaaka teed xaa tub ngog o tub palom, loka mod nzho moda lo xaa kwaan gak nzhul.
Tub ma gak gon kwaan gak nzhul xaa, lee stub ma gak gon kwaan zeek xaa ma lo mdo nu kwaan gon cheen yalgon; snee lee ngwleyy zee gak nzhul xaa lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak.
Kwaane nak ley cheen xaa kwaan nkano yalyizh cheen yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa, xaa nankanot kwaan zaa lo yalnzhul cheen.”
Yalnzhul cheen yoo kwaan mke byop choZee lee Xaa Tubka Nak ngunii lo Ches nu Aarón nu nzhé xaa:
“Gorna lee gu zeeb yizhyo Canaán, kwaan za na gak xcheen gu, chelee na le na zee kee byop cho lak yoo yezh cheen gu,
zee lee xaa kwaan nak cheen yoo yanii lo ngwleyy, nu yé xaa: “Nzak na ke byop cho li na.
Zee lee ngwleyy gorna zeraka zeeb xaa leen yoo, nabeyy xaa zee koo xaa rese kwaan nzho leen yoo, zee nagakt beed rese kwaan nzho leena. Zeera zeeb ngwleyy wii leena.
Zee wii xaa lo kwaan mke byop nu cheleeya nlu kwaan nke byop cho yoo lo xaa, kwaan na naye o kwaan naxne, kwaan nech nzho cho yoo,
zee lee ngwleyy roo leen yoo nu saaw xaa roo yoo dubse tub gazh mbizh.
zee nabeyy ngwleyy zee yakiib xaa re ke kwaan mke byop cho yoo nu yalabi xaaya zit roo yezh tub pa beed.
Zee noka nabeyy xaa re xaa zee koo xaa re ban kwaan nke cho bla cheen yoo nu lee kwaan koo xaa yalabi xaa zit roo yezh tub pa beed.
Zeera zen xaa stub naz ke nu zhiib xaaya paro mkiib xaa re ke yilo nu ban kub zee kobde xaa yoo.
Nu Chelee cho yoo mbare mke byop stuba gwluzh gorna ngulo mzuub xaa cho ke nu gorna ngulo mchezhe xaa choya stuba,
zee lee ngwleyy zeeb yasewii; nu cheleeya seetaka nzhekera byop choya beeda.
Kwaanzee nzhaal luux xaa yoo nu re ke cheena nu re yag nu rese kwaan nak cheena nzhaal yalabi xaa zit roo yezh tub pa beed.
Loka xaa zeeb leen yoo rese mbizh kwaan ngunabeyy xaa leeya yaaw, xaa ne gak beed axta la yalnakaw.
Lee xaa kwaan gaa leen yoo zee, zet xaa xab xaa; noka xaa kwaan gaw leen yoo zee zet xaa xab xaa.
Per chelee ngwleyy zeeb wii nu namketra byopa, gorna ngulola mdexkwaaya zee lee ngwleyy yé: “Ngulola ngok nzhul yoo”, nu naketra byop choya.
Zee zen xaa chop mbyin nu yag sedr, ler naxne nu tub ram yix hisopo, zee le nzhul xaa yoo;
zee gut xaa tub mbyin roo tub yas yo kwaan nzho nis xlen leen.
Zeera zen xaa yag sedr, tub ram yix hisopo, ler naxne nu mbyin mban nu le bsii xaaya kwaan ren cheen mbyin ngut nu kwaan nis xlen nu chuun xaaya tub gazh welt cho yoo.
Nu snee le nzhul xaa yoo kwaan ren cheen mbyin nu kwaan nis xlen nu kwaan mbyin mban, yag sedr nu tub ram yix hisopo nu ler naxne.
Zeera sela xaa mbyin mban naz wen. Snee le nzhul xaa yoo zee lake nzhula.
Kwaane nak ley cheen rese lo yalyizh kwaan nyall cho xaa nu cheen yeezh kwaan nzoxbab,
byop kwaan nke cho ler o cho yoo,
o kwaan nzeki nu kwaan na rus.
Snee nzho mod labeyy xaa kwaan nzhul lo beed nu kwaane nak ley cheen yalyizh kwaan nyall cho xaa.
Kwaan beed cheen xaabyiNgunii Xaa Tubka Nak lo Ches nu lo Aarón nu nzhé xaa:
—Guzh lo re xaa Israel kwaane: Loka xaabyi xaa kwaan nkano yalyizh kwaan nroo nis cho yed cho, gak beed xaa.
Chelee cho yed cho xaabyi nlu nroo nis o nyaawa, kwaane nle beed yed cho xaa, nu nis kwaan nroo cho xaa nle beed re kwaane.
Nu noka xloon xaa kwaan nzha xaa lo, kwaan mxoya lo noka gak beed, nu noka re kwaan nzob xaa lo gak beed.
Nu loka xaa gal cho xloon xaa zet xaa xab xaa, nu gaz xaa per gak beed xaa axta la yalnakaw.
Nu loka xaa zob lo kwaan mzob xaa nroo nis cho yed cho, zet xaa xab xaa nu gaz xaa per gak beed xaa axta la yalnakaw.
