Ble gu gu zee gak nambey gu lo na, nel nambey nak na, Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa nak Xtios gu.
Ble gu kwaan nii re ley cheen na, nel na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nle nambey gu.
Loka xaa nge lo xuz o lo xnaa nzhaal yet xaa, nel mde xaa lo xuz xaa nu lo xnaa xaa; zee leeka lee xaa gut xaa lo kwaan mle xaa.
Loka xaabyi xaa chaal xngwnaa wechxinn, xaabyi nu ngwnaa nzhaal yet xaa.
Loka xaa chaal xngwnaa xuz, nle nanont xaa leeka xuz xaa, ngwnaa nu xaabyi ropse xaa nzhaal yet; leeka rop xaa gut xaa lo kwaan mle xaa.
Cheleeya tub xaabyi chaal leeka saxaabyi xaa modxa nchaal xaa tub ngwnaa, mle xaa kwaan beed nu ropse xaa nzhaal yet, leeka rop xaa gut xaa lo kwaan mle xaa.
Cheleeya nzho tub xaabyi ka tub ngwnaa nu xnaa me, kwaan tira nanzhaalt le xaa. Lee xaa nu rop me yonse xaa zeek xaa, zee nayotra kwaan tira nawent lo re gu.
Chelee tub xaabyi chaal kwaan tub ma, nzhaal yet xaa nu noka lee ma yet.
Chelee tub ngwnaa chaal kwaan tub ma, nzhaal yet me, lo kwaan mle me nu noka lee ma yet.
Chelee tub xaabyi chaal leeka bzan xaa, me nak xchaap xuz xaa o me nak xchaap xnaa xaa, mloo xaa yalnto zee ropse xaa nzhaal yet delant lo re xaa yezh, nel namkanot xaa respet lo bzan xaa zee ded rop xaa bid lo re jwalt cheen xaa.
Chelee tub xaa gaa kwaan tub ngwnaa nu chaal xaa me re mbizh kwaan nded ren lextoo me nu rop xaa me nguneya, kwaanzee ropse xaa koo xaa yezh.
Nachaalt lu xnis lu bzan xuz lu nu bal xnaa lu. Kwaane nii mloo lu yalnto lo sawlizh lu, nu ropse xaa ded bid lo kwent cheen jwalt cheen xaa.
Chelee tub xaa chaal xngwnaa xich xaa koo xaa xkalnto xich xaa, ropse xaa ded bid lo jwalt cheen xaa, nu ropse xaa yet nu nalaat xaa dii.
Chelee tub xaa ka xngwnaa wech xaa nle xaa tub kwaan beed koo xaa xkalnto wech xaa, ropse xaa nalaat dii.
Ble gu kwaan nii ley cheen na nu ble gu kwaan ngunabeyy na gu le gu, zee lee yizhyo nagakt mod tub xaa zere kwaan beed lextoo.
Nalet gu kwaan nle re xaa yezh, xaa ko na lo re gu, nel lee re xaa mle rese kwaan beed ne, nu na ngunayii ne na re xaa.
Per lee na nii lo re gu: Lee yizhyo cheen re xaa gak cheen re gu, tub yizhyo pa nxonn nizh nu mzhin mod nis. Leeka na zaya lo re gu zee gaka xcheen gu,Na nak Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa nak Xtios gu mloo xa gu lo stub naz re yezh.
Per lee re gu nzhaal koo xaa re ma nambey lo re ma beed, nu re mbyin ma nambey, nu re mbyin ma beed, zee nalebeedt gu kwaan re ma ne, nixa kwaan mbyin, nu nixa kwaan ma nze lextoo lo yo, nel mlo xa ma zee nak ma ma beed.
Gok nambey re gu lo na nel lee na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nambey nak na, nu mlo xa na re gu lo re yezh zee gak re gu xaa na.
Loka tub re gu, ngwnaa o xaabyi, xaa nak wezh o xaa mbezh nzhedizh kwaan re xaa ngut, nzhaal yet xaa kwaan ke nu leeka lee xaa gut xaa lo kwaan mle xaa.
Yalnzhul cheen re ngwleyyXaa Tubka Nak nzhé lo Ches:—Guzh lo re ngwleyy, xgann Aarón, zee nagakt beed xaa kwaan tub re xaa ngut xaa yezh cheen xaa.
Per nebse xaa nzho mod gal xaa cho nak re sawlizh xaa, xaa yet, xuz xaa, xnaa xaa, xiin xaa, wech xaa,
o bzan xaa me mad, me namkanot xaabyi; kwaan tub re xaa ne nzho mod gak beed xaa.
Nagalt xaa cho tub re xaa ngut, xaa yezh, zee le xaa zee gak beed xaa, nel le xaa nak xaa non lo re xaa yezh.
Nu nachubt xaa yich yek xaa, nu nixa nachoogt xaa xlox xaa, nu nixa nakeet xaa bde cho xaa.
Nkin gak nambey xaa lo na, xaa nak Xtios xaa, nu nanzhaalt le nanont xaa le na, nel lee xaa nak xaa nzaa gon kwaan nzhek lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, kwaan nak mod kwaan nzhaw na, kwaanzee nkin gak nambey xaa.
Nik tub ngwleyy nyent mod ka tub ngwnaa me nto cho, nu nixa me kwaan mlaa xaabyi, nu nixa me kwaan mchaal xaabyi, nel nzhul nak xaa lo na, xaa nak Xtios xaa.
Nkin le nambey lu xaa, nel lee xaa nak xaa nzaa gon kwaan nak mod kwaan nzhaw na, xaa nak Xtios xaa. Nu nambey gak xaa lo lu, nel na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nambey nak na, nu na nle nambey gu.
Nu chelee xchaap ngwleyy gak me nto cho leeka lee me le zee nangwiit re xaa respet lo xuz me, zee yek me lo ki.
Lee xaa nabeyy lo rese ngwleyy mkayaa xaa yalnabeyy gak xaa ler nzhul, nel mle nzhul xaa xaa kwaan nseyt kwaan nzhul kwaan mteeb xaa yek xaa. Kwaanzee nalaat xaa zob reech yich yek xaa, nu nixa nachazt xaa xab xaa kwaan nlu lee xaa nzho bel.
Nu nixa nareept xaa paro nzhob xaa ngut, nalet xaa zee gak beed xaa kwent cheen xuz xaa o xnaa xaa.
Naroot xaa leen li na zee nalebeedt xaa leen li na, xaa nak Xtios xaa, nel ngok nzhul xaa kwaan nseyt kwaan nle nzhul na xaa; na nak Xaa Tubka Nak.
Lee ngwnaa kwaan gak xngwnaa xaa nkin gak me me kwaan zer chaal xaabyi.
Nu nakat xaa tub ngwnaa byud, nu nixa ngwnaa kwaan mlaa xaabyi, nu ngwnaa me mkano xaa lajwers, o me nto cho; xngwnaa xaa nkin gak me nik tub xaabyi zer chaal, me nak sawlazh xaa,
Kwaan nle zee nyent mod gak xaa ngwleyyXaa Tubka Nak nzhé lo Ches:
—Guzh lo Aarón: Nik tub dii cheen lu, xaa kwaan nawent nak, nyent mod bii lo na, nu zaa xaa gon kwaan nak mod kwaan nzhaw na.
Nik tub xaa kwaan nawent nyent mod bii lo na: xaa syeg o xaa mdeen, xaa nawent nak tub pa cho,
xaa kwaan ngoch nii o ngoch yaa,
xaa naleng nak tich o xaa chuut doo, xaa nzho beg garlo, xaa kwaan nzeb mbeed, o xaa kwaan nzeb yeezh kwaan nzoxbab, o xaa kwaan ngwa golp xko.
Nik tub xaa lo re dii cheen Aarón xaa nagakt wen nyent mod bii lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nu zeek xaa gon lo na. Nu chelee xaa nawent xaa; nyent mod zaa xaa gon kwaan nak mod kwaan nzhaw na, xaa nak Xtios xaa.
Nzho mod gaw xaa gon kwaan nzaa xaa lo na, xaa nak Xtios xaa, gon kwaan nambey lo re kwaan nambey.
Per nabiit xaa gax lo ler ndok kwaan nsaaw Pa Nambey Doo nixa lo mdo, chelee xaa nawent xaa, zee nalebeedt xaa leen li na, nel na nak Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa mle nambey re ngwleyy.”
Sbaa nzhé Ches lo Aarón nu lo re xgann xaa, nu lo rese xaa Israel.
Gon nzhulNgunii Xaa Tubka Nak lo Ches nu nzhé xaa:
—Guzh lo Aarón nu lo re xgann xaa zee wii doo xaa respet lo gon kwaan nambey kwaan nzaa re xaa Israel lo na, zee nalebeedt re xaa le na kwaan nambey na, Xaa Tubka Nak.
Noka ngunabeyy Dios zee yé xaa: Loka tub xaa nak dii cheen Aarón, xaa nak xaa beed zen gon kwaan nzaa xaa Israel lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, koo xaa xaa leen li na.
Chelee tub dii cheen Aarón xaa ne nzak lo yeezh kwaan nyall cho xaa, o xaa nroo nis cho, nyent mod gaw xaa gon ne chelee xaa nagakt nzhul xaa.Loka xaa kwaan gal cho tub kwaan ngok beed kwaan ngol ma ngut cho, o cho xaa kwaan nroo nis cho,
o gal xaa cho tub ma nze lazh lo yo o cho tub xaa beed, loka kwaan mle beed xaa,
gak beed xaa axta la yalnakaw nu gaz xaa, zee nzho mod gaw xaa gon kwaan nzhul.
Gorna yilo yaaz mbizh zeera gak nzhul xaa nu zeera nzho mod gaw xaa gon kwaan nzhul, nel leeya nak kwaan nzhaw xaa.
Nyent mod gaw xaa baal cheen ma nzhet sbaasa nu nixa ma kwaan mbit ma, o ma kwaan mle byog ma, nel gak beed xaa kwaan leeya. Na nak Xaa Tubka Nak.
Re ngwleyy nzhaal le re kwaan ni na nu snee naletra xaa jwalt nu nixa nadedtra xaa bid lo yalgut nel nixa mle nanont xaa gon cheen. Na nak nak, Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa nle nambey re ngwleyy.
Nik tub xaa zit nyent mod gaw gon kwaan nzhul. Nixa xaa mbaz garli ngwleyy nixa xaa nke zhiin lo xaa,
per nzho mod gaw xmos xaaya, xaa kwaan mzi ngwleyy o xaa ngol garli xaa.
Chelee xchaap tub ngwleyy ka tub xaa nanakt ngwleyy, nyent mod gaw me gon kwaan nzhul kwaan nzhaw ngwleyy.
Per chelee xchaap ngwleyy lake byud, o laa xaabyi me nu nankanot me mad nu bare me garli xuz me, mod me techo, nzho mod gaw me kwaan nzhaw xuz me. Per lee re xaa zit, nik tub xaa nyent mod gawa.
Chelee tub xaa gaw gon kwaan nzhul, per nanzeent xaaya nzhaal zere xaa gon kwaan ndaw xaa lo ngwleyy tub part lo gaay part.
Per lee re ngwleyy xaa Israel nalaat gak beed re kwaan nzaa xaa lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak,
nu chelee xaa gaw xaaya kwaan nambey, kala xaa le re xaa yezh jwalt zee nkin teed xaa ma nak gon kwaan zere xaa gorna nle wann xaa, Na nak, Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa nle nambey xaa.”
Gon kwaan kayaa Xaa Tubka NakLee Xaa Tubka Nak, ngunii lo Ches nu nzhé xaa:
—Guzh lo Aarón nu lo re xgann xaa nu lo rese xaa Israel: Loka tub re gu xaa Israel o xaa zit, xaa nzho lo re gu, zaa tub gon lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, leezha myaan xaa tub kwaan o gorna nzaa xaa tub gon kwaan nzhal lextoo xaa,
nkin gak ma tub ma mach, ma wen, ma nankanot yalyizh mbakxiil yeen o chib o ngoon, zee gaka tub kwaan kayaa na.
Nazaat gu nik tub ma nkano yalyizh lo na, nel nakayaat na ma.
Nateedt gu tub ma syeg lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nixa ma ne nzak, nixa ma ngoch, nixa ma nzeb yeezh cho, nixa ma nzeb mbeed cho, nixa ma nkano bde, nixa nateedt gu nik tub re ma snee nak.
Per nzho mod zaa gu gon kwaan nzhal lextoo gu, tub la ngoon yeen o tub mbakxiil ma nawent o ma win, per lee gon ne nakayaat na, leezha myaan gu tub kwaan.
Nixa nateedt gu tub ma mgaazh xaa xko, ma ngo xaa xko, ma nchoog xaa xko lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nalet gu kwaane yizhyo cheen gu.
Nixa nakayaat gu re ma ne lo re xaa zit, zee teed gu ma mod gon kwaan nzhaw na, xaa nak Dios cheen gu nakayaat na ma kwaan nawent nak.
Ngunii Xaa Tubka Nak, lo Ches nu nzhé xaa:
—Gorna gal tub ngoon yeen, tub mbakxiil yeen o tub chib, zo ma kwaan xnaa ma tub gazh mbizh; lee mbizh xon, naz delant nzhola mod kayaa na, Xaa Tubka Nak, ma mod gon kwaan zeek xaa ma lo mdo.
Nu nachoogt gu yenn tub la bak o tub mbakxiil kwaan xinn ma leeka mbizh.
Gorna lee gu teed ma nak gon, kwaan zaa gu dixkix lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, teed gu ma tub mod nali zee kayaa na ma.
Nu leeka mbizh zee gaw gu ma; nu nixa nalaat gu nik stik ma stub mbizh. Na nak Xaa Tubka Nak.
Ble gu kwaan mxaal na gu le gu na. Na nak Xaa Tubka Nak.
Snee le non gu le na kwaan nambey, sbaa labeyy gu na mod xaa nambey lo re xaa Israel, nel na nak Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa nle nambey gu.
Na mlo gu yizhyo Egipto zee gak na Xtios gu. Na nak Xaa Tubka Nak.
Re mbizh cheen re yalni kwaan non<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?2.12.1">Ex. 12</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?3.16.1">Lev. 16</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?4.28–29.1">Nm. 28–29</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?5.16.1">Dt. 16</a>)Ngunii Xaa Tubka Nak lo Ches nu nzhé xaa:
—Yé lu lo re xaa Israel: kwaane nak re yalni nambey kwaan le gu lo na Xaa Tubka Nak, nel na mlaya.
Xoop mbizh ke gu zhiin, per lee mbizh sab kwaz gu, nel naka tub mbizh nambey lo na Xaa Tubka Nak, nu nik tub zhiin naket gu nu mrezh re xaa yezh zee zhaal gu kwaan re xaa tub mod non doo nexa paro nzho gu.
Kwaane nak re yalni kwaan mla na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nu brezh re xaa yezh zee zhaal gu kwaan re xaa tub mod non doo nu le guya mer mbizh kwaan naka.
Yalni cheen Paskwa cheen na, Xaa Tubka Nak, zelo zhe chida xche mbee yilotlaka gorna nzhazhel yizhyo.
Leeka chiin xche mbee ne zelo yalni kwaan nzhaw xaa pan kwaan nanyut lebadur leen lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak. Nu gazh mbizh gaw gu pan kwaan nanyut lebadur leen.
Lee mbizh yilotlaka brezh gu re xaa yezh zee zhaal gu kwaa re xaa tub mod non doo nu mbizh ne nik tub zhiin nalet gu.
Dubse tub gazh mbizh zeek gu gon lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak. nu mrezh re xaa yezh zee zhaal gu kwaan re xaa tub mod non doo nu nik tub zhiin naket gu.”
Zee le Xaa Tubka Nak nzhé lo Ches:
—Guzh lo re xaa Israel: gorna reep gu leen yizhyo kwaan za na lo gu, gorna koo gu yalgon cheen gu, yalaa gu tub yaaya kwaan yilotlaka lo ngwleyy.
Zee lee ngwleyy kuna lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, stub mbizh zhe sab zee kayaa na xaa.
Leeka mbizh zee teed gu tub mbakxiil yeen, ma tub liin, ma wen, tub ma kwaan zeek xaa lo mdo lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak.
Nu noka zaa gu tap kil arin kwaan wen kwaan nuch nseyt, kwaan nak gon cheen yalgon kwaan yek, kwaan nak bech kwaan chul doo lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak nu noka zaa gu tub litr nis ub kwaan gak gon kwaan nak xis ub.
Nagawt gu pan nu nixa kwaan mbyeex o kwaan kub, axta gorna yalaa gu gon lo na, xaa nak Xtios gu. Kwaane nak tub ley kwaan tira lo re dii cheen gu, nexa paro nzho gu.
Koo gu kwent gazh sman yilo ded mbizh sab, kwaane nak mbizh kwaan wee gu gon kwaan kun xaa lo mdo lo na;
koo gu kwent choobchii mbizh per noka sab garziil; zee zaa gu gon cheen yalgon kwaan kub lo na Xaa Tubka Nak.
Loka paro nzho gu zee yiidno gu chop pan mod gon kwaan kun xaa lo na kwaan yilo, nu chop pan kwaan mdexkwaa tap kil arin, kwaan mbyeex kwaan lebadur.
Zeera zaa gu tub chib, ma mach ma wen, ma gak gon kwaan zhe xjwalt nu gak nzhul xaa chop mbakxiil yeen, ma nzho tub liin ma kwaan nak gon kwaan kwi wen gu kwaan na.
Zee lee ngwleyy zaa rop mbakxiil yeen, tubka kwaan pan, kwaan nak kwaan yilotlaka, kwaan nak gon kwaan kun xaa lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, tub gon kwaan nambey lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, kwaan nak kwaan gaw ngwleyy.
Leeka mbizh zee mrezh re xaa yezh zee zhaal gu kwaan re xaa tub mod non doo Nu mbizh ne nik tub zhiin naket gu. Kwaane nak tub ley kwaan tira lo re dii cheen gu nexa paro nzho gu.
Gorna zhin mbizh kwaan toop gu yalgon cheen gu, natoopt gu rese kwaan nak gaw kwaan mlake leen xkizhyo gu, leeya nak kwaan gaw re xaa nyent kwaan gaw nu re xaa zit. Na nak Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa nak Xtios gu.
Zee ngunii Xaa Tubka Nak lo Ches nu nzhé xaa:
—Guzh lo re xaa Israel: mbizh yilotlaka lo mbee gazh gak tub mbizh kwaan naket gu zhiin, nu mrezh re xaa yezh zee zhaal gu kwaan re xaa tub mod non doo gorna kwezh kach.
Mbizh zee nik tub zhiin naket gu, sinka zaa gu lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak tub gon.”
Zee lee Xaa Tubka Nak nzhé lo Ches:
Lee chii xchee mbee gazh nak mbizh kwaan zhe re jwalt cheen gu. nu mrezh re xaa yezh zee zhaal gu kwaan re xaa tub mod non doo zee zhaal gu zee zaa gu tub gon lo na.
Nik tub zhiin naket gu mbizh ne, nel mbizh ne nak mbizh kwaan zhe re jwalt cheen gu, zee kwii wen gu kwaan na, Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa nak Xtios gu.
Rese xaa kwaan nankwant mbizh ne, koo xaa xaa yezh.
Nu loka xaa kwaan ke zhiin mbizh ne, na ko xaa yezh.
Kwaanzee, nik tub zhiin naket gu. Kwaane nak tub ley kwaan tira lo re dii cheen gu nexa paro nzho gu.
Mbizh kwaan nak mbizh kwaan naket gu zhiin nu kwan gu. Mbizh sab ne nkin kozhaw gu mzhel yizhyo zhe yee xche mbee gazh nu axta mzhel yizhyo stub mbizh.”
Zee ngunii Xaa Tubka Nak lo Ches nu nzhé xaa:
—Guzh lo re xaa Israel: chiin xche mbee gazh zelo yalni cheen ramad zee le non gu na, Xaa Tubka Nak.
Mbizh yilotlaka mrezh re xaa yezh zee zhaal gu kwaan re xaa tub mod non doo nu nik tub zhiin naket gu mbizh ne.
Tub gazh mbizh zaa gu gon lo na Xaa Tubka Nak. Nu lee mbizh xon mrezh re xaa yezh zee zhaal gu kwaan re xaa tub mod non doo zee zaa gu gon lo na Xaa Tubka Nak nel naka yalni kwaan le non gu na; nu mbizh ne nik tub zhiin naket gu.
Kwaane nak yalni kwaan mlaa na Xaa Tubka Nak, leezha mrezh xaa re xaa yezh tub mod non doo, zee zaa gu gon lo na, gon cheen yalgon nu ma kwaan nzek xaa lo mdo zee kwii wen xaa kwaan na, nu gon cheen xis ub, mod naka kad mbizh.
Rese yalni ne nak kwaan nle xaa mbizh kwaan nyalzo ya nixa nanakta sab, mbizh cheen na, Xaa Tubka Nak, zee zaa xaa kwaan zelazh xaa, gon kwaan myaan xaa zaa xaa nu gon kwaan nzhal lextoo xaa.
Mer chiin xche mbee gazh, yilo toop gu yalgon nu dubse tub gazh mbizh le gu yalni cheen Xaa Tubka Nak. Mbizh yilotlaka nu mbizh xon gak tub mbizh kwaan naket gu zhiin, tub mbizh non doo.
Mbizh yilotlaka toop gu xle cheen yag kwaan chul doo nu ram yag yin nu yag kwaan nzeb doo lag lo nu yag la zyas kwaan nzeb ro yuu nu dubse tub gazh mbizh gak nix lextoo gu lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa nak Xtios gu.
Kad liin dubse tub gazh mbizh le gu yalni, zee le non gu na, Xaa Tubka Nak. Le guya mbee gazh. Kwaane nak tub ley kwaan tira lo re dii cheen gu.
Dubse tub gazh mbizh yo gu xramad gu. Rese xaa ngol mer lo xaa Israel yo leen xramad xaa,
zee ne rese dii cheen gu, le na mle zee mban rese xaa Israel leen ramad gorna mlo na xaa yizhyo Egipto. Na nak Xaa Tubka Nak, xaa nak Xtios gu.
Sbaa nzhé Ches lo re xaa Israel re yalni kwaan mlaa Xaa Tubka Nak le xaa.
Xni kwaan ke leen li Xaa Tubka Nak<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?2.27.20-21">Ex. 27:20-21</a>)Ngunii Xaa Tubka Nak lo Ches nu nzhé xaa:
—Guzh lo re xaa Israel zee yiidno xaa nseyt cheen yag olib, kwaan nzhul doo, zee ke xni leen li na. Zee rese bruj tubka zaaya xni.
Aarón dexkwaa bruj kwaan zaa xni leen yoo, naz tich ler kwaan nke lo kaj cheen trat, zee tubka zaaya xni lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, dubse yaal. Kwaane gak tub ley kwaan tira lo re dii cheen gu.
Pan kwaan nzaa xaa lo Xaa Tubka NakBzen arin kwaan wen doo nu keex lu chiibchop yat; nu kad cha yat gak nga tap kil.
Nu zhiib guya lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, lo mes kwaan nak nebse or, chop baal kwek guya nu xopga yat kad baal.
Nu kad baal zhiib gu yaal kwaan nzhul nu sbaa lee yat gak kwaan chul doo nzebech, kwaan gak mod tub gon kwaan nzelazh gu na, Xaa Tubka Nak.
Lee yat ne zhiib xaa tubka lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, yizata zhe sab. Kwaane gak tub kwaan tira yaan na lo re xaa Israel.
Lee yat ne nak kwaan gaw Aarón nu re xgann xaa nu gaw xaaya tub pa nambey, nel naka tub gon kwaan nambey lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak. Kwaane nak tub ley kwaan tira.
Bid kwaan ded xaa nge lo DiosLo re xaa Israel ngu tub xaabyi, xgann tub ngwnaa me Israel nu lee xuz xaa nak xaa Egipto. Nu ngu tub mbizh lee xaabyi ne mkwaan tub dil paro mbaz re xaa.
Per lee xgann ngwnaa me Israel mzelo mde lo le Xaa Tubka Nak. Zee mbe xaa xaa lo Ches. (Lee xnaa xaa le Selomit, xchaap Dibri, me nak dii cheen Dan).
Nu mlo xaa xaa lozhyib axta gorna yé Xaa Tubka Nak cho kwaan le xaa kwaan lee xaa.
Zee lee Xaa Tubka Nak nzhé lo Ches:
—Bloo gu xaa kwaan mde lo na naz paro mbaz re gu, loka xaa kwaan mbin kwaan ngunii xaa, bzhib gu yaa gu yek xaa, zee lee xaa yezh zaake xaa.
Guzh lo re xaa Israel: loka xaa ke lo le na, ded xaa bid kwent cheen jwalt cheen xaa.
Kwaanzee loka xaa kwaan ke lo le na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nzhaal yet xaa; rese xaa yezh zaake xaa, nexa chol xaa zit xaa o xaa ngol lo re guya, chelee xaa ke xaa lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nzhaal yet xaa.
Loka xaa gut samyet nzhaal yet xaa.
Loka xaa gut xma stub xaa zaa xaa stub ma zonii ma mbit xaa.
Loka xaa kwaan seweey wechxinn, sbaaka seweey xaa xaa:
loka tub xaa kiich stub xaa noka xaa zee yech, chelee tub xaa kich zaalo stub xaa noka zaalo xaa zee yech nu chelee tub xaa kiib leyy stub xaa noka leyy xaa zee yiib; mod mle xaa leeka sbaa le re xaa xaa.
