Nu kwaan tub lee ler naxne nagaas saaw xaa tich bruj, nu re kwaan nzaa xni kwaan nzob yeka, nu kwaan nsuyya, nu yann kwaan nyu xkade leen, nu tich rese kwaan nyu nseyt leen.
Zeera saaw xaa tich bruj kwaan nak or nu re kwaan nlexchinna kwaan tub lee yed kwaan chul doo, nu zhiib xaaya lo tub kwaan teed xaa bar choya zee nzho mod wee xaaya.
Lee lo mdo kwaan nak or, zhiib xaa tub lee ler naxne nagaas nu lee ticha saaw xaa kwaan tub lee yed chul doo, nu teed xaa bar choya zee nzho mod wee xaaya.
Zeera toop xaa rese kwaan nle xchinn xaa leen li na paro nzhaal xaa kwaan na, nu chal xaaya kwaan tub lee ler naxne nagaas, nu saaw xaa ticha kwaan tub lee yed kwaan chul doo, nu zeera zhiib xaaya lo bar zee nzho mod wee xaaya.
Nu koo xaa xkade lee mdo kwaan nzek xaa ma lo nu saaw xaa ticha kwaan tub lee ler naxne nagaas.
Nu lo mdo zhiib xaa rese kwaan nle xchinn na, nu yann kwaan nyu xkade leen, kwaan nkano zyen ley, palet, tas, nu rese kwaan nlexchinn xaa lo mdo. Zeera saaw xaa ticha kwaan tub lee yed chul doo nu teed xaa bar choya zee nzho mod wee xaaya.
