nu zaa xaa leeka lee xaa lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, rese mbizh kwaan myaan xaa gak nzhul xaa nu zaa xaa leeka lee xaa. Nu wee xaa tub mbakxiil yeen, ma nzho tub liin, ma gak gon kwaan zere xaa gorna nlewa rese mbizh kwaan mded yilo nakootra xaa kwent nel lee yalnzhul cheen xaa ngok beed.
Kwaane nak ley gorna yixoob mbizh yaan xaa gak nzhul xaa zaa xaa leeka lee xaa, ya xaa roo li na paro nzhaal xaa kwaan na,
