Zee lee ngwleyy zaaya lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, gon kwaan gak nzhul mdo, nu gon kwaan zeek xaa ma lo mdo kwent cheen xaa.
Zee chuub xaa yich yek xaa kwaan nambey roo li na, paro nzhaal xaa kwaan na, nu ko xaa yich yek xaa kwaan ngok nambey lo ki, kwaan nzho xan gon kwaan kwi wen xaa kwaan na.
