—Guzh lo Eleazar, xgann ngwleyy Aarón, koo xaa kwaan nyu yaal leen kwaan nzho lo ki nel nambey naka, nu yalabi xaa ki kwaan nzho leena zit.
Zen xaa re kwaan nyu yaal leen cheen re xaa ngutla nu dexkwaa xaa reya tub lag nales doo zee saawa cho mdo, nel mzaa re xaaya lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, nu nambey naka. Zee gaka mod tub nseyn lo re xaa Israel.
Zee lee ngwleyy Eleazar mzen kwaan nyu yaal leen kwaan nak brons, kwaan mzaa re xaa ngut lo bal, nu nales doo mdexkwaa xaaya zee saaw xaa cho mdo,
