Lee gon kwaan koxa gu zaa gu lo na gak mod tub gon cheen nzhobxtil nu xis ub.
Sbaaka zaa gu gon kwaan nak cheen gu lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak, rese kwaan nak tub part lo chii part kwaan kayaa gu lo re xaa Israel; zaa guya lo ngwleyy Aarón.
Rese gon kwaan nzelazh xaa kwaan nkayaa gu, nzhaal koxa gu tub part kwaan zaa gu lo na, Xaa Tubka Nak; kwaan wen doo lo rese nu kwaan nzhul nak.’
Noka yé lu: ‘Gorna koxa gu kwaan mas wenra nu zaa guya lo na, rese kwaan nlake gak xcheen re gu, xaa nak dii cheen Leví, mod xis ub nu mod nzhobxtil.
Gaw guya kwaan re xaa li gu palpa, kwaane gak kwaan yex ka gu nel nke gu zhiin leen li na.
Nalet gu nik tub jwalt gorna zaa gu gon kwaan wenra lo rese. Zee nalebeedt gu re kwaan nambey kwaan nak gon cheen re xaa Israel, zee nayeta gu.’”
