Zaa gu ma lo Eleazar, xaa nak ngwleyy, zee koo xaa ma pa nzho re gu zee gut xaa ma lo xaa.
Zee lee Eleazar, xaa nak ngwleyy, zen ren cheen ma kwaan kwen yaa xaa nu chuun xaaya tub gazh welt naz roo li na, Xaa Tubka Nak,
Zeera wii xaa le ngwley zeek ngoon; nu zeek xaa yed cheen ma, xpaal ma, ren cheen ma, nu xke ma.
Zeera zen ngwleyy yag sedr, nu yag hisopo nu ler naxne, zee ko xaaya lo bal kwaan kayek ngoon lo.
Zeera zet ngwleyy xab xaa, nu gaz xaa, zeera zeeb xaa pa mbaz re xaa; per gak beed xaa axta yilo la yalnakaw.
Seeka xaa kwaan mzeek ngoon, noka lee xaa nzhaal zet xab xaa, nu gaz xaa, per gak beed xaa axta la yalnakaw.
Nu tub xaa nzhul toop xkade cheen ngoon, ma nguk, nu yalaa xaaya naz tub lad pa nzho re xaa, pa nzhul na, zee lee re xaa Israel chaal xkade tubka kwaan nis zee gaka nis nzhul; kwaane nak nis kwaan nle nzhul xaa.
Xaa kwaan mtoop xkade cheen ngoon nkin zet xaa xab xaa, nu gak beed xaa axta la yalnakaw.
Nu xaa kwaan gal cho xaa ngut, gak beed xaa gazh mbizh.
Lee mbizh yon chuun xaa nis nzhul cho xaa nu sbaaka le xaa mbizh gazh zee gak nzhul xaa. Nu chelee xaa nachuunt xaa nis nzhul cho xaa mbizh yon nu mbizh gazh, nagakt nzhul xaa.
Rese xaa gal cho xaa ngut nu nagakt nzhul xaa, le beed xaa leen li na, Xaa Tubka Nak. Xaa zee nzhaal koo gu yezh Israel, nel namchubt xaa nis nzhul cho xaa, zee mlake beed xaa, nu tira lake beed xaa.
Kwaane nak ley kwaan nle xchiin xaa gorna nzhet tub xaa leen yoo ler pa mbaz re xaa, nu loka xaa reep leen yoo ler, nu rese kwaan nzho leena, gak beed tub gazh mbizh.
