Loka xaa nzha naz wen nu gal xaa cho tub xaa ngut kwaan spad o tub xaa ngut sbaasa o cho zhit cheen xaa ngut o cho baa, gazh mbizh gak beed xaa.
Xaa kwaan ngok beed, zen xaa xkade kwaan mzeek xaa ngoon, nu cheep xaaya leen tub yas nu xo xaa nis yuu leena.
