(-)
¿Cho kwaan nzak gu? ¡Telisa nanzheklat na nii na lee Dios nak tub xaa nanalit!
Kwaanzee nagakt xaa xinn Dios nel nzhekla xaa, nixa nagakt xaa xinn Dios kwent cheen re kwaan nle xaa, gak xaa xinn Dios nel nlesla Dios ne xaa.
Nel lo Xkyech Dios, nzhé Dios lo faraón, xaa mnabeyy Egipto: “Mle na lu rey zee ne xaa dubse yizhyo nkano na gro doo yalnabeyy, leezha le na re kwaan nawent lo lu”.
Kwaanzee Dios nlesla ne xaa re xaa nzhekla Dios, nu noka nle ned Dios lextoo re xaa nzhekla Dios gak ned.
Kwaanzee chelee myet nkin le myet kwaan nzhekla Dios, telisa né gu lo na: “¿Chozhiin nayii Dios ne re myet?”
Per lu nak tub myet yizhyo, nu nyent mod naab lu kwent lo Dios. Napa nel yé yas lo xaa mdexkwaaya, “¿Chozhiin snee mdexkwaa lu na?”
Lee xaa ndexkwaa yas nzho mod nabeyy xaa ban, zee le xaa kwaan nzhekla kwaan ban; nu kwaan ban nzho mod dexkwaa xaa tub yas chul doo, kwaan le xchiin xaa leezha yo xaa tub yalni, nu nzho mod dexkwaa xaa stub yas sbaasa.
Dios nak mod xaa ndexkwaa yas. Nyedoola xaa ne xaa re xaa mdexkwaa xaa la yalnayii tich, zee labeyy re myet yalnabeyy cheen xaa, nel sbaa nzhekla xaa.
Snee mle xaa zee nzho mod mlesla xaa ne xaa re be, nu luu xaa re kwaan chul nu re xni cheen xaa lo be, re xaa mrezhla xaa axta yilo.
Kwaanzee snee mrezh Dios rese nu, xaa Israel nu noka re gu, xaa nanakt xaa Israel.
Modxa nzhé yech kwaan mkee Oseas:Lee re xaa nangokt xaa na,yé na lee xaa nak xaa na;nu lee re xaa namkelat na,nkela na xaa nal.
Nu leeka zee paro nzhé xaa:“Re gu nanakt xaa na”.Leeka baa nzhé xaa:“Gu nak xinn Dios, xaa naban”.
Nu xomod nzhé Chay cheen dii cheen Israel: “Nixa zyen doo dii xaa Israel mod re yux kwaan nzhi roo nistoo, per chepse xaa le gan roo lo yalzi cheen yalgut.
Nel merla naab Dios kwent cheen xaa dubse yizhyo.”
Nu leeka Chay mkee:Chol Xuz be, Xaa Nabeyy, nglaa dii cheen be,nal gorne gak be mod rop yezh kwaan nak Sodoma nu Gomorra.
Xomod nzhaal zo myet nali lo Dios¿Cho kwaan nzak gu? Lee re xaa nanakt xaa Israel nakakwaant xaa zo nali xaa lo Dios, nixa seeya Dios mkiib jwalt cheen xaa nel ngwii xaa lo Dios.
Per lee nu, xaa Israel, xaa nzhekla le rese kwaan nzhé ley zee zo nali nu lo Dios, per namlet nu gan le nu kwaan nzhé ley.
¿Chozhiin? Nel lee re nu, xaa Israel, namwiit nu lo Dios, lee nu mwii lo re kwaan nle nu. Kwaanzee mralnii nu kwaan “ke kwaan nralnii re xaa”.
Modxa nzhé Xkyech Dios:Na zoob tub xaa yek yi Sión,lee xaa nak kwent tub ke kwaan ralnii rese xaa.Nu loka xaa wii lo xaa ne,nanzhebt xaa ne xaa Dios.
Wech nu bzan, kwaan naab na lo Dios nak, lee re sawlazh na, xaa Israel, le gan yalnaban kwaan tira, nel kwaan ba nak kwaan nzhekladoo lextoo na.
Nroo na jabor cheen re xaa nel ne na lee re xaa nkela re xcheen Dios, per nanlabeyyt xaa mer kwaan wli.
Nu nanet re xaa xomod nzo nali Dios re myet lo Dios, kwaanzee nzhekla re xaa le re kwaan nzhé ley cheen Dios zee sbaa zo xaa nali lo Dios; per nanet xaa wii xaa lo Jesucrist, xaa mzo Dios zee zo myet nali lo Dios;
nel Jesucrist mlozhaw rese kwaan nzhé ley, zee loka xaa wii lo Jesucrist le gan zo nali lo Dios.
Loka xaa nzhekla zo nali lo Dios kwent cheen ley kwaan mzaa Dios lo Ches, nzhaal le xaa kwaan nzhéya, nel snee mkee Ches: “Loka xaa nle rese kwaan nzhé ley, ban xaa nel mle xaa kwaan nzhé ley”.
Per loka xaa nzhekla zo nali lo Dios nzhaal wii xaa lo Dios. Kwaanzee nanzhaalt nii be: “¿Cho xaa yixoob yiba, kwaan nle zee yaad Jesucrist naz yizhyo?
o ¿cho xaa la naz lo re xaa ngut le zee roo Jesucrist naz baa?”
Kwaanzee lee Xkyech Dios nii: “Lee Wdizh Chul cheen Dios nzo gax roo lu nu leen lextoo lu”. Kwaane nak Wdizh Chul cheen Dios kwaan nzaa nu kwent.
Nel chelee lu kwaan roo lu mbezh lu lee Jesucrist nak Xaa Nabeyy lu, nu kwaan lextoo lu ne lu lee Dios mseban Jesucrist, zee le lu gan yalnaban kwaan tira.
Nel leezha nle lu krer kwaan dub lextoo lu lee Dios mseban Jesucrist, sbaa gak lu tub xaa nali lo xaa, nu leezha mbezh lu lee Jesucrist nak Xaa Nabeyy lu, zee le lu gan yalnaban kwaan tira.
Lee Xkyech Dios nzhé: “Loka xaa wii lo Jesucrist, natont xaa ne xaa Dios”.
Nel kwaane nak kwaan nzhé Xkyech Dios: “Rese xaa naab lo Xaa Nabeyy le xaa gan yalnaban kwaan tira”.
Per, ¿xomod naab xaa lo Dios chelee xaa nangwiit xaa lo xaa? ¿Nu xomod wii xaa lo xaa chelee xaa nankenzhat xaa xtizh Dios? ¿Nu xomod kenzha xaa xtizh Dios cheleeya nik tub xaa nazaat kwenta lo xaa?
¿Nu xomod zaa xaa kwent cheen wdizh chul lo stub xaa cheleeya nyent cho xaal xaa? Modxa nzhé Xkyech Dios: “¡Chul doo naka leezha nze tub xaa nzaa kwent cheen wdizh chul cheen Xaa Nabeyy!”
Per naret xaa nzaa yek gon wdizh chul. Modxa nzhé Chay lo Xkyech Dios: “Xaa Nabeyy, ¿cho xaa zaa yek gon wdizh chul kwaan nzaa nu kwent?”
Kwaanzee nik tub xaa nyent mod wii lo Jesucrist cheleeya nyent cho mzaa kwent cheen Jesucrist lo xaa.
Per, ¿cho kwaan nzak gu? ¿Che nambint re xaa wdizh chul? ¡Telisa mbin xaaya! Nel lee Xkyech Dios nzhé:Xaa dubse yizhyo mbin wdizh chul,axta pa mas zit lo yizhyo.
Nu bare na nabdizh na lo gu, ¿cho kwaan nzak gu? ¿Che namlat re kwaane yek re xaa Israel, xaa nak sawlazh na? Mlaya yek xaa nel yilo Ches mzaa kwent xtizh Dios, nu nzhé Dios:Na le zee gak gu selos xomod kanap na stub naz xaa,xaa nanakt xaa yezh ne;nu le na zee yii gu ne gu stub naz xaa,xaa nanlabeyyt na.
Nu noka Chay klar doo mkee xaa, leezha nzhé Dios:Lee re xaa kwaan nakakwaant na, nguzhal na lo xaa;nu mlu na lo re xaa nambezht na.
Nu Chay nzaa kwent cheen sawlazh na, mod nzhé Dios lo xaa: “Dubse zhe kabezh na gu, per nanzaat gu yek gu gon gu xtizh na nu mlaa gu na”.
Tira namlaat Dios xaa IsraelKwaanzee nanzheklat na nii na tira mlaa Dios re sawlazh na, xaa Israel. ¡Telisa namlaat Dios xaa! Nel mer na nak xaa Israel, dii cheen Abraham naz lad cheen Benjamín.
Nel axta yilo, mleey Dios re sawlazh na gak xaa xaa Dios; nu nal nalaat xaa xaa. ¿Che nselazh gu xomod nzaa Xkyech Dios kwent kwaan nzhé Li, xaa nzhé lo Dios nawent nak re xaa Israel? Nu nzhé xaa:
“Xaa Nabeyy, mbit xaa rese xaa nzaa kwent kwaan nzhé lu lo lee xaa, nu mlux xaa lo re mdo, pa nteed xaa ma lo lu. Nebse na mban, per noka na nzhekla re xaa gut.”
Per Dios mkeb lo xaa nu nzhé: “Natechot lu nak xaa nzo lo na, noka nkano na stub gazh mil xaa, xaa zer kichxub lo maj cheen dios Baal”.
Nu sbaaka nal nzho zlak sawlazh na nak xaa Dios, xaa mleey Dios kwaan yalnkela cheen Dios.
Nu chelee kwaane ngoka kwaan nebse yalnkela cheen Dios, nanaktraya nel mle xaa kwaan wen; nu chol ngaka nel mle xaa re kwaan wen, zee nangaktraya kwaan sbaasa nzelazh Dios.
Kwaan nzhekla na nii na nak, nanguzhalt kwaan kakwaan xaa sawlazh na lo xaa. Nixa sbaaya lee lak nu, xaa mleey Dios, nguzhala lo nu; per lee re stub naz sawlazh na Dios mle ngok ned lextoo xaa.
Modxa nzhé Xkyech Dios: “Dios mle ngok ned lextoo xaa, nu seetaka nak xaa axta mbizh nalzhe. Nel nixa nzho mod wii xaa re kwaan mle Dios nu nzho mod gon xaa re kwaan ngunii Dios, nanlat re kwaan mle Dios nu re kwaan ngunii Dios yek xaa.”
Noka David nzhé:Nzhekla na leezha kayaw xaa la xaa lo tub tramp,zee ralnii xaa nu ded xaa bid.
Nzhekla na zhib yizhchool zaalo xaa nunik stub kwaan nayuntra lo xaa,nu noka tira gak nalen tich xaa dubse mbizh mban xaa.
Lee yalnaban noka nak cheen re xaa nanakt xaa IsraelNal nzhekla na nii na, namralt nii re sawlazh na, xaa Israel tira, zee nayixchetra xaa. ¡Telisa yixche xaa! Mas wen leezha nambint re sawlazh na xtizh Dios, ngoka zee nzho mod kayaa re xaa nanakt Israel yalnaban kwaan tira, zee snee gak selos re sawlazh na ne re xaa nanakt xaa Israel.
Nu snee leezha mralnii re sawlazh na, xaa Israel, nu mlaa xaa Dios, zee mle xaa zee nzho mod mkayaa re myet yizhyo, xaa nanakt xaa Israel, re kwaan chul cheen Dios; per mas gro kwaan kayaa re xaa nanakt xaa Israel gorna gak rese xaa sawlazh na xaa Dios.
Per nal nii na lo re gu, xaa nanakt xaa Israel, nel Dios mxaal na lo re gu, kwaanzee nzak na non doo xchinn na,
nel nzhekla na lee re sawlazh na gak selos gorna wii xaa xomod mkayaa Dios re gu, nu snee zee nen che nzho mod le lak xaa gan yalnaban kwaan tira.
Nu cheleeya mlaa re sawlazh na Dios, zee snee nzho mod kwi wen re myet lo Dios, ¿cho kwaan gak gorna kayaa re sawlazh na Dios stuba? ¡Gak xaa mod xaa mroban lo yalgut!
Nel chelee pan kwaan mdexkwaa xaa yilo nak xcheen Dios, zee noka re kwaan dexkwaa gwluzh kwaan leeka koob gak xcheen Dios. Nu chelee re lox tub yag naka xcheen Dios noka re ram cheena nak xcheen Dios.
Wdizh nabix cheen yag olibNal za na tub kwent nabix lo gu. Dios mxeen tub yag olib chul, nu mas gwluzh mchoog xaa re ram cheena. Zee ngwa xaa naz wen nu mchoog xaa ram stub yag olib wen nu mkangeed xaa re ram ne lo xkyag olib xaa. Rese nu, xaa Israel, nak mod ram kwaan mchoog xaa yilo, nu rese gu nak mod re ram kwaan nkangeed xaa lo xkyag olib xaa. Kwaane nlu nkano gu re kwaan chul cheen Dios kwaan mkano re nu, xaa nak dii Israel, yilo.
Per nayét gu mas xwara gu lo re ram yag kwaan mchoog xaa. Bzelazh gu nel naleet gu nle zee mban loxa, sinka loxa nle zee mban gu, zee nyent mod to gu yalxwa.
Talbes nzhekla gu yé gu: “Lee re ram zee mroog, zee mla nu xlugara lo yag olib kwaan mxeen Dios”.
Nu wliya. Per lee xaa namwiit lo Dios nak mod re ram kwaan mroog, nu lee re gu ngwii lo Dios zee nak gu mod ram kwaan nkangeed xaa lox xkyag olib xaa. Kwaanzee natot gu yalxwa, mas wen bzheb gu.
Bwii, lee Dios nak tub xaa nlesdoola ne re myet. Nlesla xaa ne xaa gu chelee gu nze gu lo yalnkela cheen xaa, per nalestla xaa ne xaa rese xaa nanzhont xtizh xaa. Kwaanzee chelee gu nazet gu lo yalnkela cheen xaa, gak gu kwent ram kwaan mchoog xaa lo xkyag xaa.
Per stub lad, chelee re sawlazh na zelo xaa wii xaa lo Dios, bare Dios zob xaa lugar cheen xaa stub welt, nel Dios nkano yalnabeyy zob xaa xlugar xaa stub welt.
Nel chelee gu, xaa nanakt xaa Israel, mroog gu lo yag olib kwaan nzeb naz wen, nu nyaad gu ngyeed gu lo yag olib kwaan mxeen xaa (tub kwaan tira nanlet re myet), kwaanzee mas nzhora mod yeed re sawlazh na stuba, nel leeka xaa nak mer yag olib kwaan mxeen Dios.
Xomod le re xaa Israel gan yalnaban kwaan tiraWech nu bzan, nzhekla na ne re gu kwaane, tub kwaan xlaan kwaan le Dios, zee natot gu yalxwa. Lee re sawlazh na ngok ned lextoo nal, per kwaane kaded axta yilo gak re xaa nanakt xaa Israel, xaa Dios.
Nu gorna lee re xaa nanakt xaa Israel gak xaa Dios, zee rese sawlazh na le gan yalnaban kwaan tira, nel lee Xkyech Dios nzhé:Lee xaa zaa yalnaban kwaan tira yaad naz Sión,nu koo xaa re xinn Kob lo re kwaan nawent.
Nu kwaane nak wdizh kwaan laa na lo re xaa,gorna kiib na re jwalt cheen xaa.
Nu namkayaat re sawlazh na wdizh chul cheen Dios, snee ngok xaa xkontrad Dios. Nu snee ngoka, zee nzho mod lee re xaa nanakt Israel le gan yalnaban kwaan tira. Per seetaka nkela Dios re sawlazh na nel Dios mleey re xey nu, xaa yilo.
Nel kwaan nzelazh Dios, telisa nakiibt xaaya stub welt lo re xaa mrezh xaa gak xaa xaa.
Lee yilo, nambint gu xtizh Dios, per lee nal re sawlazh na nanzhont xtizh xaa, zee mlesla Dios ne re gu.
Nu nal lee re sawlazh na nanzhont xtizh Dios, per kwaane ngok zee lesla Dios ne re gu; nu zhin mbizh lesla Dios ne Dios re sawlazh na, xaa Israel, kwentaxa mlesla xaa ne xaa re gu.
Nel mlaa Dios rese myet zee nambint xaa xtizh xaa, zee nzho mod luu xaa yalnlesla cheen xaa lo rese myet.
¡Wen doo nak Dios! ¡Gro doo nak re yalnzhak cheen Dios, nu nlabeyy xaa rese kwaan! Nu nik tub xaa nyent mod zaa kwent cho kwaan le xaa, nu nixa nyent mod la yek re xaa xomod nak Dios.
Nel nyent cho nlabeyy re kwaan nle Dios xgab, nu nik tub xaa nyent mod seed Dios tub kwaan.
Nik tub xaa nyent mod zaa tub kwaan lo Dios nu kwaz kix Diosa stub welt.
Nel Dios mdexkwaa rese kwaan, nu nebse lee xaa nle zee nzhoya, nu snee zee tira naka xcheen xaa. ¡Tubka nzhaal gool be lo Dios rese mbizh! ¡Sbaa gaka!
Xomod nzhaal zo be lo DiosNu nii na, wech nu bzan, nel mlesla Dios ne re be, nzhaal zaa be dub be lo Dios; mod nteed xaa ma lo Dios. Kwaane nak tub gon nambey nu mban kwaan nzaa be lo Dios, nu snee nak mod nzhaal gool be lo Dios; nu kwaane nak kwaan nyula Dios.
Nu nalet be re kwaan nle re xaa yizhyo ne, sinka nzhaal laa be chee Dios re xgab cheen be, nu snee ne be xomod nak kwaan nle Dios xgab kwaan nak kwaan wen, kwaan nyula Dios, nu kwaan nali nak.
Nel nkela Dios na, zee mxaal xaa na kee na zhiin ne, kwaanzee naab na lo gu, nalet gu xgab lee gu xwa doo. Nel ngwii be lo Jesucrist, mas wen le be xgab mod tub xaa nzho yek.
Lee kwerp cheen myet nkano zyen doo pa, nu kad tub pa nkano tub zhiin nleya.
Nu sneeka, nixa zyen doo be, nak be mod tubka kwerp cheen Jesucrist, nu nkin be tub be stub be.
Dios mzelazh kwaan lo rese be, zee le xchiin beya lo zhiin cheen Dios, nu mzelazh xaaya kwentaxa nzhekla xaa. Nu chelee Dios mzelazh kwaane lo be zee zaa be kwent kwaan né xaa lo be, zee le xchiin beya konxa ngwii be lo Dios.
Per chelee Dios mzelazh lo be, le be yudar stub naz xaa, zee le beya. Loka be mkayaa lu be xtizh Dios, nzhaal luu beya.
Chelee be mkayaa be yalnzhak zaa be rason lo re wech nu lo re bzan, nzhaal zaa beya tub mod chul. Loka be mkayaa lo Dios zelazh be tub kwaan lo stub xaa, zelazh beya kwaan dub lextoo be. Cheleeya lo be mzaa Dios nabeyy be lo re xaa Jesús, nzhaal nabeyy be tub mod nali. Loka be mkayaa lesla be ne be re xaa nkin tub kwaan, le be yudar xaa kwaan dub lextoo be.
Kela be tub be stub be kwaan dub lextoo be. Laa be re kwaan nawent, nu reke be tich re kwaan wen.
Kela be tub be stub be mod nkela be re wech be nu re bzan be, nu le be xgab xwara stub be ke leeka be.
Kee be zhiin lo Xaa Nabeyy kwaan dub lextoo be nu nachaabt be.
Yakdoola be le be xgab kwaan nkambaz be; yela be ded be bid, nu tubka wdizhno be Dios.
Nu le be yudar re wech nu re bzan leezha nkin xaa tub kwaan. Nu chul kayaa be stub naz xaa zhin garli be nu zaa be tub pa kwaz xaa.
Naab be lo Dios kwent cheen re xaa nrenal be; nu nii be kwaan wen lo re xaa nge lo be.
Kwi chul be kwaan re wechxinn be. Natot be yalxwa nu nzhaal yeen be kwaan re xaa sbaasa, nixa natot be yalxwa lo re kwaan nzhak be.
Nazaret be tub kwaan nawent lo re xaa kwaan nawent nle lo be. Le be kwaan nzak rese myet nak kwaan wen.
Le be zee kwi chul be kwaan stub naz re xaa, axta paro nzho moda lo be.
Rese be wech nu bzan, nazeret be re kwaan nawent mle stub naz xaa lo be, nzhaal laa be naab Dios xkwent xaa. Modxa nzhé Dios lo Xkyech Dios: “Lee na nzhaal naab kwent; nu na zereya, né Xaa Nabeyy”.
Kwaanzee nazeret beya. “Chelee xaa nrenal lu nlaan, bzaa kwaan gaw xaa, nu chelee xaa nzhek lextoo xaa, bzaa nis go xaa; nu snee le gu zee ton xaa”.
Nalaat be le re kwaan nawent gan lo be, sinka le be re kwaan wen zee le be gan lo re kwaan nawent.
Nzhaal gon be xtizh re xaa nak zhiin, nel nebse Dios nzho mod zaa yalnabeyy lo xaa, nu Dios mle zee ngok xaa xaa nak zhiin.
Kwaanzee rese xaa nanzhont xtizh re xaa nak zhiin, noka nayii xaa ne xaa Dios, nel Dios mle zee ngok xaa xaa nak zhiin. Nu rese xaa nanzhont xtizh xaa, ted xaa xaa bid.
Nel re xaa nle kwaan wen nanzhebt xaa ne xaa xaa nak zhiin, per re xaa nle kwaan nawent nzheb xaa ne xaa xaa nak zhiin. Chelee be nzhekla be nazhebt be ne be re xaa nak zhiin, le be re kwaan wen, zee ne wen xaa be,
nel re xaa nak zhiin nak xmos Dios, zee le xaa yudar be. Per chelee be nle be kwaan nawent nzhaal zheb be ne be xaa nak zhiin, nel lee xaa nak xaa nabeyy, nu nted xaa bid re xaa nle kwaan nawent. Nel xchiin Dios nle xaa, zee nteed xaa bid re xaa kwaan nle kwaan nawent.
Kwaanzee nkin le be kwaan né re xaa nak zhiin, zee nateedt xaa be bid, nu nel nela be xana kwaan nzhaal le be.
Kwaanzee nzhaal kix be kwent cheen leyo lo re xaa nak zhiin nel lee xaa nak xaa mlaa Dios le zhiin ne.
Kix be lo kad tub xaa kwaan nzhaal yex lo. Kix be lo re xaa nak zhiin rese kwaan nzhaal kix be lo xaa; nu sbaaka nii be wdizh wen lo xaa nu lo re xaa nzhaal nii be wdizh wen lo; nu wii be respet lo re xaa, kwaan nzhaal wii be respet lo.
Nik tub kwaan nanzhaalt zeb be lo stub xaa. Per kwaan nzeb be nak yalnkela lo wechxinn be, nel loka xaa nkela wechxinn nle xaa rese kwaan nzhé ley.
Nel lo ley kwaan mzaa Dios lo Ches nzhé:Nakanot lu xngwnaa stub xaa,naguta lu wechxinn lu,nalewannt lu,nazoblazht lu.Re kwaane nu re stub naz kwaan mnabeyy Dios, nak tubka kwaane: “Bkela wechxinn lu mod nkela lu leeka lu”.
Loka xaa nkela nanlet xaa nik tub kwaan nawent lo wechxinn xaa, nu sbaa nle xaa rese kwaan nzhé ley.
Kwaanzee nkin le be re kwaane nel nela be xomod nak re mbizh nzho be nal; nkin roo mkaal lo be, nel mzhin gaxla mbizh leezha zaa Dios yalnaban lo be; nu nel mas mzhin gaxla mbizh nal ke leezha mbin be wdizh chul cheen Dios.
Nel nal merla mded yaal nu merla nguni yizhyo; kwaanzee nkin naletra be re kwaan mle be leezha mzo be lo yalnakaw; nkin gak be xab be, kwaan nak cheen Dios kwaan nla xni cho, mod tub soldad, xaa list nzo.
Kwaanzee le be kwaan wen modxa nle xaa zhe:nayat be yalni pa nle xaa rese kwaan nzhekla xkwerp xaa,nazuzht be,nachaalt be stub sa myet be,nadildiizht be,nazoblazht be.
Zo be gax lo Jesucrist zee gak be mod tub soldad xaa nkee yiib xuk, nu tira nalet be re kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen be.
Nagawyixt be wech be nu bzan beChul kayaa be re xaa nanyet nzo ngwii lo Dios, nu nagawyixt be xaa.
Nel tub naz xaa nzak nzho mod gaw xaa rese kwaan, nu lee stub naz xaa nanyet nzo lo re kwaan nak xcheen Dios, nanzhawt xaa baal, nebse re kwaan naye nzhaw xaa.
Kwaanzee lee re xaa kwaan nzhaw rese kwaan, nanzhaalt yé xaa, mas wenra xaa ke stub naz xaa nanzhawta. Nu lee re xaa kwaan nanzhawt rese kwaan, nanzhaalt yé xaa lee re xaa nzhaw rese kwaan nak xaa nawent, nel Dios mkayaala tub naz xaa stub naz xaa.
Nanzhaalt gawyix be wechxinn be, nel re be nak xmos Xaa Nabeyy, nu lee Xaa Nabeyy nak xaa nzho mod nabeyy xmos xaa, nu nanakta be. Nu telisa kayaa Xaa Nabeyy xmos xaa nel nzhak Xaa Nabeyy kanap xaa.
Nu nzho stub kwaan, nzho lak xaa nzak mas nonra tub mbizh ke stub mbizh, nu nzho zlak xaa nzak rese mbizh lal. Kad tub be nzhaal le xgab mod nzak be mas wenra.
Loka xaa ngozhaw tub mbizh, ngozhaw xaaya zee gool xaa lo Xaa Nabeyy. Nu loka xaa nzhaw rese kwaan, nzhaw xaaya nel nkela xaa Xaa Nabeyy nu nzaa xaa dixkix lo xaa. Nu loka xaa nanzhawt rese kwaan nle xaaya nel nkela xaa Xaa Nabeyy nu noka nzaa xaa dixkix lo xaa.
Nel nambant re be zee le be kwaan nzhekla be, nixa nayeta be nel nzhekla be.
Nel chelee be mban be, mban be zee kee be xchiin Xaa Nabeyy, nu chelee be yet be, yet be nel nzhekla Xaa Nabeyy yet be. Kwaanzee, chelee be mban be nu chelee be ngut be, xaa Xaa Nabeyy nak be.
Nel kwaanzee ngut Jesucrist nu mbare xaa mroban xaa stub welt, zee gak xaa Xaa Nabeyy lo re xaa mban nu lo re xaa ngut.
Nel lee Xkyech Dios nzhé:Mban na, né Xaa Nabeyy,rese myet kichxub delant lo na,nu rese myet gool lo Dios.
Kwaanzee sbaa, kad tub be zaa kwent cheen lo Dios.
Le be kwaan wen lo re xaa JesúsKwaanzee nagawyixt be tub be stub be. Wii be xana re kwaan nle be, zee nalet be zee ralnii stub be, zee laa xaa re xcheen Dios.
Kwaanzee mlu Jesucrist kwaane lo na nu lee xaa nak Xaa Nabeyy na; wena nzho mod gaw be rese kwaan, per chelee tub be nzak nawenta, nazhaalt gaw xaaya.
Per cheleeya kwaan nzhaw be nle zee nawent gak lextoo wech be, zee lee kwaan kale be nlu nankelat be xaa. Wii be xana re kwaan gaw be, zee nalet be laa wech be nu bzan be re xcheen Dios, nel noka ngut Jesucrist kwent cheen xaa.
Kwaanzee nalaat be nii xaa nawent kwaan nzak be wen nak, nel nzak xaa nawent mod nle be.
Kwaanzee leezha nabeyy Dios lextoo be, nanont kwaan nzhaw be nixa kwaan nzho be, kwaan non nak zo nali be lo Dios nu kwi chul be, zee yakla be nel lee Mbi Naban cheen Dios nzo kwaan be.
Loka xaa snee nzo lo Jesucrist, nyula Dios xaa nu noka re myet nyula xaa.
Kwaanzee nzhaal kwaan be zee chul kwi re be; zee snee nzho mod le be yudar tub be stub be, zee zo nyera rese be lo Dios.
Nanzhaalt lux be xchiin Dios lextoo stub be, nebse kwent cheen kwaan nzhaw be. Rese kwaan nzhaw xaa nak wen, lee kwaan nawent nak gaw be tub kwaan le zee ralnii stub wech be.
Mas wen nagawt be baal, nixa nagot be xis ub, nixa nalet be stub naz re kwaan, kwaan le zee ralnii stub be.
Lee mod nzak be lo kwaane, nebse nzhaal gaka tub kwaan lo be nu lo Dios. ¡Nix doo nzhak lextoo xaa kwaan kale kwaan wen!
Per lee xaa nzhaw tub kwaan nu nzak xaa nawent gaw xaaya, nle xaa jwalt nel nzak xaa nawent gaw xaaya. Nu loka kwaan nle be, chelee be nzak be nawent naka, jwalt naka lo be.
Nanzhaalt le be nebse kwaan nyula beRese be, xaa nye nzo lo re xcheen Dios, nzhaal yela be ne be re xaa nanyet tant nzo lo re xcheen Dios; nu nakwaant be kwaan nyula leeka be.
Rese be nzhaal le be kwaan nyula re wechxinn be, zee mas nyera zo xaa lo re xcheen Dios.
Nel nixa Jesucrist, namkwaant xaa le xaa re kwaan nyula xaa; nu re kwaan mle xaa nak kwaan nkee lo Xkyech Dios, leezha nzhé Dios: “Lee re wdizh nawent kwaan nii xaa lo lu noka ngunii xaaya lo na”.
Nel rese kwaan mkee xaa lo Xkyech Dios yilo mkeeya zee seed be; zee nzho mod yela be ded be re bid nu leeya seleyy be leezha nkambaz be gak re kwaan nguné Dios.
Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa nyedoola nu xaa nseleyy be, le yudar gu zee chul kwi gu kwaan re wechxinn gu, modxa mlu Jesucrist,
zee rese be kwaan tubka bos gool be lo Dios, xaa nak xuz Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be.
Pab mzaa kwent wdizh chul lo re xaa nanakt xaa IsraelKwaanzee, chul kayaa be re wechxinn be, modxa mkayaa Jesucrist be, zee zyen doo myet gool lo Dios.
Nii na lo gu, lee Jesucrist myaad mkee zhiin lo re sawlazh na, xaa Israel, zee gak rese kwaan nzhé xaa lo re xey nu, xaa yilo nu snee luu xaa lee Dios nak tub xaa wli lo re kwaan nii xaa.
Noka myaad xaa zee gool re xaa nanakt xaa Israel lo Dios nel mlesla xaa ne xaa xaa, modxa nzhé Xkyech Dios:Kwaanzee gol na lo lu delant lo re xaa dubse yizhyo,nu gol na wen nak lu.
Lee stub pa lo Xkyech Dios nzhé:Bill gu, re xaa nanakt xaa Israel,tubka kwaan re xaa nak xaa Dios.
Lee stub pa nzhé:Rese gu, xaa nanakt xaa Israel, bill gu lo Dios,bill re gu kwaan re myet lo Dios.
Nu noka Chay mkee:Lo dii cheen Isaí, xuz David,roo tub xaa nabeyy lo dubse yizhyo,nu lo lee xaa wii re xaa nanakt xaa Israel.
Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa zaa kwaan nkambaz be, le nix lextoo re gu zee chul kwi re gu, nel ngwii gu lo xaa, zee yela gu kwaz gu re kwaan nguné xaa zaa xaa lo be, nel nkano gu yalngezh cheen Mbi Naban lextoo gu.
Rese gu wech nu bzan, ne wen na lee gu nle kwaan wen, nu nkano gu yalnzhak, zee nzho mod seedra gu re wechxinn gu, xaa nagakt.
Per nzho rol pa namzhebt na mkee na klar doo kwaan nzhaal nii na lo gu, zee tira nayenlazht guya; sbaa mkee naya nel Dios mxaal na kee na zhiin ne lo yalnkela cheen xaa.
Mxaal xaa na, zee kee na zhiin lo Jesucrist, nu mxaal xaa na lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel. Kwaan nle na nak, za na kwent cheen wdizh chul, mod tub ngwleyy lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel zee nzho mod gak xaa mod tub gon nzhul lo Dios, tub kwaan mle Mbi Naban.
Kwaanzee nyent mod nii na stub kwaan cheleeya nanakta kwaan mle Jesucrist kwaan na, zee lee kwent kwaan nii na nu kwaan nle na, lee re xaa nanakt xaa Israel gon xtizh Dios,
nu lee re kwaan gro kwaan mle Mbi Naban kwaan yalngezh cheen xaa lo re xaa, mle Dios zee mbin xaa xtizh Dios. Nu snee nzho mod kaza na kwent cheen wdizh chul; mzelo na axta yezh Jerusalén nu mzhin na axta yezh Ilírico.
Kwaanzee nzhekla na za na kwent cheen wdizh chul pa zer gon xaa cho kwaan mle Jesucrist. Nel chelee na za na kwenta pa mbinla xaaya, zee gak na kwenta tub xaa za tub yoo tich simyent xcheen stub xaa.
Modxa nzhé Xkyech Dios:Gon re xaa kwaan nik tub welt zer ne cho nak Dios;nu laya yek re xaa kwaan nik tub welt zer gon cho nak Dios.
Pab nle xgab ya yezh RomaNzhekla na yal na lo re gu per lee xchinn na kale tras na, zee zeeraka yal na lo re gu.
Per nal, ngulola mgaan na xtizh Dios re yezh ne; nu nel nzha doo liin nzhekla na yal na lo gu,
nal nzhekla na ya na naz España, nu gorna ya na naz ba deed na Roma. Nu gorna zhin na lo gu, zee wdizh be chep, zee nen che nzho mod le gu yudar na ya na España.
Per nal ya na Jerusalén, yalaa na tub gon lo re xaa mle Jesús nambey, xaa nzho baa.
Nel lee re xaa yizhyo Macedonia nu yizhyo Acaya ngol lextoo re xaa mzaa xaa tub gon lo re xaa Jesús, xaa prob, xaa nzho yezh Jerusalén.
Nu myula re xaa mle xaaya. Nu wli nzeeb xaa kwaan lo re xaa Jesucrist, xaa sawlazh na, nel mzaa re nu kwent cheen wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel, kwaanzee nal nzhaal le xaa yudar re xaa Jesucrist, xaa Israel kwaan demi.
Kwaanzee gorna yilo le na zhiin ne, gorna yilo za na gon ne lo re xaa Jesucrist, xaa sawlazh na; zee roo na baa nu deed na lo re gu, zee ya na naz España.
Ne wen na gorna yal na naz baa, nzho mod le Jesucrist tub kwaan chul lo re gu.
Wech nu bzan, kwent cheen Jesucrist nu kwaan yalnkela kwaan nzaa Mbi Naban lo be, naab na lo gu zee tubka naab gu lo Dios zee kanap Dios na.
Naab gu lo Dios zee nayigat na lo re xaa kwaan nangwiit lo Jesucrist, xaa kwaan nzho yizhyo Judea, nu zee wen kayaa re xaa mle Jesús nambey, xaa Jerusalén, gon kwaan nzhano na.
Kwaanzee chelee Dios nzhekla, naab gu lo xaa zee chul gak lextoo na gorna zhin na lo re gu nu nzho mod kwaz na tub deskans lo re gu.
Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa nle zee chul kwi rese be, kanap rese gu. ¡Sbaa gaka!
Dix kwaan gwluzhNaab na lo gu zee chul kayaa gu bzan be Febe, nel lee me nkee zhiin lo re xaa Jesucrist yezh Cencrea.
Chul bkayaa gu me kwent cheen Xaa Nabeyy, mod nzhaal kayaa gu re xaa mle nambey Jesús. Nu ble gu yudar me loka kwaan nkin me, nel lee me nzhale yudar zyen doo xaa nu axta na mle me yudar.
Guzh gu “dix” kwent cheenta lo Priscila nu lo sa me Aquila, xaa nkee zhiin kwaan na lo xchiin Jesucrist.
Lee rop xaa ba mle yudar na leezha mer yet na nixa noka lee xaa mle ryez yet; nu natechot na nza na dixkix lo xaa, noka re xaa Jesús, re xaa nanakt xaa Israel nzaa dixkix lo xaa.
Nu noka sbaa guzh gu “dix” lo re xaa Jesucrist, xaa nkasa garli Priscila nu Aquila. Noka guzh gu “dix” lo xmig na wech Epeneto, xaa tant nkedoola na, xaa yilotlaka mwii lo Jesucrist yizhyo Asia.
Noka guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo Mari, me tant nzha doo mbizh nkee zhiin lo re gu.
Noka guzh gu “dix” lo rop sawlizh na, wech Andrónico nu wech Junias, xaa tubka ngu lozhyib kwaan na. Nu nlabeyy wen re xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist xaa, nu rop xaa ngok tub xaa Jesucrist mas yilo ke na.
Guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo xmig na wech Ampliato, xaa tant nkedoola na kwent cheen Xaa Nabeyy.
Guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo wech Urbano, xaa tubka nkee zhiin kwaan na lo xchiin Jesucrist, nu noka lo wech Estaquis, xaa nkedoola na.
Guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo wech Apeles, nel mle xaa gan lo preb ngwii xaa lo Jesucrist; nu noka lo re xaa nzho li wech Aristóbulo.
Guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo sawlizh na wech Herodión, nu lo re xaa Xaa Nabeyy, xaa nzho li wech Narcis.
Guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo bzan Trifena nu lo bzan Trifosa, me tant nkee zhiin lo Xaa Nabeyy. Noka guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo bzan be Pérsida, nel nkedoola re xaa Jesús me, tant kakee doo me xchiin Xaa Nabeyy.
Guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo wech Rufo, tub xaa non doo lo Xaa Nabeyy; nu noka lo xnaa xaa, me nzak na mod xnaa na.
Nu noka guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo wech Filólogo nu lo bzan Jul, nu noka lo Nereo, nu lo bzan xaa, nu lo Olimpas nu lo rese xaa mle nambey Jesús kwaan nzhi kwaan lee xaa.
Kad tub gu guzh “dix” lo re wech gu nu lo re bzan gu nu daw gu tub bit tagarlo tub xaa stub xaa tub mod nali. Nu noka rese xaa mle nambey Jesús nxaal “dix” lo re gu.
Rese gu wech nu bzan, naab na lo re gu zee zeen gu cho xaa nle zee nzhak rol gu, nu nle zee nralnii re xaa lo xcheen Xaa Nabeyy. Re xaa ne nanlet re kwaan mseed re gu. Bachii gu lo re xaa snee nak,
nel nankeet re xaa ne xchiin Jesucrist, lee re xaa kakwaan kwaan nyula leeka kwerp cheen xaa; nu kwaan re wdizh chul cheen xaa nkade xaa re xaa nanyet nzo lo Jesucrist.
Rese xaa nzho nee, ne lee re gu nak xaa nzhon xtizh Dios nu kwaanzee nyakla na; nu nzhekla na seed gu le gu rese kwaan wen, nu nalet gu re kwaan nawent.
Nu snee lee Dios, xaa nle zee chul nzhi re be, le zee le be gan lo Maxuu. Nzhekla na lee Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, luu re yalnkela cheen xaa lo gu.
Nxaal Timoteo “dix” lo re gu, xaa kwaan nkee rop nu zhiin. Noka Lus, nu Jasón, nu Sosípater, xaa nak xaa sawlizh na, nxaal re xaa “dix” lo re gu.
Na nak Tercio, xaa kakee xtizh Pab lo yech ne, nu noka na xaal na “dix” cheenta lo re gu kwaan le Xaa Nabeyy.
Noka wech Gayo nxaal “dix” lo gu. Nzhoo na garli xaa, nu ntache xaa garli xaa nzhak kult. Noka wech Erasto nxaal “dix” lo re gu, xaa nak tesorer yezh ne, nu wech be Cuarto nxaal “dix” lo re gu.
Nzhekla na lee Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, kanap rese gu. Sbaa gaka.
Re wdizh gwluzh kwaan nzholl Pab lo DiosGool be lo Dios, xaa kwaan nzho mod le zee nye zo re be lo xaa, modxa nza na kwent cheen Jesucrist. Kwaan nza na kwent nak kwaan mlu Dios lo be, tub kwaan ngulaan axta leezha zeeraka dexkwaa yizhyo.
Per nal mlu Dios lo be kwaan nzho yek Dios le Dios, nel snee mkeela re xaa yilo, re xaa mzaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa, zee labeyy rese xaa dubse yizhyoya. Kwaanzee Dios, xaa tubka mban, mnabeyy gak rese kwaane, zee wii re myet lo Jesús.
¡Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa nzhak rese kwaan, kayaa re wdizh chul nu gool re myet lo xaa, nal nu rese mbizh, kwent cheen kwaan chul kwaan mle Jesucrist!¡Sbaa gaka!
<font color=teal>Yech yilo kwaan mkee Pab lo re xaa yezh Corinto</font>Dix cheen PabNa nak Pab, nu Dios mrezh na zee mkayaa na yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, mod nzhekla xaa. Tubka kwaan wech Sóstenes,
kakee na yech ne lo re gu, xaa mle nambey Jesús, xaa nzho yezh Corinto. Dios mrezh gu, zee gak gu xaa xaa nu mle nambey xaa gu. Sbaaka mle xaa kwaan rese xaa xaa. Kwaanzee lee xaa nak Xaa Nabeyy be nu Xaa Nabeyy re xaa zee.
Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa nak Xuz be, nu Jesucrist Xaa Nabeyy be, luu xaa yalnkela cheen xaa lo re gu zee kwi chul rese gu.
Mlu Dios yalnkela cheen DiosTubka nza na dixkix lo Dios, nel mlu Dios yalnkela cheen xaa lo re gu nel xaa Jesucrist nak gu.
Kwaanzee mzelazh Dios re kwaan chul cheen xaa lo re gu, axta re wdizh kwaan nii gu nu re xgab wen kwaan nzho yek gu.
Zee snee lee wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist kwaan ngunii nu lo gu tira mla lextoo gu, mod tub kwaan wli.
Nu nik tub kwaan nanzhijwalt lo re gu, rese kwaan chul cheen Dios mzelazh xaa lo gu lepa nkambaz gu bare Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be.
Dios le zee zo gu nali lo xaa nal nu axta gwluzh, gorna bare Jesucrist Xaa Nabeyy be, zee nik tub xaa nyent mod gaazh tub kwaan tich re gu.
Dios nak tub xaa nali nu nle xaa rese kwaan né xaa. Nu lee xaa nak xaa mrezh be zee yo be tubka kwaan Xgann xaa, xaa nak Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be.
Jesucrist nak tubkaNal wech nu bzan, kwaan yalnabeyy cheen Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, naab na lo gu zee nadildiizht gu nixa narezhchot gu. Chul gu gu nu tubka lal ble re gu xgab.
Wech nu bzan, nii na kwaane nel re xaa li wech Cloé nguné lo na, lee re gu ndildiizh.
Nzhekla na nii na kwaane, nel lee lak re gu mbezh: “Lee nu nreke tich Pab”. Zlak gu mbezh: “Lee nu nreke tich Apolos”. Nu zlak gu mbezh: “Lee nu nreke tich Pér”. Nu zlak gu mbezh: “Lee nu nreke tich Jesucrist”.
¿Che chop nak Jesucrist?, o ¿che ngut na, Pab, lo krus kwent cheen gu? ¿O che mrubnis tub gu zee mlu nreke gu tich na?
¡Dixkix Dios namchubnist na zyen gu, nebse wech Crispo nu wech Gayo!
Nu snee nik tub xaa nyent mod yé, lee xaa mrubnis kwaan yalnabeyy cheen na.
Noka mchubnis na Estéfanas nu re xaa nzho garli xaa, per nanselazht na che mchubnisra na stub xaa.
Jesucrist nkano yalnzhak cheen DiosLo re xaa nya naz lo ki, lee kwent kwaan ngut Jesucrist lo krus kwent cheen be, nak tub kwaan nachan nzak re xaa, per lo re be kwaane nak yalngezh cheen Dios nu kwaan wli lo re be, xaa nzhola naz le gan yalnaban.
Modxa nzhé Dios lo xkyech xaa:Nalenont na yalnzhak cheen re xaa nzhak,nu le na nalata yek re xaa nzho yek.
¿Paro mlake re xaa nzhak nu re maestr nu re xaa nzhak nii chul? ¡Dios mlu nanont re yalnzhak cheen re xaa yizhyo ne!
Nel kwaan yalnzhak cheen Dios, mle xaa zee lee re xaa yizhyo nanglabeyyt lee xaa, kwaan yalnzhak cheen leeka re xaa yizhyo. Nu nzhekla Dios zelazh yalnaban kwaan tira lo re xaa ngwii lo xaa, nixa lee wdizh ne, kwaan nzaa nu kwent, nlu lo re myet mod tub kwaan nachan.
Per lee re sawlazh na, xaa Israel, nzhekla xaa ne xaa le Dios kwaan gro doo nu lee re xaa nanakt xaa Israel nkwaan yalnzhak,
per lee nu nzaa kwent cheen Jesucrist, xaa ngut lo krus. Kwaane nralnii re sawlazh na, nu lee re xaa nanakt Israel nzak tub kwaan nachan naka,
per lee re xaa mleey Dios, xaa nak sawlazh na o xaa nanakt xaa Israel, ne xaa Jesucrist nkano yalnzhak nu yalngezh cheen Dios.
Kwaanzee nzaa nu kwent, lee Dios mxaal Xgann xaa zee ngut xaa lo krus, nu kwaane nak yalnachan nzak re xaa yizhyo, per leeya nlu lee Dios wlipa nzhak; nu lee re xaa yizhyo nle xgab naka tub kwaan nlu nangezht Dios, per leeya nlu wlipa ngezh Dios.
Nalsi wech nu bzan, ble gu xgab xomod mzo gu leezha mrezh Dios gu: lakse gu nzhak doo mod nzhak xaa yizhyo ne, lakse gu mkano yalnabeyy, noka lakse gu ngok xaa non.
Per Dios mleey re xaa nagakt zee seton xaa re xaa nzhak, nu mleey xaa re xaa sbaasa zee seton xaa re xaa non.
Dios mleey re xaa nanlet re myet kas nu re xaa nanont yizhyo ne, zee nalenont Dios xgab kwaan nzho yek re xaa yizhyo ne.
Kwaanzee snee nik tub xaa natot yalxwa lo Dios.
Per leeka Dios mleey be zee zhaal be kwaan Jesucrist, nu sbaa nkano be yalnzhak cheen Dios, nu gak be nzhul lo xaa. Nu mloxcho xaa be lo yizhyo nu mloo xaa be lo yalgut.
Snee modxa nzhé Xkyech Dios:Chelee tub gu nzhekla to yalxwa,to gu yalxwa cheen Xaa Nabeyy be.
Wech nu bzan, leezha ngwa na ngunii na wdizh wli cheen Dios lo gu, nanguniit naya kwaan wdizh nagan nixa kwaan yalnzhak cheen myet yizhyo ne.
Nu leezha mzo na kwaan re gu, tubka mza na kwent cheen Jesucrist, nel xomod ngut xaa lo krus.
Gorna mzhin na lo re gu mzheb doo na nu nyentra jwers lo na,
zee leezha ngunii na mza na kwent, nanguniit naya kwaan yalnzhak cheen myet yizhyo ne, nixa kwaan wdizh gaya zee gon guya. Nel lee Mbi Naban nu yalngezh cheen Dios mle zee mlu kwaan gro lo re gu.
Kwaanzee ngwii gu lo Dios, per nanakta nel mbin guya kwaan yalnzhak cheen myet yizhyo ne, leeya nak nel mla yalngezh cheen Dios lo gu.
Mbi Naban nlu cho nak DiosPer kwaan yalnzhak nzhedizh nu lo re xaa nye nzo ngwii lo Dios, per nanakta yalnzhak yizhyo ne nu nixa nanakta yalnzhak cheen re xaa nabeyy yizhyo ne, kwaan nakladiizh lux.
Nzhedizh nu kwaan yalnzhak cheen Dios kwaan ngulaan, tub kwaan nzholaanla axta leezha zeeraka dexkwaa Dios yizhyo, nen xomod zaa xaa yalnaban kwaan tira lo be.
Kwaane nak tub kwaan nanlat yek re xaa nabeyy yizhyo ne, nel chol nglaya yek xaa, nangkeet xaa Xaa Nabeyy be lo krus.
Kwaanzee snee nzhé Xkyech Dios:Dios nkano re kwaan chul nu nzaa xaaya lo re xaa nkela xaa,re kwaan nik tub xaa zer ne lo,nu re kwaan nik tub xaa zer gonnu re kwaan nik tub xaa zer le xgab.
Per lee Dios mlu kwaane lo be kwaan Mbi Naban, nel Mbi Naban nlabeyy rese kwaane, axta re kwaan nzho yek Dios.
Nii na lo gu, nik tub xaa nanet cho xgab nzho yek stub xaa, nebse mbi naban cheen xaa ne cho xgab nzho yek xaa. Nu leeka snee nebse Mbi Naban cheen Dios ne cho kwaan nle Dios xgab.
Nu namkayaat be mbi cheen yizhyo ne, lee be mkayaa Mbi Naban cheen Dios, zee labeyy be re kwaan mzelazh Dios lo be.
Nii nu re kwaane kwaan wdizh kwaan mzaa Mbi Naban cheen Dios lo nu, nu naniit nuya kwaan yalnzhak cheen nu. Nu snee nzaa nu kwent re xcheen Dios lo re xaa nak xaa xaa.
Loka xaa nayot Mbi Naban cheen Dios lextoo, nyent mod la re kwaan nak cheen Mbi Naban yek xaa, nel lo lee xaa naka tub kwaan nawlit. Nu nyent mod laya yek xaa nel nanzhot xaa Mbi Naban lextoo xaa.
Per lee xaa kwaan nzho Mbi Naban lextoo xaa, nzho mod labeyy xaa rese kwaan wen nu nyent mod yé re myet nawent nak xaa.
Tubka nkee re be xchiin DiosWech nu bzan, nyent mod ngnii na lo gu mod tub xaa nye nzo lo re xcheen Jesucrist, lee na ngunii lo re gu mod tub xaa nyeen doo lo xcheen Jesucrist.
Mseed na gu kwenta madoo, mad nzho nizh, nel nyent mod gaw gu kwaan nzhaw xaa gro. Noka nal seesa nkin za na nizh go gu,
nel seetaka nak gu mod tub madoo. ¿Chozhiin nkano gu re xgab yizhyo ne nel seetaka nzoblazh gu, nu nayii gu ne gu tub gu stub gu? Nlu seetaka nak gu kwenta xaa yizhyo ne nel kwenta xaa yizhyo ne nle gu,
leezha mbezh gu: “Na nreke tich Pab”, nu zlak gu mbezh: “Na nreke tich Apolos”, mod myet yizhyo ne nzhedizh gu.
Ble wen gu xgab, ¿cho nak na?, ¿cho nak Apolos? Nebse nak nu mos, xaa mle zee mbin gu xtizh Xaa Nabeyy. Kad tub nu nle zhiin kwaan mzaa Xaa Nabeyy kee nu.
Nal za na kwent xomod naka; leezha mza na kwent xtizh Dios lo gu, naka mod mlo na bizh lo yo; nu leezha mseed Apolos gu, naka mod mzoog xaaya, per Dios nak xaa nle zee mxena.
Nu kwaanzee lee xaa ngo bizh lo yo nu xaa nzooga nak tub xaa nanont, per Dios nak xaa non nel lee xaa mle zee mxena.
Kwaanzee lee xaa ngo bizh lo yo nu xaa nzooga lal non xaa nu lal nak xgab cheen xaa, nu Dios kix kad lo tub xaa, lo zhiin kwaan mle xaa.
Tubka nkee rop nu xchiin Dios. Nak nu mos, xaa nkee zhiin lo Dios, nu gu nak kwenta yizhyo kwaan nkee Dios zhiin.Nal za na stub kwent nen xomod nak gu mod tub yoo kwaan kaza Dios.
Nu Dios mzaa yalnzhak lo na zee nak na kwenta maestr lo re xaa ndexkwaa yoo. Na mzob simyent nu stub xaa za duba. Per kad tub xaa nkin wii xaa nen xomod za xaaya,
nel nik tub xaa nyent mod zob stub simyent, nel nzobla kwaan nak Jesucrist.
Nu tich simyent ne nzho mod dexkwaa be tub yoo kwaan or o kwaan plat o kwaan ke kwaan chul nzhak o kwaan tab o kwaan goob o kwaan yixyi;
per lee xchiin kad tub be gakbeyy mbizh gwluzh; nel mbizh zee, xaal Dios ki nu lee ki le preb zhiin kwaan mle kad tub be.
Chelee tub be mdexkwaa tub yoo nu nangukta lo ki, kayaa xaa kwaan zaa Dios lo xaa.
Per chelee yoo kwaan mdexkwaa be nguka, zee luux kwaan mkano be, per Dios koo be lo ki.
Noka re gu nzhaal ne, be nak mod yidoo cheen Dios nu lee Mbi Naban cheen Dios nzho lextoo re be.
Nu chelee tub xaa lux yidoo cheen Dios, Dios lux xaa zee, nel lee yidoo cheen Dios nak tub kwaan nali, nu yidoo cheen Dios nak re be.
Nakadet gu leeka gu; nu chelee tub gu nzak gu nzhak gu re kwaan yizhyo ne, ble gu mod tub xaa nanlabeyyt kwaan yizhyo ne, zeesi zaa Dios yalnzhak lo gu.
Nel lee yalnzhak cheen myet yizhyo ne nak tub kwaan nachan lo Dios. Nel sbaa nzhé Xkyech Dios: “Leeka lo yalnzhak cheen xaa nzen Dios xaa”.
Nu noka nzhéya: “Lee Xaa Nabeyy nela, lee re xgab cheen re xaa nzhak, nak tub kwaan nanont”.
Kwaanzee nik tub gu natot yalxwa nel nreke gu tich kwaan nlu tub xaa non lo gu, nel rese kwaane nak cheen re gu:
kwaan mseed na gu, kwaan mseed Apolos gu, kwaan mseed Pér gu, yizhyo, yalnaban, yalgut, kwaan nzho nal, nu kwaan yo gwluzh, rese kwaane nak cheen re gu,
gu nak xaa Jesucrist, nu Jesucrist nak xaa Dios.
Xchiin re xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo JesucristKwaanzee nzhaal wii re gu lo nu nebse mod xmos Jesucrist, nel lee xaa mlaa zhiin ne lo nu, zee nseed nu re myet re kwaan ngulaan, kwaan mzaa Dios lo re myet nal.
Nu loka tub xaa kayaa tub zhiin, nzhaal le xaa zhiin mod nzhaal le xaaya.
Per lee na, nik tik nyent cho nzhak lextoo na, naab re gu kwent lo na o kwalkyer tub re xaa nak zhiin, nel nixa na nanaabt na kwent lo na.
Nel ne na wen nkee na xchiin Dios per nanont kwaan nzak na, nel Xaa Nabeyy nak xaa naab kwent lo na.
Kwaanzee nanaabt gu kwent nal, blaz gu yaad Xaa Nabeyy, zee luu xaa klar re kwaan nzho lo yalnakaw zee gakbeyy re xgab cheen re myet. Zee lee Dios nii kwaan chul lo kad tub xaa konxa nzhaal kayaa xaaya.
Wech nu bzan, nii na kwaane lo gu zee ne gu xomod nak xchiin Apolos nu xomod nak xchinn na. Nii na kwaane zee le gu mod nle nu, nu nalet gu kwaan nankeet lo Xkyech Dios, zee nik tub gu natot yalxwa lo tub xaa nu yé gu nawent stub xaa.
Nu nal nzak gu rikla gu, nkano gu rese kwaan nzoblazh tub xaa, nu nzak gu nak gu kwenta rey nu nankintra gu nu. ¡Wena chol rey ngak gu zee nzho mod nabeyy gu tubka kwaan nu!
Nel ne na lee nu, xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, nak tub xaa tira nanont lo re myet yizhyo ne, xaa nakladiizh yet; nu nak mod tub xaa lach re xaa yizhyo ne lo nu noka re mandad cheen Dios.
Nu nel nkela nu Jesucrist zee mbezh re xaa nachan nu, nu lee gu nzak nkela gu Jesucrist nu mbezh re xaa list gu. Gu nzak lee nu nak xaa nangezht nu lee gu nak xaa ngezh doo, nu nayii re myet ne nu, nu nkela re xaa gu.
Axta mbizh ne, lee nu tubka nded yalnlaan, yizhnzhek, nyent ler gak nu, nzaa re xaaya yenn nu, nankanot nu tub li nu,
nu nyazha nu nkee nu zhiin kwaan yaa nu. Nu leezha nge re xaa lo nu, zee naab nu lo Dios kwent cheen xaa; nrenal re xaa nu, nu nyela nu.
Nzhedizh nawent re xaa nu, lee nu naab lo Dios zee yo wen re xaa. Mod yix wen re xaa, nu mod tub kwaan nyent sirb. Nu snee nle xaa nu axta mbizh nalzhe.
Nakakeet na kwaane zee ton gu, lee na kakeeya zee za na tub konsej lo gu, mod xiin na, nel nkedoola na re gu.
Kwaanzee chol nkano gu tub chii mil maestr, xaa nzaa kwent cheen Jesucrist lo gu, per nankanot gu zyen xuz gu. Nu na nak kwenta xuz gu, nel ngok gu xinn Dios leezha mza na kwent cheen wdizh chul lo gu.
Kwaanzee naab na lo gu ble gu mod nle na.
Xaal na Timoteo lo gu. Nu lee xaa nak kwenta xgaan na, nel na nak xaa mzaa kwent cheen Xaa Nabeyy lo xaa. Le xaa selazh gu xomod nle na re kwaan, nel na nak tub xaa Jesucrist, modxa nlu na re kwaane lo rese xaa Jesús paro nzha na.
Lee lak gu nto yalxwa nel nzak gu nayalt na lo gu;
per chelee Xaa Nabeyy nzhekla, kwalkyer stub mbizh ne yal na lo re gu. Zee ne na nen che nzho yalnabeyy cheen Jesucrist lo re xaa nto yalxwa, o che nebse nii xaaya.
Nanakt xaa xaa Dios nel xwa nzhedizh xaa, per nak xaa xaa Dios cheleeya nzho yalngezh cheen Mbi Naban cheen Dios lextoo xaa.
¿Che nzhekla gu yal na zee teed na gu bid o yal na tub mod nadoo lo gu?
Nzhaal koo gu xaa nchaal stub ngwnaa lo re guNzhedizh re xaa, lee tub gu nchaal leeka sa xuz. ¡Nu kwaane nak tub kwaan tira nawent, nixa re xaa nanakt xaa Jesucrist nanlet kwaane!
Nu zeesi nto doo gu yalxwa, per nzhaal gak nales lextoo gu. Nzhaal koo gu xaa nle kwaane lo re gu.
Chol lo re gu nzo na, naab na kwent lo xaa sbaa nle. Per lee xgab cheen na nzo kwaan gu, nu kwaanzee ngulola mnaab na kwent lo xaa.
Nu gorna lee re gu kasa, naab gu kwent lo xaa ne, na zo kwaan re gu kwaan re xgab cheen na, nu noka yalnabeyy cheen Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, zo kwaan re gu.
Gorzee nzhaal zaa gu xaabyi ne lo yalnabeyy cheen Maxuu, zee luux re kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen xaa, zee lee xaa le gan nya naz yiba, zhe bare Jesucrist.
Nawent to gu yalxwa lo kwaan nawent ne, nel mod lebadur naka. Nela gu xomod nii xaa: “Chepse lebadur ntexoob dubse koob”.
Kwaanzee bloo gu lebadur kwaan nkanola gu naz jwer, kwaan ntexoob koob, zee gak gu pan kwaan mdexkwaa kwaan koob kub nu koob kwaan nyent lebadur, kwaane nak re gu. Nel Jesucrist, xaa nak mbakxiil cheen yalni Paskwa, mteedla xaa lo Dios kwent cheen be.
Kwaanzee nzhaal le be yalni Paskwa, tub mod wen nu nzhul, kwaan nak mod pan kwaan nanyut lebadur, nu nalet beya kwaan re kwaan nawent nu re kwaan nanambeyt, kwaan nak mod lebadur yilo.
Lo stub yech cheen na mkee na lo gu, nanzhaalt zhaal gu kwaan re xaa kwaan nchaal stub naz sa myet.
Nu leezha ngunii na kwaane, nanzheklat na ngnii na, zee nazhaalt gu kwaan rese xaa nle kwaan nawent yizhyo ne, xaa nchaal stub naz sa myet, xaa nzoblazh, xaa nlewann, xaa ngwii lo maj, nel chelee gu nzhekla gu le gu kwaan ba, chol sbaa naka nzhaal tira roo gu lo yizhyo ne.
Kwaan nzhekla na nii na nak: Nazhaalt gu kwaan tub xaa mbezh nak xaa Jesús nu nle kwaane, xaa nchaal stub ngwnaa, xaa nzoblazh, xaa ngwii lo maj, xaa nii nawent, xaa nzuzh, xaa nlewann. Rese myet, xaa nle kwaane, nixa nazobt gu gaw gu kwaan lee xaa.
<sup>(12-13)</sup> Kwaanzee nanzhaalt naab na kwent lo re xaa nanakt xaa Jesús, Dios nak xaa naab kwent lo re xaa ne. Per re gu nzhaal naab kwent lo re xaa nak xaa Jesús, kwaanzee nzhaal koo gu xaa nle kwaan nawent ne lo re gu.
(-)
Nanzhaalt gaazh be tub kwaan tich tub be lo stub xaa nanakt xaa JesúsNu leezha lee tub re gu nzhekla gaazh tub kwaan tich stub gu, ¿chozhiin nya gu lo re xaa nak zhiin, xaa nanalit nzo lo Dios? ¿Chozhiin nanzaat gu kwenta leeka lo re xaa Jesús, re xaa nambey?
¿Che nanet gu lee re xaa Jesús nak xaa naab kwent lo re myet lo dubse yizhyo? Nu cheleeya gu naab kwent lo re myet dubse yizhyo, ¿chozhiin nyent mod naab gu kwent lo leeka tub gu stub gu lo tub kwaan sbaasa?
Nu kwaanzee, chelee tub re gu nzhekla gaazh tub kwaan tich stub gu, ¿chozhiin ya gu zaa gu kwent kwaan mle xaa lo tub xaa nanakt xaa Jesús?
¡Nii na kwaane zee ton gu! ¿Cheleeya nyent nik tub xaa nzhak lo gu, xaa nzho mod gak jwes?
¡Per lee re gu, leezha gaazh gu tub kwaan tich stub gu, tira nya gu nu nzaa gu kwenta lo xaa nak zhiin, tub xaa nanakt xaa Jesús!
Nle gu tub jwalt ngaazh gu tub kwaan tich stub gu. ¿Chozhiin nayetla gu? ¡Mas wen laa gu lewann xaa gu!
¡Per lee re gu rese kwaan rebes nle gu, nawent nle gu nu nlewann gu leeka lo stub gu!
¿Che nanet gu rese xaa nakap nyent mod zeeb pa nabeyy Dios? Nalaat gu kade xaa gu,nel lee re xaa nchaal stub ngwnaa,xaa ngwii lo maj,xaa nchaal leeka sa byi,
xaa nlewann,xaa nzoblazh,xaa nzuzh,xaa nzhedizh nawent stub xaa,xaa nkade,nik tub re xaa nle re kwaane, narept pa nabeyy Dios.
Nu snee nak re gu yilo, per nal nzhula nzo gu lo re jwalt, nebse xaa Dios nak gu, mbyiibla re jwalt cheen gu nel mwii gu lo Jesús, Xaa Nabeyy be, nu nel nzho Mbi Naban cheen Dios lextoo gu.
Xomod nzhaal kano nzhul be kwerp cheen beMbezh re xaa: “Libr na, nzho mod le na kwaan nzhekla na”. Wli libr nak gu per naret kwaan nzhaal le gu. Libr na, per nalaat na lee kwerp cheen na nabeyy lo na zee leya kwaan nzheklaya.
Mbezh re xaa: “Lee kwaan gaw na, gaw naya nel naaba lextoo na”. Wliya, per ropse kwaane lux Dios. Kwaanzee lee kwerp cheen be namzaat Dios lo be zee leya re kwaan nawent, mzaa xaaya lo be zee gaka cheen Xaa Nabeyy nu lee Xaa Nabeyy nkanapa.
Nu sbaa modxa mseban Dios Xaa Nabeyy be, sbaaka seban Dios be kwaan yalngezh cheen xaa.
¿Che nanet gu lee kwerp cheen gu noka nak tik kwerp cheen Jesucrist? Kwaanzee nyent mod chaal na xkwerp na kwaan stub ngwnaa, me nto cho. ¡Telisa nalet naya!
¿Che nanet gu leezha lee tub xaa nchaal stub ngwnaa, me nto cho, tubka nzhak xkwerp xaa kwaan lee me? Nel lee Xkyech Dios nzhé: “Leezha zhaal rop xaa gak xaa tubka kwerp”.
Per leezha lee tub xaa nreke tich Xaa Nabeyy, nzhak xaa tubka kwaan Xaa Nabeyy.
Kwaanzee nachaalt gu stub myet, me nanakt sa gu. Chelee tub xaa nle stub kwaan nawent, nyent cho gak kwerp cheen xaa; per lee xaa kwaan nchaal stub myet, nle xaa tub kwaan nawent lo leeka xkwerp xaa.
Nzhaal ne gu lee kwerp cheen be nak yidoo cheen Mbi Naban cheen Dios, xaa mzaa Dios lo be, nu lee Mbi Naban nzho lextoo be. Kwaanzee lee xkwerp be nanakta cheen be, leeya nak cheen Dios,
nel kar doo mzi Dios be. Kwaanzee rese kwaan le be lo xkwerp be, nzhaal gaka kwaan nyula Dios.
Pab nzaa kwent cheen yalnchelyaLee nal keb na re kwaan mnabdizh gu lo na lo yech kwaan mkee gu. Per na nii: Mas wen nachelyat xaa;
per nel zyen doo xaa nchaal stub myet, me nanakt sa xaa, kwaanzee kad tub xaa nzhaal kano xaa xngwnaa xaa nu kad ngwnaa nzhaal kano me xmbyi me.
Konxa xaabyi nu konxa ngwnaa nzhaal zaa xaa xkwerp xaa lo sa xaa.
Nel lee kwerp cheen ngwnaa nanakta cheen me, nel cheen xmbyi me naka; nu lee kwerp cheen xaabyi nanakta cheen xaa nel cheen xngwnaa xaa naka.
Kwaanzee nawent yen gu xkwerp gu lo sa gu. Per nzho moda, cheleeya ropse gu yaan nazhaalt gu lak mbizh, zee wdizhno gu Dios. Zeera nzhaal zhaal gu stub welt, zee nyent mod le Maxuu gan lo gu zee le gu kwaan nawent.
Kwaane nii na lo gu mod tub xgab cheen na, cho kwaan nzhaal le gu, per nanakt kwaan mxaal Xaa Nabeyy le be.
Na nzhekla rese gu zo kwenta na, xaa nankanot sa. Per ne na, Dios mzaa lo tub naz be zee kano be sa be, nu mzaa xaa lo stub naz be zee chul yo techosa be.
Lee lo re xaa zer chelya nu lo re byud nii na, mas wen nachelyat gu, zee gak gu kwenta na.
Per chelee gu nayet gu nachelyat gu, mas wen chelya gu ke le gu kwaan nawent nchaal gu sa myet gu.
Per lee lo re xaa mchelyala, nabeey na kwaane kwaan nanakt cheen na, kwaane nak cheen Xaa Nabeyy: Lee ngwnaa nanzhaalt laa me xmbyi me.
Per chelee tub ngwnaa laa xmbyi, nyentra mod chelya me kwaan stub xaabyi, per nzho mod bare me kwaan xmbyi me stub welt. Nu leeka snee, lee xaabyi nanzhaalt laa xaa xngwnaa xaa.
Per kwaan xtizh na nii na lo gu, nu nanakt kwaane xtizh Xaa Nabeyy: Chelee xngwnaa tub xaa Jesús, nanakt me tub me ngwii lo Jesús, per wen nzho me kwaan lee xaa, nanzhaalt laa xaabyi me.
Nel lee xaabyi, xaa nangwiit lo Jesús, nambey xaa nel xngwnaa xaa nak tub me ngwii lo Jesús; nu lee ngwnaa, me nanakt tub me ngwii lo Jesús, nambey me nel xmbyi me nak tub xaa ngwii lo Jesús. Nel chol nanakta snee, zee lee re xinn xaa o xinn me gak xaa nanzhult, per kwaan wlipa nak, nambey xinn xaa.
Per chelee ngwnaa o xaabyi, xaa nangwiit lo Jesús, nzhekla laa sa, nzho mod le xaaya. Nu snee lee ngwnaa o xaabyi, xaa ngwii lo Jesús, nzho mod laa xaa o laa me nya sa me, nel Dios mrezh xaa zee chul yo xaa.
Kwaanzee bzan na, nyent mod ne lu che zkoo Dios xmbyi lu lo yalgut. Nu noka gu wech na, nyent mod ne lu che zkoo Dios xngwnaa lu lo yalgut.
Per kad tub gu yo mod mzaa Xaa Nabeyy diizh yo gu, mod nzho gu gorna mrezh xaa gu, nu kwaane nii na lo rese xaa Jesús.
Chelee Dios mrezh tub gu, xaa nzho beyy cheen re nu, xaa Israel, nakacht guya, o chelee Dios mrezh tub gu, xaa nanzhot beyy, nanzhaalt koo gu beyy cho gu.
Nel lee kwaan non nak, gon be xtizh Dios nexa chol nzho be beyy o nanzhot be beyy.
Kad tub be nzhaal gak mod nak be leezha mrezh Dios be.
Kwaanzee chelee tub be, leezha mrezh Dios be, nak be tub mos, nalet be xgab, per cheleeya nzho mod laa be nagaktra be mos, nzhaal laa beya.
Kwaanzee lee xaa nak mos leezha mrezh Dios xaa, nal nak xaa tub xaa mla nzho mod kee xaa zhiin lo Xaa Nabeyy; nu lee xaa nanakt mos leezha mrezh Dios xaa, nal nak xaa tub mos cheen Jesucrist.
Kar doo mzi Dios be, kwaanzee nalaat be le stub xaa be mod tub mos stuba.
Kwaanzee wech nu bzan, kad tub be nzhaal gak be mod nak be leezha mrezh Dios be.
Chelee tub xaa nzhekla chelya o nachelyat xaa, nik tub kwaan nanabeyyt Dios kwent ne; per nii na xgab cheen na lo gu, nu nali nzo na lo Dios, nel mlesla Dios ne na.
Nzak na: Lee xaa nanchelyat, nzhaal lake xaa mod nzo xaa nal, nel kaded be bid nal, kwaanzee mas wen nachelyat be.
Chelee be nkano be xngwnaa be, nalaat be me; nu chelee be nankanot be me nakwaant be me.
Per chelee be chelya be tub ngwnaa, nanlet be tub kwaan nawent, nu chelee tub ngwnaa chelya noka nanlet me kwaan nawent. Per xaa nkano sa ropse xaa ded bid, kwaan nzhekla na nak nadedt be bid.
Wech nu bzan, kwaan nzhekla na nii na lo gu nak: Lee mbizh mzhin gaxla. Kwaanzee lee re xaa nkano ngwnaa, nzhaal kee xaa zhiin lo Dios mod tub xaa nankanot ngwnaa.
Lee re xaa nzho bel, nzhaal kee xaa zhiin lo Dios mod tub xaa nanzhonnt, lee re xaa nyakla nzhaal kee xaa zhiin lo Dios mod tub xaa nanyaklat, nu lee re xaa nzi kwaan, nzhaal kee xaa zhiin lo Dios mod tub xaa nanakta xcheen.
Nu lee re xaa chul nzho yizhyo ne, nzhaal kee xaa zhiin lo Dios mod tub xaa nanont re kwaan chul yizhyo ne lo, nel nela be lee yizhyo ne lux.
Na nzhekla zee nalet gu xgab. Lee re xaa nankanot ngwnaa, nyakla xaa nkee xaa zhiin lo Xaa Nabeyy nel nkela xaa Xaa Nabeyy.
Per lee xaa nkano ngwnaa, nkwaan xaa re kwaan yizhyo, zee chul yo rop sa xaa,
nu snee nzhak chop xgab cheen xaa. Nu sneeka lee ngwnaa, me nankanot sa, nu me tira namkat xaabyi, nyakla me nkee me zhiin lo Xaa Nabeyy, zee dubse me gak nebse cheen Dios. Per lee re me nkano sa, nkwaan me re kwaan yizhyo, zee chul yo rop sa me.
Nanzheklat na zhiib na tub kwaan nga tich gu, nii na kwaane zee wen yo gu nu nadedt gu bid. Nu nii naya, zee yo gu tub mod nali nu kee gu zhiin lo Xaa Nabeyy kwaan dub lextoo gu.
Nu chelee tub xaa nzak nzhaal chelya rop xaa me nakladiizh chelya xaa, nakalet xaa tub kwaan nawent, nu nel nzhola me liin kwaan nzhaal chelya me. Nu chelee xaa nzak xaa kwaane nak kwaan nzhaal le xaa, nzho mod le xaaya. Nzho mod chelya gu, nel yalnchelya nanakta tub kwaan nawent.
Per chelee stub xaa nzak mas wen nachelyat xaa, nu nik tub xaa nanzhaalt le jwers lo xaa zee chelya xaa. Chelee xaa nzak xaa nzho mod nabeyy xaa xkwerp xaa, kwaanzee nanzhaalt chelya xaa, xaa ne nle kwaan wenra.
Kwaanzee chelee xaa chelya xaa kwaan me gak sa xaa, me nkela xaa, wena; per chelee xaa nzak xaa mas wen nachelyat xaa, wenra nle xaa.
Lee ngwnaa me nkano sa, nzhaal gak me nali lo sa me dubse mban xaa; per chelee xaa yet xaa, me ne nak tub me libr, nzho mod ka me stub xaabyi kwaan nzhekla me, per nzhaal gaka kwaan tub xaa Jesús.
Per nzak na nza na kwent kwaan mzaa Mbi Naban lo na leezha nii na, chulra yo me chelee me nachelyat me stuba.
¿Che nzho mod gaw xaa baal kwaan mded lo maj?Lee nal za na kwent cheen che nzho mod gaw xaa baal, ma kwaan mteed xaa lo maj. Nela beya: “Rese be nela xomod naka”. Per nzhekla na selazh guya: “Lee yalnzhak le zee to xaa yalxwa, nu lee yalnkela le zee mas nye zo xaa lo Dios”.
Chelee tub xaa nzak nzhak doo xaa, zeraka ne wen xaaya mod nzhaal ne xaaya.
Lee nal za na kwent, che wen gaw xaa baal kwaan mteed xaa lo maj. Ne be lee maj nak tub kwaan nawlit nak Dios nel tubka Dios nzho.
Kwaanzee nixa nzak re myet zyen dios nzho naz yiba nu naz yizhyo, (nu wlipa nzho zyen kwaan nzhekla gak Dios nu nzhekla nabeyy),
per lo re be nzho tubka Dios, xaa nak Xuz be, xaa mdexkwaa rese kwaan nu be nak xaa xaa. Noka nzho tubka Xaa Nabeyy be, Jesucrist, xaa mdexkwaa rese kwaan nu leeka lee xaa mle zee mban be.
Per naret xaa ne kwaane. Lak gu mbill lo re maj yilo nu leezha nzhaw gu re ma mteed xaa lo maj, nzak gu nzhaw gu tub kwaan nak cheen tub dios. Nel lee xgab cheen gu nangezht, zee nzhak chop yek gu.
Per nalet kwaan nzhaw be nle zee nyula Dios be, nel nagakt be mas xwara nel nzhaw be tub kwaan, nixa nagakt be xwara nel nanzhawt beya.
Per wii gu napa kale gu kwaane, zee lee re xaa nanyet nzo lo Dios kale tub kwaan nawent.
Nel chelee gu, ne gu re kwaane, nu nzob gu nzhaw gu paro nteed xaa ma lo tub maj, nu chelee tub wech gu, xaa nanyet nzo lo Dios, ne lee gu kayaw baa, talbes noka lee xaa le kwaan mle gu, nu gaw xaa baal kwaan mded lo maj. Per naz leen lextoo xaa nzak xaa naka tub kwaan nawent,
nu zee lee re kwaan mle gu, mle zee mluux mod ngwii wech gu lo Jesús; xaa nanyet nzo lo Dios. Nu bselazh gu noka ngut Jesucrist kwent cheen lee xaa.
Nu leezha nchep gu xgab nawent ne yek re wech gu nu re bzan gu, xaa nanyet nzo lo xcheen Dios, nle gu tub jwalt lo Jesucrist.
Kwaanzee, chelee kwaan nzhaw na nle zee nralnii tub wech na o tub bzan na lo xcheen Dios, mas wen nagawtra na baal, zee nalet na ralnii xaa lo xcheen Dios.
Nanaabt Pab kwaan nzhaal kayaa PabLee na nak xaa libr. Na mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, nu na ngune lo Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be. Nu mod ngwii rese gu lo Xaa Nabeyy, nlu mreke xchinn na.
Chelee stub xaa nanzheklat zaa yek gon lee na nak tub xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, per nzhaal ne re guya, nel gu nlu lee na nak tub xaa zee.
Kwaane nak kwaan nkeb na lo re xaa nawent nzhedizh na.
Nkano nu derech naab nu kwaan gaw nu nu kwaan go nu lo gu.
Nu noka nkano nu derech wee nu tub sa nu, xme Xaa Nabeyy, mod nle re stub naz xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, kwenta Pér nu kwenta re wech Xaa Nabeyy.
¿O che nebse na nu Bernabé nzhaal le nu gan kwaan gaw nu lo xchiin nu?
Nik tub soldad nankeet zhiin lo leeka lee xaa; nu nixa nik tub xaa nxeen tub xan yag ub, nu nanzhawt xaa ub kwaan nzaa yag; nu nixa nik tub xaa nkano mbakxiil, nu nanzhot xaa xizh ma.
Nalet gu xgab lee kwaane nak nebse tub xgab cheen na, nel noka nkeeya lo ley kwaan mzaa Dios lo Ches.
Nel lee yech cheen ley nzhé: “Nakot gu yex roo ngoon gorna yo ma yee dexkwaa ma nzhobxtil”. Per nanakt kwaane lee Dios nle xgab re ngoon,
leeya nak nel Dios nle xgab re be. Nel lee ley mkee zee leya yudar be, nel mod nii xaa: “Lee xaa nlee lo yo nu xaa nkich nzhobxtil nle rol xaa re yalgon”.
Kwaanzee, chelee nu mxeen nu ben cheen Mbi Naban lextoo gu, nanzakt na gro nak top nu chepse kwaan nkin nu lo re gu.
Nu chelee stub naz xaa nzhaal naab kwaane lo gu, mas nzhaal naab nu chepa lo re gu. Zer naab nu kwaane lo re gu, nixa nzho mod ngnaab nuya, sinka myedoola nu dubse mzaa nu kwent cheen Jesucrist lo gu, zee nangakt kwaane storb lo re kwaan nguné nu.
Nu ne re gu, lee re xaa nkee zhiin leen xkyidoo Dios nzhaw xaa re kwaan nla yidoo. Kwaan nzhekla na nii na nak, lee re ngwleyy nzo nteed ma, kwaan mzaa re xaa lo Dios, nu nzhaw re ngwleyy tik baal cheen re ma nteed xaa lo mdo leen xkyidoo Dios.
Nu leeka snee, lee Xaa Nabeyy nxaal loka xaa zaa kwent cheen xaa, nzhaal gaw xaa kwaan nzaa re xaa mkayaa xtizh xaa.
Per lee na nik tub welt zer le na re kwaane, nixa nankeet na kwaane lo gu zee zaa gu kwaan lo na nal. ¡Mas wen yet na ke stub xaa zaa kwaan gaw na! (Nto na yalxwa lo kwaane.)
Nu nzak na nawent to na yalxwa nel nza na kwent cheen wdizh chul, nel leeya nak tub kwaan mzaa Dios le na. ¡Nu bid doo deed na chelee na nazat na kwent cheen wdizh chul!
Kwaanzee, chelee na za na kwent cheen wdizh chul nel nzhekla na, telisa kayaa na kwaan chul kwaan zaa Dios lo na. Per noka chol nanzheklat na za na kwenta, seetaka telisa za naya nel Dios mzaa zhiin ne lo na.
Nu kwaanzee, kwaan nle na gan nak, nzho mod nza na kwent cheen wdizh chul nu nanaabt na nik tub kwaan nel mle naya. Kwaan nzhekla na nii na nak, nanaabt na kix xaa ka na.
Nixa nik tub xaa nanabeyyt na, per ngok na xaa nkee zhiin lo rese xaa, zee gon zyen xaa xtizh Dios.
Noka nle na mod tub xaa nangozhawt ley cheen Ches, zee gon re xaa nangozhawt ley cheen Ches xtizh Dios; nixa wlipa nabeyy ley cheen Jesucrist lo na.
Leezha nzo na kwaan tub xaa nanyet nzo lo Dios, nle na mod tub xaa nanyet nzo lo Dios, zee gon xaa xtizh Dios. Kwaan nzhekla na nii na nak, nle na mod nak rese xaa, zee nzho mod gon lak xaa xtizh Dios.
Rese kwaane nle na zee gon re xaa wdizh chul, zee noka na gak xaa le gan.
Kwaanzee re gu ne leezha nyu tub karrer rese xaa nrexonn, per tubka xaa nak xaa nle gan. Kwaanzee sbaaka bkee gu zhiin zee le gu gan kwaan zelazh Dios.
Kwaanzee rese xaa nrexonn lo tub karrer nkanap xaa xkwerp xaa lo rese kwaan nawent. Nu nle xaa rese kwaane, zee le xaa gan nebse tub koron kwaan ndexkwaa kwaan lag yag laurel, nu chepse nyeya ta ngoola. Per lee be nkambaz kwaan zelazh Dios lo be, tub kwaan tira dii.
Kwaanzee nye nkee na zhiin, noka nak na tub xaa nye ndil nu nakakeet na panyet lo mbi.
Nteed na kwerp cheen na bid, nle naya zee leya kwaan nzhekla na, zee nagakt na tub xaa nanreket xnaz Dios, mod nza na kwent lo stub naz xaa.
Nangwiit gu lo re majWech nu bzan, nanzheklat na yenlazh gu: Leezha mroo re xey nu, xaa yilo, Egipto lee xkaw cheen Dios mlu naz lo xaa nu mded xaa Nistoo Naxne lo yo bizh.
Nu snee mded rese xaa zee, modxa mrubnis xaa leen xkaw nu leen nistoo zee ngok xaa tub xaa mreke tich Ches.
Nu rese xaa zee ndaw leeka kwaan mzaa Dios gaw xaa,
nu rese xaa zee ngu leeka nis kwaan mzaa Dios go xaa. Nel cho ke cheen Dios ngu xaa nis. Ke ne nak Jesucrist, xaa nzha kwaan re xaa naz wen.
Mkanap Dios re xaa, nixa nangulat Dios re kwaan mle xaa, kwaanzee zyen doo xaa ngut naz wen.
Rese kwaane mded zee zeen re be nalet be re kwaan nawent, mod mle re xaa zee.
Kwaanzee, nawiit gu lo re maj, kwentaxa mle re xaa zee. Modxa nzaa Xkyech Dios kwent: “Lee re myet mle yalni, ndaw xaa, ngu xaa, zeera nguxso xaa, mkanii xaa nu mbill xaa lo xmaj xaa”.
Nu nachaalt be sa myet be, mod mle re xaa zee. Kwaane mle zee tubka mbizh ngut tub galbchon mil myet.
Nu nixa nalet be zee zhaal xyan Xaa Nabeyy, modxa mle re xaa zee, zee mkee mball wiza re xaa, zee ngut xaa.
Nu nixa nanzhedizh went be Dios, nel kwaane mle lak re xaa zee, kwaanzee Dios mxaal xmandad xaa zee mbit xaa re xaa zee.
Rese kwaane mded re xey nu xaa yilo, zee ne be nalet be re kwaane, nu mkeeya lo Xkyech Dios zee zeen re be, xaa nzho re mbizh gwluzh ne.
Kwaanzee chelee be nzak be nali nzo be, kanapka be be napaka le be tub kwaan nawent.
Zee lee Maxuu nzhekla kiil be mod nkiil xaa rese myet yizhyo, per Dios nle yudar be nu nanlaat xaa kiil Maxuu be axta paro nayet be. Nu leezha nzhekla Maxuu kiil be, zeera luu Dios tub mod roo be, zee ye be ded beya.
Kwaanzee wech nu bzan, xaa nkela na, tira nawiit gu lo re maj.
Nii na kwaane lo gu mod xaa nzhak, zee nzho mod labeyy gu nen che wli kwaan nii na.
Leezha nzho be xis ub leen bas cheen xchee Xaa Nabeyy, nzaa be dixkix lo Dios, nu leeya nlu lee be tubka nak kwaan Jesucrist lo xren xaa; nu leezha nzhaw be pan, leeya nlu lee be tubka nak kwaan Jesucrist lo kwerp cheen xaa.
Nu nixa zyen doo be, per tubka pan nzhaw re be, kwaanzee lee be nak tubka kwerp.
Bzeen gu xomod mle re sawlazh nu; leezha nzhaw xaa re ma mteed xaa lo Dios, nlu tubka nak xaa lo Dios.
Nu kwaan nzhekla na nii na nak, lee maj nanakt dios, kwaanzee lee baal kwaan nteed xaa lo maj, nebse nak tub kwaan sbaasa.
Kwaan nzhekla na nii na nak, leezha lee re xaa nanakt xaa Dios nteed tub ma lo maj, naleet lo Dios nzaa xaaya, lee xaa kazaaya lo re mbi mal, nu nanzheklat na tubka yo gu kwaan mbi mal.
Nel nyent mod go gu kwaan nzho leen bas cheen xchee Xaa Nabeyy nu go gu kwaan nzho leen bas cheen re mbi mal, nixa nyent mod zob gu gaw gu roo mes cheen Xaa Nabeyy nu zobka gu roo mes cheen re mbi mal.
¿Cho kwaan nzhekla gu le gu? ¿Che nzhekla gu zee yii Xaa Nabeyy ne be? ¡Telisa nyent mod dil be kwaan lee xaa!
Nanzhaalt kwaan be zee yo chul leeka be, nzhaal kwaan be zee chul yo stub naz xaa.
Nzho mod gaw be rese baal kwaan nto xaa, nu nanabdizht be nen che naka tub baal kwaan mteed xaa lo maj zee nalet be xgab.
Mod nkee: Lee yizhyo nak cheen Xaa Nabeyy, nu noka rese kwaan nzho leena.
Chelee tub xaa nanakt xaa Jesús kwezh gu gaw gu garli xaa, nu nzhekla gu ya gu, daw gu rese kwaan zaa xaa lo gu, nu nanabdizht gu nen che naka tub kwaan mteed xaa lo maj, zee nalet xaa xgab.
Per chelee tub xaa né lo be: “Lee baal ne mteed na lo maj”, nagawt beya nel nanzheklat be leya, zee lee xaa ne le xgab nawenta.
Kanii na xgab kwaan nzho yek stub xaa, nu nanakta xgab kwaan nzho yek be.Per chelee tub gu nabdizh: “¿Chozhiin naab xaa kwent lo na, libr nak na lo xgab cheen stub xaa?
Nu chelee na nza na dixkix lo Dios gorna gaw naya, ¿chozhiin wdizh nawent re xaa na, nel nzhaw naya?”
Kwaane nkeb na: Rese kwaan nle be, gorna nzhaw be o gorna nzho be, nzhaal le beya zee nii wen re xaa Dios.
Nu nalet be zee lee stub naz xaa le jwalt, nixa re sawlazh nu o re xaa nanakt sawlazh nu, nixa re xaa nak xaa Jesús.
Nu lo rese kwaan nle na, nanzheklat na le na nawent lo stub naz xaa, nu nankwaant na kwaan nyula na, lee na nkwaan kwaan nyula stub naz xaa, zee nzho mod le xaa gan yalnaban cheen xaa.
Ble gu mod nle na, nel nle na mod mle Jesucrist.
Xomod nzhaal le be leezha nzholl be lo DiosNal nyakla na mbin na nselazh gu na, nu nle gu re kwaan mnabeyy na le gu.
Per nzhekla na, zeen gu lee Jesucrist nabeyy rese xaabyi, nu xaabyi nabeyy ngwnaa, modxa Dios nabeyy Jesucrist.
Nu chelee tub xaabyi saaw yek gorna wdizhno xaa Dios, o gorna nzaa xaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa, nlu xaa nanzhont xaa xtizh Xaa Nabeyy.
Nu chelee tub ngwnaa nasaawt yek gorna nii me lo Dios o gorna nzaa me kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee me, nlu me nanzhont me xtizh sa me. Nu snee lal nle me ke tub me tira mrub yek, kwaane nlu nawent nak me.
Wena, chelee tub ngwnaa nsaaw me yek me, per nawent chuub me yek me. Nel nton me chuub me yek me, zee mas wen saaw me yek me.
Lee xaabyi nanzhaalt saaw xaa yek xaa nel mdexkwaa Dios xaa mod lee xaa nu snee nlu chul nak Dios. Per lee ngwnaa nzhaal saaw me yek me, zee luu nzhon me xtizh sa me.
Sbaa nii na nel namzant ngwnaa xaabyi yilo, sinka lee ngwnaa, me yilo, cho xaabyi mroo me.
Nu lee xaabyi namdexkwaat Dios nel nkin ngwnaa xaa, per lee ngwnaa mdexkwaa Dios nel nkin xaabyi me.
Kwaanzee lee ngwnaa nzhaal saaw me yek me zee luu me lo re mandad cheen Dios, lee me nak tub me nzhon xtizh sa me.
Per lee re be, xaa nzhon xtizh Xaa Nabeyy, lee xaabyi nkin ngwnaa nu sbaaka lee ngwnaa nkin xaabyi.
Nixa wli lee ngwnaa yilo mdexkwaa kwaan tik cho xaabyi yilo, per noka nal wli lee ngwnaa nzan xaabyi, nu xaabyi rop ngwnaa, mdexkwaa Dios.
Nu leeka re gu nzhaal nii, che wen lee ngwnaa wdizhno Dios nu nasaawt me yek me.
Nu leeka re myet yizhyo ne nlu lo re gu lee xaabyi nanzhaalt laa xaa roo yich yek xaa,
nu leeka snee lee ngwnaa nzhaal laa me roo yich yek me, zee saawa yek me, nel leeya nak tub kwaan chul lo me, nel lo lee me mzaa Dios diizh roo yich yek me.
Wena, per chelee tub xaa nanzheklat kayaa kwaane, nzhaal ne xaa, nixa nu, nu nixa re xaa Jesús, nanzaat nu stub kwent lo re kwaane.
Nawent nle gu xchee cheen Xaa Nabeyy beKwaan nii na lo gu nal nak, nanyulat na re kwaan nle gu gorna nkasa gu gool gu lo Dios. Nel leezha nkasa gu nzhaal leya zee nyera zo gu lo Dios, per lo re gu rebes naka.
Nu kwaan yilo, nguné xaa lo na nrexcho gu leezha nkasa gu gool gu lo Dios, nu nzak na wliya.
¿Che nzak gu snee nzho mod luu gu na xana xaa wlipa nreke tich Jesucrist?
Nel gorna nzhaw gu, rol gu nzhaw yilo, nu nzhaw gu rese kwaan, nu lee zrol gu seetaka nlaan nu zrol gu tira nzuzh.
¿Che nyent garli gu pa gaw gu nu pa go gu? Nel tira nawent kwaan nle gu lo re xaa Jesús, nu nle gu zee nton re xaa prob ne gu. ¿Cho kwaan nzhekla gu nii na lo gu? ¿Che nzhekla gu nii na chul nle gu? ¡Per na nii, tira nawent nle gu kwaane!
Xchee cheen Xaa Nabeyy<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?40.26.26-29">Mt. 26:26-29</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?41.14.22-25">Mr. 14:22-25</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?42.22.14-23">Lc. 22:14-23</a>)Lee kwaan mseed na lo Xaa Nabeyy noka mlu naya lo gu: Leeka gwzhe kwaan mzaa xaa Xaa Nabeyy yet, lee xaa mzen cha pan,
nu gorna ngulo mzaa xaa dixkix lo Dios mxux xaaya nu nzhé xaa: “Kwaane nak xbaal na, kwaane za na kwent cheen re gu. Ble gu kwaane zee selazh gu xomod yet na.”
Nu leeka snee gorna ngulo ndaw xchee xaa, zee mzen xaa bas, kwaan nzho xis ub leen, nu nzhé xaa: “Lee xis ub kwaan nzho leen bas ne nak xren na cheen wdizh kub kwaan laa Dios lo gu. Kad welt kwaan go guya ble guya zee selazh gu na.”
Nu kad welt kwaan gaw be pan ne nu go be xis ub ne nselazh be xomod ngut Xaa Nabeyy. Nu snee le beya axta bare Xaa Nabeyy.
Nu nii na, loka xaa gaw pan ne o go xis ub ne sbaasa, tira nawent kwaan nle xaa leezha nselazh be xkwerp Xaa Nabeyy nu xren xaa.
Kwaanzee kad tub xaa nzhaal le wen xaa xgab, gorna gaw xaa pan ne nu gorna go xaa xis ub ne.
Nel chelee xaa sbaasa gaw xaa pan nu sbaasa go xis ub, nu nanet xaa cho kwaan naka, sbaa nle xaa zee teed Dios xaa bid.
Nel snee nle zyen gu zee nyent jwers lo gu, nu lak gu ne nzak nu zlak gu axta ngutla.
Nu chelee be le wen be xgab leezha nzhaw be Xchee cheen Xaa Nabeyy, zee nankint teed Dios be bid.
Nu chelee Xaa Nabeyy naab kwent cheen be naka zee seed be, nu nanakta zee tira ded be bid kwaan re myet yizhyo.
Kwaanzee wech nu bzan, leezha gaw be xchee cheen Xaa Nabeyy, kwaz be zee tubka gaw re beya.
Nu chelee tub be nlaan, nzhaal gaw be garli be, zee nakint teed Dios be bid kwent cheen xchee ne.Lee stub naz kwaan mnabdizh gu lo na, luu naya lo gu gorna bare na lo re gu stub welt.
Re kwaan nzelazh Dios lo re xaa JesúsNal wech nu bzan, nzhekla na za na kwent, zee ne gu chep xomod nak kwaan nzelazh Mbi Naban cheen Dios lo re be, xaa nak xaa Jesús.
Nzhaal ne gu leezha zer gak gu xaa Xaa Nabeyy, mbill gu lo re maj kwaan nambant.
Kwaanzee nal, nzhekla na ne gu nik tub xaa kwaan nzho Mbi Naban lextoo, nyent mod né: “Jesucrist nak Maxuu”. Nu nixa nik tub xaa nyent mod né: “Jesucrist nak Xaa Nabeyy na”, cheleeya nanzhot Mbi Naban cheen Dios lextoo xaa.
Xa nak kwaan nzaa Mbi Naban cheen Dios lo tub be nu lo stub be, nel lee Mbi Naban tubka nak.
Zyen doo mod nkee be xchiin Dios per lo tubka Xaa Nabeyy nkee be zhiin.
Xa kwaan nzelazh Dios lo kad tub be zee kee be xchiin xaa, per lee xaa nak xaa nkee zhiin kwent cheen be.
Lo kad tub be nzelazh Dios Mbi Naban cheen xaa, zee nzho mod le be yudar re xaa Jesús.
Nu kwaan Mbi Naban nzelazh Dios re kwaane:zee tub naz xaa nii kwaan yalnzhak,nu stub naz xaa labeyy cho kwaan nzhekla Dios,
nu stub naz xaa nzho mod wii cho kwaan nzhekla Dios le,nu stub naz xaa sekwen re xaa ne nzak,
nu stub naz xaa nzho mod le zyen doo kwaan gro,nu stub naz xaa nzho mod zaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa,nu stub naz xaa ne xana kwaan nroo lo mbi mal nu lo Mbi Naban,nu stub naz xaa nii stub diizh kwaan nagakt xaa,nu stub naz xaa nzho mod zaa kwent cho kwaan ngunii xaa ba,
Per tubka Mbi Naban nzelazh rese kwaane, nu nzaa xaaya lo kad tub be mod nzhekla xaa zaa xaaya.
Rese be nak kwerp cheen JesucristNu lee kwerp cheen myet nixa nkanoya zyen pa (kwenta nii xaa, yaa xaa, nzha xaa), per tubka kwerp naka. Nu seeka nak kwerp cheen Jesucrist.
Nu leeka snee rese be, xaa Israel o xaa nanakt xaa Israel, xaa nak mos o xaa nanakt mos, mrubnis be kwaan tubka Mbi Naban zee gak be tubka kwerp, nu leeka Mbi Naban nabeyy leen lextoo rese be.
Lee kwerp nanakta tubka pa, leeya nak zyen pa.
Chol yé nii tub xaa: “Nel nanakt na yaa xaa, nanakt na cheen kwerp”. Nixa sbaa yéya, seetaka naka tub pa cheen kwerp cheen xaa.
Chelee dubse kwerp nak nebse zaalo xaa, nyent mod gon xaa. O chelee dubse kwerp nak nebse nzha xaa, nyent mod koob xaa bech.
Per lee Dios mzob kad pa kwerp cheen be paro mas wen nzhaala nzak xaa.
Cheleeya tubka kwaan ngak dubse xaa, zee nyent kwerp.
Per kwaan wli nak, lee kwerp nkano zyen pa choya per tubka kwerp naka.
Zee lee zaalo xaa nyent mod yé lo yaa xaa: “Nankint na lu”; nixa yek xaa nyent mod yé lo nii xaa: “Nankint na lu”.
Per lee re pa cho be, pa nzak be nanont, leeya nak kwaan mas nkin be.
Nu lee cho be paro nzak be sbaasa, nak paro nzob be kwaan chul nlu. Noka lee cho be pa nanzheklat be luu mas nsegak beya ler,
nu lee pa mas chul nlu nankint tant kanap beya. Per Dios mdexkwaa cho be zee lee paro nzak be mas nachult mas nkanap beya.
Zee nayiit tub pa ne stub pa, zee rese pa cho be kanap stub pa cho.
Chelee tub pa cho be ne nzak, dubse cho be ne; nu chelee tub pa cho be wen nzak, dubse cho be wen nzak.
Nu sbaa nak be mod kwerp cheen Jesucrist, nel kad tub be nak mod tik cho kwerp cheen xaa.
Kwaanzee Dios mzaa lo re xaa Jesús pa nzhaal kee xaa zhiin.Xaa mas non nak xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist,nu zeera xaa nzaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa,nu zeera re xaa nseed xtizh Dios,nu gwluzh xaa nle kwaan gro kwaan nyent mod le re myet,xaa nsekwen re xaa ne nzak,xaa nle yudar re xaa nkin kwaan,xaa nabeyy lo re xaa Jesús,xaa nzhedizh stub naz diizh kwaan nagakt xaa.
Naret xaa nak xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, nu nixa naret xaa nzaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa. Naret xaa nseed xtizh Dios, nu nixa naret xaa nle re kwaan gro.
Nu nixa naret xaa nsekwen re xaa ne nzak, nu nixa naret xaa nzhedizh stub diizh kwaan nagakt xaa nu nixa naret xaa nzho mod nzaa kwent cho kwaan nzhé xaa zee.
Kwaanzee re gu nzhaal yula gu kayaa gu re kwaan mas wen, kwaan nzelazh Dios.Nal luu na stub naz kwaan mas chul lo re gu.
YalnkelaChelee na nzhedizh na xtizh re myet kwaan nagakt na, nu axta xtizh mandad cheen Dios per nankelat na wechxinn na, nanont kwaana nii na, nebse mod tub lee yiib kwaan nkee chi naka.
Nu chelee Mbi Naban nzelazh lo na zee za na kwent kwaan né Dios lo na, nu chelee na ne na re kwaan xlaan cheen Dios, nu chelee na nkano na rese yalnzhak, nu chelee na ngwii na lo Dios zee nzho mod nabeey na axta bachii yi, per nankelat na wechxinn na, tira nanont na.
Nu chelee na ngiiz na rese kwaan nkano na lo re xaa nkin kwaan nu za na na yo na lo ki nel nza na kwent xtizh Dios per nankelat na wechxinn na, nanont kwaane.
Xaa nkela:nyela xaa ne xaa rese kwaan nle stub naz xaa lo xaa,nlesla xaa ne xaa stub naz xaa,nanzoblazht xaa cheen stub naz xaa,nanzhedizht xwa xaa nixa nantot xaa yalxwa;
xaa nkela naniit wdizh nawent,xaa nkela nangozhawt xaa rese xcheen xaa para leeka lee xaa,xaa nkela nanzhalxyant,xaa nkela nanselazht re kwaan nle xaa lo xaa,
xaa nkela nanyulat ded stub xaa bid,nu nix doo nzhak lextoo xaa ne xaa re kwaan wli.
Tub xaa nkela: Tubka nyela nded bid, tubka nali nak xaa lo xmig xaa, tubka nkambaz xaa lee stub xaa le kwaan wen, nu tubka nyela xaa lo rese kwaan nle stub xaa lo xaa.
Tira ndii yalnkela. Per stub naz re kwaan nzelazh Dios nankint diiya tira, re kwaan kwenta kwaane: re xaa nzaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa, zhin mbizh nazaatra xaaya; nu lee re xaa nzhedizh stub diizh kwaan nagakt xaa, zhin mbizh nawdizhtra xaaya; nu lee re yalnzhak kwaan nzaa Mbi Naban, zhin mbizh nakayaatra xaaya. Rese kwaane nadiit tira.
Nal nanlat rese kwaan yek be, nu noka nzho welt nawent nzaa be kwent rese kwaan nzhekla Dios nii lo be.
Per zhin mbizh leezha bare Xaa Nali, zee nakintra be re kwaan nadiit.
Leezha nyeen na mdizh na nu mle na xgab nu mla kwaan yek na mod tub xaawin, per leezha ngok na tub xaabyi mlaa na rese kwaan nak cheen xaawin.
Nal nanyaniwenta lo be, nlu rese kwaan lo be kwenta leezha ngwii be lo spej beed, per yo tub mbizh kwaan luu reya lo be kwentaxa naka. Nal chepseya nlabeyy naya per mbizh zee tira yilo labeyy naya, kwentaxa tira nlabeyy Dios na.
Nal nkano be chon kwaan ndii: mod ngwii be lo Dios, nu mod nkambaz be re kwaan nguné xaa, nu mod nkela be; per kwaan nonra lo yon kwaane nak yalnkela.
Mas chul zaa xaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa ke wdizh xaa stub diizhTubka kela be, nel kwaane nak kwaan nonra. Nu zoblazh be re kwaan nzelazh Dios kwaan Mbi Naban, nu lo reya zoblazhra be zaa be kwent re kwaan né Dios lo be.
Per lee xaa kwaan nzaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa nle xaa zee mas nye nzo stub naz xaa lo Dios, nu nzaa xaa balor lextoo re xaa nu nseleyy xaa xaa.
Lee xaa nzhedizh stub diizh kwaan nagakt xaa, nle xaa zee mas nye nzo leeka lee xaa lo Dios, per lee xaa nzaa kwent wdizh kwaan mkayaa xaa lo Dios nle xaa zee mas nye nzo re xaa Jesús lo Dios.
Nzhekla na rese gu wdizh stub diizh, per mas nzhekla na zaa gu kwent kwaan né Dios lo gu, mas wen kwaane ke wdizh xaa stub diizh kwaan nagakt xaa. Per noka nzho mod wdizh xaa stub diizh kwaan nagakt xaa, chelee stub xaa zaa kwent cho kwaan ngunii xaa lo re xaa Jesús, zee snee mas nye zo kad tub xaa lo Dios.
Kwaanzee wech nu bzan, nyent sirb chelee na ya na lo re gu nu nii na kwaan stub diizh kwaan nagakt gu, lo re gu. Mas wen yal na lo re gu zee nii na kwaan nzhekla Dios né lo re be, o kwaan yalnzhak nii na kwaan wli lo gu, o za na wdizh kwaan nguné Dios lo na, o seed na gu stub kwaan cheen Dios.
Kwaanzee re kwaan nzholl xaa, kwenta bzhik nu kwenta bagwel, cheleeya nakanota mer bi cheena nyent mod labeyy xaa xana tuba stuba.
Nu cheleeya lo dil nakwezh went xaa trompet, nanet re xaa cho gor zelo dil.
Leeka kwaane nded lo re be, chelee be nii be tub diizh kwaan nanlat yek re be, nyent mod ne xaa cho kwaan kanii be. ¡Lo mbi nzhob xtizh be!
Wli nzho zyen doo stub naz diizh lo yizhyo, per nlaya yek xaa niiya.
Per chelee na nanet na cho kwaan nii xaa lo na, mod xaa zit nak na lo xaa, nu leeka xaa zit nak xaa zee lo na.
Nel nzoblazh be kano be kwaan nzelazh Mbi Naban, zoblazh be kano be re kwaan nzho mod le zee nyera zo kad tub xaa Jesús lo Dios.
Kwaanzee lee xaa kwaan nzhedizh stub diizh kwaan nagakt xaa, nzhaal naab xaa lo Dios zee nzho mod zaa xaa kwent cho kwaan ngunii xaa.
Kwaanzee leezha nii na lo Dios kwaan stub diizh kwaan nagakt na, nii Mbi Naban kwent cheen na per lee na nanet na cho kwaan kanii na.
¿Nu zee cho kwaan nzhaal le na? Nzhaal nii na lo Dios kwaan Mbi Naban nu noka nzhaal nii na kwaan nla yek na. Nu nzhaal gol na lo Dios kwaan Mbi Naban nu noka nzhaal gol na lo Dios kwaan kwaan nla yek na.
Nel chelee be nii be lo Dios nu zaa be dixkix lo xaa kwaan Mbi Naban snee, nu chelee tub xaa sbaasa kenzhaya, nu nakanot xaa kwaan nzelazh Mbi Naban, nyent mod wdizhno xaa Dios tubka kwaan be, nel nanet xaa cho kwaan kanii be.
Nzho mod zaa be dixkix lo Dios per naleta yudar zo nye stub xaa lo Dios.
Nzaa na dixkix lo Dios nel mas nzhak na nii na stub re diizh ke tub re gu;
per lee lo re xaa Jesús mas wen seed na xaa gaayka wdizh kwaan la yek xaa, ke kwaan chii mil wdizh kwaan nanet xaa ne cho kwaan nii na.
Wech nu bzan, nagakt be mod xaawin mod nle be xgab, per gak be mod tub xaawin lo re kwaan nawent nu naletra beya, per mod nle be xgab gak be xaa gox.
Nel lee Xkyech Dios nzhé: “Nii na lo yezh ne kwaan stub wdizh, nu nii naya kwaan roo xaa zit, nu nixa sneeya nanzhont xaa xtizh na, né Xaa Nabeyy”.
Kwaanzee leezha nii be stub diizh kwaan nagakt be, naka mod tub nseyn lo re xaa nanakt xaa Jesús, nu nanakta tub nseyn lo re xaa Jesús. Nu gorna nzaa be kwent kwaan nguné Dios lo be, naka mod tub nseyn lo re xaa Jesús per nanakta mod tub nseyn lo re xaa nanakt xaa Jesús.
Nu gorna nkasa re be, xaa Jesús, nu rese xaa nzhedizh stub diizh nu rep tub xaa nanakt xaa Jesús, xaa nanlabeyyt re kwaan nzelazh Mbi Naban, zle xaa xgab nzhak nachan re be.
Per cheleeya rese be kazaa be kwent re kwaan né Dios lo be, nu rep tub xaa nanakt tub xaa Jesús nu gon xaaya, tub xaa nanlabeyyt re kwaan nzelazh Mbi Naban, zlabeyy xaa jwalt cheen xaa nu leeka lee xaa zeen re kwaan nawent kwaan mle xaa gorna gon xaa re kwaan kazaa be kwent.
Zee zeen xaa re kwaan nzho lextoo xaa, nu snee kichyek xaa axta lo yo nu gool xaa lo Dios, zee zeen xaa lee Dios wlipa nzo kwaan re be.
Xomod nzhaal gool be lo DiosWech nu bzan, kwaan nzhekla na nii na lo rese kwaane nak, leezha kasa be gool be lo Dios, lak be nzho mod gool kant, zlak be nzho mod lu xtizh Dios, zlak be nzho mod zaa kwent kwaan ngunii Dios lo xaa, zlak be nzho mod nii stub diizh kwaan nagakt xaa, nu zlak be nzho mod yé cho kwaan ngunii xaa kwaan stub diizh, per rese kwaane nzhaal le yudar be, zee mas nye zo be lo Dios.
Nu leezha lee tub xaa nii stub diizh kwaan nagakt xaa, nzhaal nii chop xaa o chon xaa, nu kad xaa nii gorna yizo xaa nii xaa, nu noka nzhaal lee stub xaa zaa kwent cho kwaan kanii xaa, xaa kanii stub diizh.
Per chelee lo re be, xaa Jesús, nyent stub xaa zaa kwent cho kwaan kanii xaa, xaa kanii stub diizh, mas wen naniit xaaya lo re xaa, nu mas wen nii xaaya leezha nii techosa xaa lo Dios.
Nu leeka snee lee xaa nzhekla yé kwaan ngunii Dios lo xaa, nzhaal nii chop xaa o chon xaa, nu lee stub naz xaa nzhaal kenzha kwaan kanii xaa, zee ne xaa che naka cheen Dios.
Per chelee Dios nii tub kwaan lo stub xaa nzob lo re xaa zee, lee xaa kanii nzhaal laa nii xaa.
Nu snee kad tub xaa nzhaal nii gorna yizo xaa nii xaa, nzho mod zaa xaa kwent kwaan ngunii Dios lo xaa, zee snee nzho mod seed re xaa nu nzho mod yo balor lextoo re xaa.
nel Dios nak cho nle zee kwi chul re xaa, nel nanzheklat xaa guchniz re kwaan.Ble gu modxa nle rese xaa Jesús, xaa nambey nak,
lee re ngwnaa nanzhaalt nii me leen kult, nel nyent derech nii ngwnaa leen kult. Nzhaal gon me xtizh sa me, kwentaxa nkee lo Xkyech Dios.
Chelee me nzhekla me né me tub kwaan, nzhaal nabdizh meya lo sa me garli me, nel nawent nak lee tub ngwnaa nii leen kult.
Nu tubka bselazh gu xtizh Dios, nel namzhinta yilotlaka lo re gu, nu nixa nanebt gu mkayaaya.
Chelee tub xaa nzak nak xaa tub xaa nzaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa o nak xaa tub xaa mkayaa tub kwaan lo Mbi Naban, nzhaal zaa xaa yek xaa gon xaaya, lee kwaan kakee na lo gu nak kwaan mxaal Xaa Nabeyy.
Nu chelee xaa nagont xaa kwaane, noka nagont gu re kwaan yé xaa.
Nu sbaaka wech nu bzan, bzoblazh gu zaa gu kwent kwaan ngunii Dios lo gu, nu noka laa gu zee nii xaa stub diizh kwaan nagakt xaa;
per ble gu re kwaane tub mod chul, mod nzhaal le guya.
Yalmroban cheen JesucristLee nal wech nu bzan, nzhekla na selazh gu wdizh chul kwaan mza na lo re gu, wdizh kwaan mkayaa re gu, lo kwaan nali nzo gu.
Nu noka Kwent Chul ne mle zee le gu gan yalnaban, nel nzhon gu re kwaan nzhéya; per chelee gu nagont gu kwaan nzhéya, nik tub kwaan nakayaat gu lo Dios.
Lee wdizh kwaan mseed na re gu nak leeka kwaan mseed na lo Jesucrist nu naka tub kwaan non doo. Lee wdizh ne nak: Jesucrist ngut kwent cheen jwalt cheen re be, modxa nkeeya lo Xkyech Dios;
nu mkaach xaa xaa nu leezha mzhaal yon mbizh lee xaa mroban, modxa nkeeya lo Xkyech Dios;
yilotlaka mlu xaa lo Pér, zeera mlu xaa lo re xchiibtub xaa mseed lo xaa.
Nu gwluzh zeera mlu xaa lo kan tub gaay gayoo wech nu bzan, nu zyen doo xaa ne ngune lee xaa mbanaka nal, per noka nzho lak xaa ngune lo xaa ngutla nal.
Nu gwluzh zeera mlu Jesús lo Chag nu lo re xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo xaa.
Nu noka lo na mlu xaa axta gwluzhtlaka, nel na nak mod tub mad mded mbizh gal.
Nel na nak xaa mas tira nanont lo re xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, nu nixa nanzhaalt role na tub xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, nel na mrenal re xaa Jesús.
Per nak na kwaan nak na nel mlesla Dios ne na, nu kwaan yalnkela cheen xaa nangokt na tub xaa sbaasa. Lee na mas nzhakee zhiin ke rese stub xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, per wlipa natechot na mle rese kwaane, xaa mleya nak Dios, nu kwaan yalnkela cheen xaa mle xaa yudar na.
Kwaanzee nanont che naya o che stub xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, mzaa nu kwent kwaane lo gu, kwaan non nak mbin guya.
Yalmroban cheen re xaa ngutMod mzaa nu kwent, lee Jesucrist mroban. ¿Chozhiin nii lak gu lee re xaa ngut narobant?
Nel chol lee re xaa ngut narobant, zee noka Jesucrist nangrobant xaa.
Nu chol nangrobant Jesucrist, zee nanont kwaan nzaa nu kwent, nu nixa nanont mod ngwii be lo Jesús.
Nu chol nangrobant Jesucrist, lee nu nak xaa nkade, nel leeka re nu né lee Dios mseban Jesucrist. Nu sbaa nkade nu chol nawlit roban re xaa ngut.
Nel chol narobant re xaa ngut, noka Jesucrist nangrobant;
nu chol namrobant Jesucrist, zee nanont mod ngwii be lo Jesús, zee lee re jwalt cheen be seetaka nzhib tich be.
Nu chol snee naka, zee lee re xaa ngut, xaa mwii lo Jesucrist, tira ngulo mlux xaa.
Chol nreke be tich Jesucrist nebse kwent cheen kwaan kayaa be yizhyo ne, be nak xaa mas nales doo lo rese myet.
Per kwaan wli nak lee Jesucrist mroban. Lee xaa nak kwenta xle kwaan nzaa yag yilo, kwaan nak mod tub gon lo Dios; nel lee xaa nak xaa yilotlaka mroban.
Nel nebse jwalt cheen tub xaabyi, xaa le Dan, mle mrep yalgut lo yizhyo; sneeka nebse kwaan wen kwaan mle stub xaabyi, xaa le Jesús, nzho yalmroban cheen re xaa ngut.
Per kad tub be roban gorna nzhaal roban be; yilotlaka Jesucrist mroban zeera roban re xaa xaa gorna bare xaa.
Gorzee lux yizhyo nu lee Jesucrist kiib rese yalnabeyy cheen re myet, nu cheen rese mbi mal, nu cheen Maxuu, nu zaa xaa yalnabeyy ne lo Dios, xaa nak Xuz be.
Nel lee Jesucrist nzhaal nabeyy axta le xaa gan lo rese xaa nayii ne xaa,
nu gwluzhtlaka kiib xaa yalnabeyy cheen yalgut.
Mod nii Xkyech Dios: “Dios mle zee nabeyy xaa rese xaa nu rese kwaan”. Naniit kwaane lee Jesucrist nabeyy Dios.
Per gorna nabeyy xaa rese kwaan, zee laa xaa nabeyy Dios xaa. Nu snee lee Dios, xaa mzaa yalnabeyy lo Xgann xaa, gak Xaa Nabeyy lo rese xaa nu lo rese kwaan.
Nu chol narobant myet, ¿chozhiin nrubnis lak xaa, kwent cheen re xaa ngut?
Nu chol sbaa naka, ¿chozhiin nle nu reyez yet nu rese mbizh?
Kwaanzee wech nu bzan, yizata mbizh nzho reyez yet na. Wli kwaane, nu noka wli nyula na ne na xomod nye nzo gu lo xcheen Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be.
Nu chol nebse kwent cheen na mdil na kwaan re xaa mrixyan kwenta ma nakap, yezh Éfeso, ¿cho sirb leya cheleeya narobant be? Chol wli lee re xaa ngut narobant, mas wen le be mod nii re xaa: “¡Gaw be nu go be nel yee yet be!”
Nalaat gu kade xaa gu. Modxa nzhé xaa: “Lee re xmig xaa nawent, nle zee nle xaa kwaan nawent”.
Ble gu xgab kwaan wli, nu nalet gu kwaan nawent, nel nzho xaa nanlabeyyt Dios. Nii na kwaane zee ton gu.
Xomod gak kwerp cheen re xaa robanKwaanzee lak gu mbezh: “¿Xomod gak kwerp cheen re xaa roban? ¿Cho klas kwerp kano xaa?”
Kwaane nak tub yalnabdizh nachan, nel ne wen be leezha ngo be tub bizh lo yo, nzhaal lux xaba zeera gaka tub xan yag.
Lee kwaan ngo be nanakt yag, kwaan ngo be nak tub bizh zee xena, tub bizh cheen nzhobxtil o stub lo re bizh.
Per Dios xeena mod nzhekla xaa, nu kad bizh zaa yag kwaan nzhaal gaka.
Naret baal lal nak, tuba nak xcheen myet stuba nak xcheen ma, nu stuba nak xcheen mbyin nu stuba nak xcheen mbal nistoo.
Nu leeka snee nzho kwerp naz yiba, nu noka nzho kwerp yizhyo. Chul nak re kwerp kwaan yiba per nalalt chul naka kwaan re kwerp cheen yizhyo.
Lee xni mbizh xa nak ke xni mbee, nu ke xni cheen re mbal yiba; nzho tub mbal xa xni cheen ke re stub naz mbal.
Nu sneeka gak yalmroban cheen re myet. Lee kwaan nyubyo lux per lee kwaan roban tira nanluxtra.
Lee kwerp kwaan ngubyo nak tub kwaan nachult, lee kwerp kwaan roban nak tub kwaan chul doo. Lee kwerp kwaan ngubyo nak tub kwaan nangezht nu lee kwerp kwaan roban nak tub kwaan ngezh doo.
Lee kwerp kwaan ngubyo nak kwerp cheen yizhyo nu lee kwerp kwaan roban nak kwerp cheen yiba. Nu mod nzho kwerp cheen yizhyo, sbaaka nzho kwerp cheen yiba.
Kwaan nzhé Xkyech Dios: “Dan, xaabyi yilotlaka, Dios mle mban xaa”; per Jesucrist, ngok mod Dan xaa yilo; mzhin xaa naz yiba zee zaa xaa yalnaban.
Nu lee kwerp kwaan yilo nanakt kwerp kwaan nzho mod yo yiba, kwaan yilo nak kwerp cheen yizhyo, kwaan gwluzh nak kwerp cheen yiba.
Lee xaabyi, xaa yilotlaka mdexkwaa Dios kwaan yo, kwaanzee nak xaa xaa yizhyo, lee stub xaabyi mroo naz yiba.
Lee kwerp cheen xaa yizhyo nak mod kwerp cheen xaabyi, xaa mdexkwaa Dios kwaan yo; lee xaa nya naz yiba kano stub kwerp cheen xaa kwaan nzho mod yo naz yiba, mod kwerp cheen xaa myaad naz yiba.
Nel nzhak be mod xaabyi, xaa kwaan mdexkwaa kwaan yo, seeka gak be kwenta xaabyi, xaa myaad naz yiba.
Kwaan nzhekla na nii na lo re gu wech nu bzan, nak tub kwaan ngulaan axta yilo: Lee kwerp kwaan nak baal, nyent mod repa pa nabeyy Dios, nu lee kwerp kwaan nlux nyent mod zhaal kwaan re kwaan nanluxt.
¡Bkenzha gu! Nii na tub kwaan nagakt re myet lo gu: Naret be yet, per rese be zhee.
Nel lee xkwerp be kwaan nlux nzhaal gak tub kwerp kwaan tira naluxt; nu xkwerp be kwaan nzhet nzhaal gak tub kwerp kwaan tira nayeta.
Nu gorna lee xkwerp be kwaan nlux gak tub kwerp kwaan naluxt, nu gorna lee xkwerp be kwaan nzhet gak kwaan tira nayeta, zee mbarlo kwaan nzhé lo Xkyech Dios: “Nal lee yalgut tira mlux, nu lee yalnaban mle gan”.
“¿Ma yalnabeyy cheen lu, yalgut? Lee yalgut nik tub kwaan nyent mod le lo be.”
Lee yalgut nabeyy lo re myet nel nle re myet jwalt, nu lee re myet nle jwalt nel nyent mod le xaa kwaan nzhé ley cheen Ches.
¡Per dixkix Dios, mla xaa be lo yalgut kwent cheen Jesucrist!
Nu kwaanzee wech nu bzan, re gu xaa nkedoola na, tubka nali zo be lo Dios nu tubka nye zo be lo Dios, nu tubka kee be zhiin lo xchiin Xaa Nabeyy, nel ne re be lee zhiin kwaan kale be nanakta tub zhiin sbaasa.
¿Xomod nzhaal zaa xaa tub gon?Nal za na kwent cheen gon kwaan le gu yudar re xaa mle nambey Jesús. Btop guya modxa nzhé na lo re xaa Jesús, xaa re yezh cheen Galacia.
Yizata dming, kad tub gu nzhaal koxa paro mle gu gan, zee koxa gu laka zee gorna zhin na nankint top beya gor zee.
Nu gorna zhin na nzhekla na kweey gu lak xaa xaal na yezh Jerusalén yilaa gon ne, zee za na tub yech lo xaa yilaa ayud ne.
Nu chelee na nkin ya na, ya re nu xaa ne.
Xgab kwaan nzho yek Pab le PabLee byaj kwaan le na, nkin deed na naz re yezh Macedonia, nu gorna yilo deed na Macedonia zhin na lazh gu.
Nu nle na xgab kwaz na lo re gu lak mbizh, o cheleeya nzho moda kwaz na lo re gu re mbee kwaan nla nal, zee nzho mod xaal re gu na pa nkin ya na gwluzh.
Nanzheklat na nebse deed na lo re gu, nzhekla na kwaz na lo re gu lak mbee chelee Xaa Nabeyy nzhekla,
per kwaz na yezh Éfeso, axta yilo ded yalni cheen Pentecostés,
nel nee nzak na nzho mod le na xchiin Xaa Nabeyy, nu nzak na nee nzho mod le na tub kwaan gro, nixa zyen doo xaa nayii ne na nee nu nzhekla xaa saaw xaa na naz.
Nu cheleeya zhin Timoteo lo gu, ble gu zee chul yo xaa lo re gu, nel lee xaa nkee xchiin Xaa Nabeyy, mod na.
Kwaanzee bkayaa gu xaa; nkin le gu yudar xaa zee chul ya xaa xnaz xaa, zee nzho mod yaadsewii xaa lo na, nel nkambaz na xaa nee kwaan re stub naz re wech be nu re bzan be.
Nal lee wech Apolos nixa ngunaab na lo xaa yaadsewii xaa lo re gu kwaan re wech nu re bzan, per nanet xaa ya xaa nal, per gorna nzho moda lo xaa, zee yaad xaa.
Dix gwluzhTubka bkanap gu gu, nu nye bzo gu lo xcheen Xaa Nabeyy. Tubka blo gu balor lextoo gu nu nye bzo gu.
Nu rese kwaan le gu, ble guya kwaan yalnkela.
Wech nu bzan, lee re gu ne lee re sawlizh wech Estéfanas nak xaa yilotlaka mwii lo Jesucrist xkyizhyo gu, kwaan nak Acaya, nu lee re xaa tubka nle yudar re xaa Jesús, xaa nambey.
Wech nu bzan, nzhekla na gon re gu xtizh re xaa kwenta lee xaa, noka gon gu xtizh rese xaa nle yudar re xaa Jesús, nu noka rese xaa snee nkee zhiin.
Nu nyakdoola na nze wech Estéfanas, wech Fortunato nu wech Acaico nee, kwent cheen re gu, zee le xaa yudar na.
Mseleyy doo re wech ne na, kwentaxa nseleyy xaa gu. Nzhaal wii gu respet lo re xaa kwenta re xaa ne.
Lee re xaa nak xaa Jesús, xaa nzho naz re yezh cheen Asia nxaal “dix” lo re gu. Noka Aquila nu sa xaa Priscila, nu re xaa nkasa garli xaa, nxaal re xaa “dix” lo re gu, nel rese gu nak xaa Xaa Nabeyy.
Bkayaa gu “dix” cheen rese wech nu rese bzan, xaa nzo nee, nu guzh gu “dix” lo re wech nu re bzan xaa naz baa, nu daw gu tub bit tagarlo xaa tub mod nali.
Na nak Pab nu kakee na nebse “dix” ne lo re gu kwaan xletr na, kwaan mer yaa na.
Nu chelee tub xaa nankelat Xaa Nabeyy, xobde Dios xaa zee.¡Te lo re nu, Xaa Nabeyy!
Nu nzhekla na lee Xaa Nabeyy kanap rese gu lo yalnkela cheen xaa.
<font color=teal>Yech mrop kwaan mkee Pab lo re xaa yezh Corinto</font>Dix cheen PabNa nak Pab, nu na nak tub re xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist nel sbaa nzhekla Dios. Tubka kwaan wech Timoteo, kakee na yech ne lo re gu, xaa mle nambey Jesús, xaa nzho yezh Corinto, nu lo re xaa mle nambey Jesús, xaa nzho dub naz ba pa nak yizhyo cheen Acaya.
Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa nak Xuz be, nu Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, luu xaa yalnkela cheen xaa lo re gu nu le xaa zee kwi wen re gu.
Bid kwaan mded PabGool be lo Dios, xaa nak Xuz be nu xaa nak Xuz Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, nel lee xaa nak xaa nlesla ne re be, nu Dios nak xaa tubka nseleyy be.
Nu nseleyy Dios be gorna kaded be bid, zee noka re be seleyy re xaa kaded bid; nu seleyy be xaa kwentaxa mseleyy Dios be.
Nel nded be bid mod mded Jesucrist bid, sbaaka nseleyy Dios be kwent cheen Jesucrist.
Kwaanzee chelee nu nded nu bid, nded nu bid zee lee re gu leyy, nu le gu gan yalnaban kwaan tira; nu cheleeya Dios nseleyy nu, naka zee noka lee re gu leyy, zee noka gu ye ded bid kwaan nded nu.
Kwaan né nu nak, modxa nded gu bid sbaaka nded nu bid, per sbaa noka re gu nseleyy Dios modxa nseleyy xaa nu.
Wech nu bzan, nzhekla nu ne gu gro doo bid mded nu yizhyo Asia. Kwaane nak tub yalzi, tub yalzi kwaan mer nyent mod ngle nu gan ngded nu, nu axta mle nu xgab ngyet nu.
Mzak nu nak nu mod tub xaa naklakwent yet. Per kwaane mle sirb zee mseed nu nawiit nu leeka lo nu, sinka nkin wii nu lo Dios, xaa nseban re xaa ngut.
Dios mkanap nu leezha nzhekla re xaa ngut nu, nu ne nu tubka sbaa kanap xaa nu lo rese kwaan.
Nu chelee re gu naab gu lo Dios, telisa kanap xaa nu; nu seeka zyen xaa nzaa dixkix lo Dios mod mkanap xaa re nu, kwent cheen kwaan ngunaab zyen xaa lo xaa.
Chozhiin nangwat Pab lo re xaa yezh CorintoNzeen nu naz leen lextoo nu lee rese kwaan mle nu lo re myet yizhyo, mle nuya tub mod nali nu kwaan dub lextoo nu, nel Dios mle yudar nu, zee masra mle nuya lo re gu. Nu kwaanzee nix doo nzhak lextoo nu, nel kwaan mle nu lo re gu namlet nuya mod nzhak xaa yizhyo ne nel Dios mle yudar nu.
Nu lo re xkyech nu nankeet nu nik tub kwaan zee kade nu gu, zee nalata yek gu. Nzhekla na klar laya yek gu.
Nixa nal gor ne nanlabeyyt gu nu wen wen, nzhekla na leezha bare Jesucrist Xaa Nabeyy be, lee re gu nzho mod to gu yalxwa cheen re nu modxa noka re nu to yalxwa cheen re gu.
Nel nela na sbaa naka, nzhekla na yilotlaka lo re gu ngal na, zee nzho mod ngzhaal re be stuba, ngak rop welt.
Kwaanzee mle na xgab ngdeed na lo re gu gorna ngwa na naz yizhyo Macedonia nu noka ngdeed na lo re gu gorna ngbare na stuba, zee ngle re gu yudar na nga na naz yizhyo Judea.
Nu gorna mle na xgab ngle na kwaane, mle wen na xgaba. Nu nanlet na xgab mod re xaa yizhyo ne, xaa mbezh le xaa tub kwaan nu nanlet xaaya.
Nel lee Dios nali nak lo rese kwaan, sbaaka re nu nali nak nu lo rese kwaan nii nu lo re gu.
Nel leezha yon nu Silban nu Timoteo nzaa nu kwent cheen Jesucrist, Xgann Dios lo re gu, mzaa nuya tub mod nali, nel tubka wli nak Jesucrist.
Nel rese kwaan né Dios, telisa nle xaaya. Nu snee kwent cheen Jesucrist nzho mod yé be: “Sbaa gaka”, nu sbaa nzho mod gool be lo Dios.
Nu Dios nak xaa nle zee nye nzo rese be lo Jesucrist, nu mleey xaa be zee tubka yo be kwaan Jesucrist,
nu mzaa xaa Mbi Naban cheen xaa lo be zee luu nak be xaa xaa, nu sbaa nzho mod ne be telisa kayaa be re kwaan zaa xaa lo be gwluzh.
Nu chelee na zeeraka ya na yezh Corinto mrop welt mod nak xgab cheen na, zoob na Dios mod tub testig, nagat na nel nanzheklat na galno na re gu.
Nu nanzheklat nu nabeyy nu gu xomod nzhaal ngwii gu lo Dios, nel nye nzo gu lo Dios ngwii gu lo xaa, nebse nzhekla nu le nu yudar gu zee chul gak lextoo gu.
Kwaanzee nanzheklat na ngal na lo re gu stuba, zee le na gak nales lextoo gu.
Nel chelee na le nales na lextoo gu, ¿cho le zee gak chul lextoo na, cheleeya nanakta re gu?
Kwaanzee mkee na yech zee lo gu, nel nanzheklat na ngal na zee gak nales lextoo na, ne na xomod nle gu. Mas wen ble nix gu lextoo na zee nix gak lextoo rese be.
Per gorna mkee na yech zee, nyentra gan lextoo na nu nales doo ngok lextoo na, nu axta mbinn na. Per nanzheklat na kee naya zee gak nales lextoo re gu, nel mkee naya zee ne gu wlipa nkela na gu.
Pab mles lextoo ne xaa mchaal sa xuz yiloNu chelee tub xaa mle zee ngok nales lextoo na, nanebt lextoo na mle nales xaa, noka mle nales xaa lextoo rese gu. Nii na kwaane: Nanzheklat na gak na tub xaa nakap doo lo xaa.
Nal nzhaal les lextoo gu ne gu xaa zee, nu seleyy gu xaa, napa nales doo nzhak lextoo xaa.
Kwaanzee nzhaal luu gu lo xaa xomod nkela gu xaa.
Nel mkeela na kwaane lo re gu yilo, zee ne na nen che zon gu xtizh na kwaan mnabeey na.
Lee xaa kwaan nles lextoo gu ne gu, noka na nles lextoo ne xaa. Nu nles lextoo na ne na xaa kwent cheen Jesucrist, zee wen yo rese gu.
Nu snee mles lextoo na ne na xaa, zee nyent mod le Maxuu gan lo re be, nel nela be xomod nak re xgab cheen Maxuu.
Pab nle xgab TitoGorna mzhin na yezh Troas, za na kwent cheen wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist, ngune na nzho mod chul kee na xchiin Xaa Nabeyy baa.
Per nyent gan lextoo na ngza na kwent nel nanguzhalt wech Tito lo na, nel zeeraka bare xaa lo re gu. Kwaanzee mroo na baa nu mya na naz yizhyo Macedonia.
Xomod nak kwent cheen Jesucrist¡Dixkix Dios, xaa tubka nle zee nyent mod le stub xaa gan lo nu, kwent cheen kwaan mle Jesucrist! Nu kwent cheen nu nle Dios nrech kwent cheen Jesucrist zee labeyy re xaa xaa, kwaan nzharech zyen doo yezh mod tub bech;
nel Dios mle zee lee re nu nak mod bech cheen Jesucrist, kwaan nzhin lo re xaa kale gan yalnaban nu lo re xaa kalux.
Nu lo re xaa kalux, lee bech cheen Jesucrist nak tub bech naxinn doo; per lo re xaa kale gan yalnaban, lee bech ne nak tub bech chul doo nzebech, kwaan nzaa yalnaban kwaan tira. Nu techosa nu nyent mod le nu kwaane.
Nu nakalet re nu negos lo Kwent Chul cheen Dios, modxa nle zyen xaa; per nela Dios, kwaan dub lextoo nu nle nuya, nel Dios mxaal nu zaa nu kwent cheen Jesucrist.
Wdizh kub kwaan mlaa DiosLeezha nii nu kwaane, talbes nzak gu nto nu yalxwa nel mxaal Dios nu lo gu. Nawent nle gu xgab nel nzak gu nkin luu nu tub yech lo gu, nel Jesucrist mzaa yalnabeyy lo nu, kwaanzee nankint naab nu tub yech lo gu gorna zaa nu kwent cheen Jesucrist stub naz yezh.
Re gu nak mod tub yech kwaan nzaa kwent mkayaa na yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist; nel kwent cheen Jesucrist nkee lextoo gu, kwaan nzho mod lab rese xaa nu laya yek xaa.
Leeya nlu lee re gu nak mod tub yech kwaan mkee Jesucrist, nel mkayaa gu kwent kwaan mzaa nu lo gu. Gu nak mod tub yech kwaan namkeet kwaan lap, sinka gu nak mod tub yech kwaan mkee kwaan Mbi Naban cheen Dios, xaa wlipa mban; nu re wdizh ne namkeet xaaya lo ke mod kwaan mzaa Dios lo Ches, sinka lee xaa mkeeya leen lextoo re myet.
Delant lo Dios klar doo mlu Jesucrist kwaane lo nu, leeya nak kwaan wli.
Nyent mod yé nu techosa nu mle re kwaane, nel Dios nzaa re kwaan, zee nzho mod le nuya.
Nel Dios mseed nu nkee nu zhiin lo wdizh kub kwaan mlaa xaa. Nanakta tub wdizh kwaan mkee lo tub ke, mod nak ley kwaan mzaa Dios lo Ches; leeya nak wdizh kwaan mkee Mbi Naban leen lextoo re myet. Lee ke kwaan mkee ley lo nle nzhet myet, per lee Mbi Naban cheen Dios nzaa yalnaban lo myet.
Lee ley kwaan mkee lo ke, mzaa Dios kwaan tub xni gro doo lo Ches nu kwaanzee lee xey nu, xaa dii cheen Israel, nyent mod wii garlo Ches, nel nla doo xni garlo xaa. Per nixa nkee xni ne garlo xaa nyuyya. Lee ley zee nak kwaan nle zee nzhet re myet. Nu Dios mzaa kwaane tub mod chul doo,
per mas chul mlaa xaa wdizh kub cheen Mbi Naban.
Nel lee ley kwaan naab kwent lo re myet, Dios mzaaya tub mod chul doo, ¡per mas chul doo mlaa xaa wdizh kub kwaan nle zee nali nzo be lo Dios!
Nel lee xni cheen ley kwaan yilo, nik tik nanzhakta kwenta xni cheen wdizh kub.
Nu lee xni cheen ley kwaan mzaa Dios lo Ches myuyy, per lee xni cheen wdizh kub grora nu tira nanyuyyt.
Nu nel ne nu wli kwaane, kwaanzee kwaan dub lextoo nu nzaa nu kwenta lo gu.
Nu nanlet nu mod mle Ches, leezha msaaw xaa garlo xaa kwaan tub lee ler, zee lee re xey nu nawiit xomod nzheyuyy xni garlo xaa.
Nu noka myaww yek re xey nu. Nu nixa axta nal nanlat wdizh gox ne yek re sawlazh na, xaa Israel, nel nanzaat xaa yek xaa gon xaaya leezha nlab xaaya. Nu naka mod nsaaw tub lee ler yek xaa nu nanlaata wii xaa, nel zer kwe xaa ler ne yek xaa; nu kwaane yiib leezha wii xaa lo Jesucrist.
Kwaanzee axta mbizh ne gorna nzhon xaa nlab xaa ley kwaan mzaa Dios lo Ches, seetaka nsaaw ler zee yek xaa, zee nanlat xtizh Dios yek xaa.
Per gorna lee tub xaa nzelo ngwii lo Xaa Nabeyy ngiib ler zee yek xaa, zee laya yek xaa.
Nu lee Xaa Nabeyy nak Mbi Naban; nu leezha nabeyy Mbi Naban cheen Xaa Nabeyy lextoo xaa, mla xaa lo ley.
Kwaanzee lee lo re be nyentra ler kwaan nsaaw garlo be, nak be mod tub spej kwaan nlu xni cheen Xaa Nabeyy, nu Mbi Naban cheen Xaa Nabeyy kachee be, zee gak be kwenta lee xaa, zee kad mbizh nzhiroo be lo xni cheen xaa.
Nu mlaa nu re yalnto kwaan nle xaa xlaan; nixa nankadet nu, nixa nancheet nu xtizh Dios. Dios ne wen, wli nu re kwaan nzhedizh nu, snee lee re myet nzho mod ne xomod nak kwaan wli.
Nu chelee wdizh chul kwaan nzaa nu kwent lo re myet, nanlat yek xaa, naka nel leeka lee xaa nle zee nya xaa lo ki.
Nel lee Maxuu, xaa nabeyy yizhyo ne, mle syeg re xaa nanet wii lo Jesucrist, zee nyent mod wii xaa lo xni cheen wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist, xaa nak lal ke Dios.
Nanzaat nu kwent cheen leeka nu, lee nu nzaa kwent cheen Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be. Nebse nak nu xaa nkee zhiin lo re gu, kwent cheen Jesucrist.
Nel leeka Dios, xaa ngunii zee yo xni lo yalnakaw, nak xaa mle yo xni lextoo be, zee nzho mod wii be lo xni cheen Dios, kwaan nak Jesucrist.
Yalnaban kwaan nzho leen xkwerp beNu lee xni ne nzho leen lextoo be. Per mod tub yas yo nak be, zee luu lee yalngezh ne nak cheen Dios nu nanakta cheen be.
Nu nixa nzhin yalzi lo be mod tub kwaan ntaaw yas, per nanakta tub kwaan lux be. Nu nixa nle doo be xgab per wen lextoo be.
Nu nixa nrenal xaa be, per natechot be nzo, nu nixa gobi xaa be per naluxt xaa be.
Nu nixa pa nzha be nzho ryez yet be, zee luu yalnaban cheen xaa leen kwerp cheen be.
Nel lee re be tubka nzho reyez yet be kwent cheen Jesucrist, zee luu yalnaban cheen xaa leen kwerp cheen be, kwaan yet.
Nu nii na, konxa nzo yalgut kwaan re nu, seeka nzo yalnaban kwaan re gu.
Nel stub pa nzhé: “Ngwii na lo Dios, kwaanzee nza na kwent cheen xaa”, zee snee nzaa re be kwent cheen Jesucrist nel ngwii be lo Dios.
Nel ne be Dios mseban Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be lo yalgut, noka seban xaa re be kwaan lee xaa, zee wee xaa rese be zee zo be kwaan lee xaa.
Rese kwaane mded zee chul yo rese gu, nu snee zyenra xaa kayaa kwaan nzhekla Dios zaa xaa lo xaa nu tubka zaa xaaya lo rese be, sneeka zyen xaa zaa dixkix lo Dios lo rese kwaan chul kwaan mzaa xaa.
Kwaanzee nalet be xgab. Nixa yizata mbizh nzheyex kwerp cheen be per lee lextoo be yizata mbizh nyera nzheyak lo Dios.
Nagrot nak bid kwaan nded be nu nadiita tira, per leeya nle kwaan chul lextoo be zee kano be tub yalnaban kwaan tira, tub yalnaban pa nabeyy xni cheen Dios, kwaan chulra lo rese kwaan.
Kwaanzee nangwiit be lo re kwaan nlu, lee be ngwii lo re kwaan nanlut, nel lee re kwaan nlu lux, per lee re kwaan nanlut tira naluxt.
Mod zhee kwerp cheen beLo yizhyo ne lee kwerp cheen be nak mod tub ramad kwaan nlux. Per nela be gorna luxa, Dios zaa stuba kwaan tira naluxt lo be naz leen yiba, kwaan nak mod tub yoo kwaan namdexkwaat myet.
Kwaanzee nal nzilextoo be nzho be leen kwerp cheen be, nel nzhekla be segak be be kwaan kwerp kub kwaan tira naluxt,
kwaan gak be mod tub ler zee nagakcheeyt be.
Nu leezha seetaka nzho be leen kwerp cheen be, nales doo nzhak lextoo be nel nanzheklat be gak cheey be, nel nzhekla be gak kwerp cheen be kwaan nzho naz leen yiba zee lee re kwaan yizhyo ne lux lo yalnaban naz yiba.
Nu snee mdexkwaa Dios be, nu leeka xaa nak xaa mzaa Mbi Naban yo leen lextoo be mod tub nseyn zee kayaa be re kwaan né xaa zaa xaa lo be.
Kwaanzee tubka yo gan lextoo be. Nu ne be leezha mbanaka be leen kwerp ne, nayot be yiba kwaan Xaa Nabeyy be.
Nal ngwii be lo xaa, nixa nanyunt xaa lo be.
Kwaanzee nzhaal yakla be, nel ne be, leezha laa be kwerp ne zee nya be lo Xaa Nabeyy be.
Kwaanzee tubka nkwaan be le be kwaan nyula Xaa Nabeyy be, nexa chelee be mban be o chelee be ngut be.
Nel rese be telisa zhin zaa kwent lo Jesucrist, zee kad tub be kayaa lo Dios kwaan nzhaal kayaa be, kwaan wen o kwaan nawent, modxa mle be leezha nzoka be leen xkwerp be lo yizhyo ne.
Wdizh kwaan le kwi chul re xaaNu nzheb nu ne nu Xaa Nabeyy, kwaanzee nseed nu stub naz xaa xomod zheb xaa ne xaa Xaa Nabeyy. Nlabeyy wen Dios re nu, nu nzhekla na noka re gu labeyy wen gu nu.
Naniit na kwaane zee le gu xgab wen re nu, sinka nii na kwaane zee nzho mod keb gu lo re xaa nto yalxwa nel nzhak xaa, per nangwiit xaa cho kwaan nzho leen lextoo xaa.
Lee yalnkela cheen Jesucrist nabeyy leen lextoo be, nel ne be lee xaa ngut kwent cheen rese be, nu kwaanzee naka mod rese be ngut.
Kwaanzee Jesucrist ngut kwent cheen rese be, zee rese be mban; nu nambant be zee le be kwaan nzhekla be; mban be zee le be kwaan nzhekla Jesucrist, xaa ngut nu mroban kwent cheen rese be.
Kwaanzee nanzhaalt wiira be lo re myet mod tub xaa yizhyo, nixa yilo mlu Jesucrist mod myet lo be, per nal nangwiitra be lo xaa mod tub myet.
Kwaanzee lee xaa nzo kwaan Jesucrist, nak xaa kub. Lee re kwaan gox mdedla lo xaa, lee re kwaan nal nak kwaan kub lo xaa.
Nu rese kwaane nak xchiin Dios. Nebse kwent cheen Jesucrist mle Dios zee chul kwi re be kwaan lee xaa. Nu mzaa xaa zhiin ne lo nu le nu zee rese xaa kwi chul kwaan lee xaa.
Kwaan nii na nak, lee Dios kale kwi chul re myet kwaan lee xaa kwent cheen Jesucrist, nu sbaa nanaabt xaa kwent lo re jwalt cheen re myet, nu lo nu mlaa xaa zhiin ne zee zaa nu kwent cheen re kwaane.
Kwaanzee mkayaa nu yalnabeyy zaa nu kwent cheen Jesucrist; nu naab nu zee kwi chul rese myet kwaan lee xaa, kwent cheen Jesucrist.
Dios mzhib rese jwalt cheen be tich Jesucrist, xaa namzeebt nik tub jwalt, zee mdix xaa rese jwalt cheen be, zee kwent cheen xaa nzho mod gak be nali kwenta Dios.
Lee nal, nel nkee nu xchiin Dios, naab nu lo re gu kayaa gu re kwaan nzelazh Dios, nu nakayaat guya mod tub kwaan sbaasa.
Nel lo Xkyech Dios nzhé Dios:Leezha nzho mod le na yudar lu,mroo na xjabor lu,nu mbin na xtizh lu;mbizh kwaan nle xaa gan yalnaban.Bwii gu, nalzhe nak mbizh kwaan nroo Dios xjabor be. ¡Nalzhe nak mbizh le xaa gan yalnaban!
Nu nik tub welt zer le nu zee ralnii tub xaa lo xcheen Dios, zee snee nyent mod nii xaa nawent nak xchiin nu.
Per nela gu xomod nle nu rese kwaan mod xmos Dios, axta nyela nu nded nu re bid nu re yalzi,
nu mzaa xaaya yenn nu, mlo xaa nu lozhyib, nayii xaa ngune xaa nu, mkee doo nu zhiin, nu namlat mkaal lo nu pa mlaz nu yaal, nu mded nu bid lo yalnlaan.
Noka nlu lee nu nak xmos Dios lo re kwaan nali nle nu, lo re kwaan nzhak nu, nu mod nyela nu nded nu bid, nu mod nadoo nak nu, nlu nzho Mbi Naban cheen Dios lextoo nu, nel nkela nu wechxinn nu.
Noka nlu nak nu xmos Dios nel nii nu kwaan wli, nu nlu nkano nu yalngezh cheen Dios nseed nu re myet nu ndildiizhka nu kwaan myet.
Lak mbizh ngwii re xaa respet lo nu zlak mbizh nayii xaa ne nu, lak mbizh nzhedizh nawent xaa nu, zlak mbizh nzhedizh wen xaa nu. Mod tub xaa nkade nle xaa nu, nixa kwaan wli nii nu.
Nle xaa nu mod tub xaa nanlabeyyt xaa, nixa nlabeyy wen xaa nu. Nle xaa nu mod tub xaa ngut per seetaka mban nu; nchezi xaa nu, per nanzhuta xaa nu.
Nle xaa nales nzhak nu per tubka nix nzhak lextoo nu; nlu nu mod tub xaa prob per nle nu zee ngok rik zyen xaa; nal nik tub kwaan nankanot nu per nixa sneeya rese kwaan nkano nu.
Wech nu bzan, xaa yezh Corinto, ngunii nu duzna kwaan wli lo re gu, nu noka kwaan dub lextoo nu nkela nu re gu.
Per namlaat nu kela nu re gu per lee re gu nankelat gu re nu.
Kwaanzee, naab na lo re gu mod naab tub xaa lo xinn xaa, bkela gu nu mod nkela nu gu, modxa nzhaal kela gu.
Be nak yidoo cheen Dios xaa mbanNyent mod yo tub xaa Jesús kwaan tub xaa nanakt xaa Jesús, kwaanzee nyent mod yo kwaan wen lo re kwaan nawent, nu nyent mod zhaal xni kwaan yalnakaw.
Nyent mod yo Jesucrist kwaan Maxuu, nu nixa nachult yo tub xaa Jesús kwaan tub xaa nanakt xaa Jesús, nel nalalt nle xaa xgab.
Nu nik tub kwaan nanakt lal lo yidoo cheen Dios nu lo yidoo cheen re maj. Nel re be nak mod yidoo cheen Dios, xaa mban. Mod né Dios:Yoo na kwaan re xaa ne,nu nzheze na kwaan re xaa ne;na gak Xdios xaa,nu lee xaa gak xaa na.
Nu kwaanzee noka né Xaa Nabeyy:Broo gu lo re xaa ba,bachii gu lo xaa,nagalt gu kwaan nanzhult lo Dios,zee kayaa na re gu,
nu na gak Xuz rese gu,nu gu gak re xgaan na nu re xchap na,snee né Xaa Nabeyy, xaa nkano gro doo yalngezh.
Kwaanzee wech nu bzan, xaa nkedoola na, nel nguné Dios zaa Dios re kwaane lo be, zee nzhaal zo nzhul kwerp cheen be nu mbi naban cheen be lo Dios, zee tira gak be xaa Dios, nel nzheb be ne be Dios.
Mzobdiizh re xaa yezh Corinto re kwaan mkee Pab¡Bkela gu nu! Nik tub kwaan nawent zer le nu lo nik tub xaa, nixa zer le nu zee le tub xaa kwaan nawent, nixa zer kade nu nik tub xaa.
Nanaabt na kwent lo gu. Mod nguniila na lo gu yilo, tant nkedoola nu gu, nzhekla nu yo nu tubka kwaan re gu, nu axta listla nzo nu yet nu kwent cheen re gu.
Axta gorna mzhin nu yizhyo Macedonia, nik chep zer le nu deskans, rese pa nzhin nu nted xaa nu yalzi nu tubka nchaal dil xaa nu re pa nded nu, nu tubka nzheb nu.
Per Dios, xaa nzaa balor lextoo re myet, xaa nyent balor lextoo, mle zee ngu balor lextoo re nu gorna mzhin Tito lo re nu.
Kwaanzee chul doo ngok lextoo nu mwii nu lo xaa, nu noka chul doo ngok lextoo nu nel chul doo nzhak lextoo Tito nel mseleyy gu xaa. Noka lee xaa mzaa kwent lo nu, lee re gu nzhekla doo ne lo na, nu né xaa xomod nales nzhak lextoo gu nu nle gu xgab na, kwaane mas chul mle lextoo na.
Nixa lee yech kwaan mkee na lo re gu yilo mle nales lextoo gu, nyent cho nzhak lextoo na. Ngok nales lextoo na gorna ne na lee yech zee mle nales lextoo gu lak mbizh;
per nal chul nzhak lextoo na mkee na yech zee. Nu nanzhak chult lextoo na nel mle nalesa lextoo gu, chul nzhak lextoo na nel mle nales yech lextoo gu, zee mlaa gu kwaan nawent kwaan mle gu. Leezha mleya nales doo lextoo re gu tub mod nyula Dios, nu snee lee nu namlet nik tub kwaan nawent lo re gu.
Nel leezha ngok nales lextoo tub xaa mod nyula Dios, zee le xaa gan yalnaban, nu nik tub kwaan nankint le xaa xgab. Per lee yalnales lo yizhyo ne nle zee nya xaa lo yalgut.
Nyula Dios mod ngok nales lextoo gu. ¡Zyen doo kwaan gro mleya leen lextoo gu! Nel mbin gu kwaan mkee na lo gu yilo zee myaan gu mted gu bid xaa mle kwaan nawent, nel nayii gu ne gu kwaan nawent kwaan mle xaa nu mzheb gu ne gu yalnayii cheen Dios; kwaanzee nal nzhekla gu le gu re kwaan nali. Nu kwaane nlu lee re gu nalalt nzhedizh kwaan lee xaa, xaa sbaa mle kwaan nawent.
Nu nii na, gorna mkee na yech zee, namkeet naya lo xaa mle kwaan nawent, nu nixa lo xaa mded bid lo kwaan nawent kwaan mle xaa; sinka lo re gu mkee naya zee luu Dios xomod nzhaal gon gu xtizh nu.
Nu kwaane mseleyy doo nu.Kwaanzee chul nzhak lextoo nu, nu mas chul ngok lextoo nu leezha mbin nu mle gu ngoknix lextoo Tito, nu nal nanlet xaa xgab re gu.
Nu namlet gu zee roo xkalnto na, nel nzhé na lo Tito chul nto na yalxwa cheen re gu. Nu snee wli rese kwaan mlu nu lo re gu, sbaaka wli kwaan nzhé nu lo Tito.
Nu lee Tito mas nkela gu gorna nselazh Tito xomod mbin gu xtizh nu, nu xomod chul mkayaa gu xaa kwaan dub lextoo gu nu kwaan yalnacheb.
¡Nu chul doo nzhak lextoo na, nel ne na lee re gu nle re kwaan nzhaal le gu!
Xomod chul top xaa gonLee nal wech nu bzan, nzhekla nu ne gu xomod mkee Dios zhiin lextoo re xaa Jesús, xaa yizhyo Macedonia.
Nu nixa zyen bid kwaan nagan mded xaa, chul doo nzhak lextoo re xaa; nu nixa prob xaa, mod tub xaa rik mzaa xaa gon.
Nu nzho mod za na kwent lee xaa mzaa gon kwaan dub lextoo xaa, nu mzaa xaa re kwaan nzho mod zaa xaa nu axta kwaan nagan zaa xaa, mzaa xaa.
Nu mnaab xaa lo re nu zee nzho mod le xaa yudar re xaa mle nambey Jesús, xaa prob.
Nu mzaa xaa axta paro namlet nu xgab, yilotlaka mzaa xaa leeka lee xaa lo Xaa Nabeyy, mod tub gon kwaan dub gan cheen xaa, sbaa mle xaa yudar nu lo xchiin nu, noka kwaane nak mod tub gon, nu mlela xaaya modxa nzhekla Dios.
Kwaanzee ngunaab nu lo Tito, zee naab xaa gon kwaan mzelo re gu ntop gu nzhala lak mbee.
Re gu nak xaa masra kwaan nle: mod ngwiira gu lo Jesús, mod nzhedizhra gu stub naz diizh kwaan nagakt gu, nu mod nzhakra gu, nu nzhora mas gan lextoo gu kee gu xchiin Dios. Kwaanzee nzhaal zaara gu gon, kwaane nak tub kwaan wen le gu.
Nu nanabeyyt na gu zaa gu gon ne, nebse nzhekla na ne na che wlipa nak yalnkela cheen gu, zee mlaa na luu gu yalnkela cheen gu lo re xaa Jesús, xaa yizhyo Macedonia.
Nel nela re gu lee Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, kwaan yalnkela cheen xaa, ngok xaa tub xaa prob, nixa rik doo nak xaa, zee kwaan yalprob cheen xaa, gak rik re be.
Kwaanzee snee nii na lo gu. Nzha tub liin lee re gu mzelo mzaa gon; nu kwaan dub lextoo gu mzelo gu mzaa guya, kwaanzee nal nzhaal yilo top guya.
Nel mzelola gu mtop guya kwaan dub lextoo gu, gulo btop guya.
Nel chelee tub xaa nzhekla zaa gon, Dios nkayaa kwaan nzho mod zaa xaa. Dios nanaabt tub kwaan nankanot xaa.
Nu nanzheklat na zaa gu gon, zee yo jwalt kwaan lo re gu zee lee stub gu nkano zyen kwaan;
kwaan nzhekla na nak lal kwaan kano re be. Lee nal lee re gu nkano kwaan nankanot re xaa ba, per stub welt lee xaa kano kwaan nankanot gu, nu snee lal yo re gu.
Modxa nkee lo Xkyech Dios: “Xaa mtop zyena namlaketraya lo xaa, nu lee xaa mtop chepse nangujwaltraya lo xaa”.
Tito nu xaa nzha kwaan lee xaaDixkix Dios nel noka Tito nkela xaa re gu kwenta na.
Nel mzeyal xaa le xaa zhiin ne, nel tant nle doo xaa xgab re gu, nal nzhekla xaa yaadsewii xaa lo re gu stuba.
Nu leeka re xaa Jesús mleey xaa, zee ya xaa kwaan re nu le xaa yudar nu yilaa nu gon ne lo re stub naz xaa Jesús, zee ne rese xaa zee wlipa nkela be xaa, zee chul luu Xaa Nabeyy.
Snee nzhekla nu le nu, zee nyent mod gaazh xaa kwaan tich nu lo zyen doo gon kwaan katop gu.
Kwaanzee tubka nkwaan nu le nu re kwaan nali, nu nanebt delant lo Dios noka delant lo re myet.
Nu kwaan re xaa ne, xaal nu stub wech, tub xaa mlu nali doo nak xaa lo rese kwaan; nu nal nzho gan lextoo xaa yiid xaa lo gu, nel ne xaa xomod nak re gu.
Nu chelee tub xaa nabdizh lo re gu, cho nak Tito, yé gu lo re xaa, lee xaa nak tub xmig na nu tubka nkee rop nu zhiin, zee nle nu yudar re gu. Nu chelee xaa nabdizh xaa cho nak rop wech ne, xaa nzha kwaan Tito, guzh gu lo xaa, lee xaa nak tub xaa mxaal re xaa Jesús, zee gool re myet lo Jesucrist.
Nu kwaanzee blu gu yalnkela cheen gu lo re xaa Jesús, zee ne xaa wli nak mod mto nu yalxwa cheen gu lo xaa; snee luu yalnkela cheen gu lo re xaa ne.
Gon kwaan xaal xaa lo re xaa Jesús, xaa probLee gon kwaan xaal be lo re xaa mle nambey Jesús, xaa prob, nankintra nii na lo re gu xomod nzhaal top guya,
nel ne wen na lee gu topa. Nel tubka nto na yalxwa cheen gu lo re xaa Jesús, xaa yizhyo Macedonia, nel kwaan dub lextoo gu ntop guya. Axta dub liin zee, lee re gu xaa yizhyo Acaya, nzhekla gu zaa gu gon ne. Zee snee ngune re xaa Macedonia kwaane, zee noka re xaa mzelo ntop gon.
Nu xaal na Tito kwaan xchop wech ne, zee zo list gu kwaan re gon mod mza na kwent lo re xaa Macedonia,
napa lee lak wech, xaa Macedonia, ya kwaan na lo re gu nu yiid nu lo gu. Nu chelee gu nalist nkano gu gon cheen gu, zee ton nu ne nu gu, zee noka re gu ton wii leeka lo re gu.
Kwaanzee ngunaab na lo yon wech ne zee yilo yasewii xaa lo re gu, le xaa yudar gu top gu gon, kwaan né gu zaa gu. Kwaanzee nzhaal listla nzho gon cheen gu gorna zhin nu, zee naka tub gon kwaan zaa gu kwaan dub lextoo gu, nu nanakta tub gon kwaan zaa gu kwaan lajwers.
Bselazh gu kwaane: “Xaa kwaan nanzhaant gro, chepse yalgon ntop xaa; nu xaa kwaan gro nzhaan, zyen yalgon ntop xaa”.
Kad tub gu nzhaal zaa kwaan mlela gu xgab zaa gu, nu nazaat guya lajwers, nel Dios nkela xaa kwaan nzaaya kwaan dub lextoo.
Dios nzho mod zelazh zyen doo kwaan lo re be, zee tubka kano be kwaan nkin be, nu axta lakeya le be yudar re xaa prob.
Nel lee xtizh Dios nzhé:Zyen kwaan mzaa Dios lo re xaa prob,nel tubka nali nak xaa.
Dios nak xaa nzaa ben kwaan nxeen myet, noka nzaa xaa kwaan nzhaw myet. Lee xaa nzaa lo re be rese ben kwaan nkin be ko be lo yo, nu lee xaa le zee chul rooya, zee masra gon nzho mod zaa be.
Nu nii na, kano be reta lo kwaan, zee nzho mod zaa gu zyen kwaan, kwaan dub lextoo gu. Nu lee gon kwaan xaal gu kwaan nu, le zee zyen xaa zaa dixkix lo Dios.
Nel gorna zaa nuya lo re xaa mle nambey Jesús, nanebt zaa guya lo xaa nel nkin xaaya, noka leeya le zee zaa xaa dixkix lo Dios.
Zee lee re xaa gool lo Dios, nel gon ne luu lo re xaa lee re gu wlipa nzhon wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist. Nu snee noka re xaa zaa dixkix lo Dios mod nzaa re guya kwaan dub lextoo gu, kwent cheen xaa nu kwent cheen rese xaa.
Zee noka kela xaa gu nu naab xaa lo Dios kwaan dub lextoo xaa zee chul yo gu, nel lee yalnkela cheen Dios, kwaan gro doo nak, nlu leen lextoo gu.
¡Dixkix Dios nel mzelazh xaa tub kwaan gro doo lo re be, kwaan nyent mod zaa be kwent kwaan wdizh!
Yalnabeyy kwaan mzaa Jesucrist lo PabLak xaa mbezh leezha nzo na lo re gu, nzheb doo na nii na, nixa nakap doo nkee na lo yech leezha nzo na zit lo re gu. Kwaanzee ngunaab na kwaane lo re gu kwaan yalnadoo nu kwaan yalnkela cheen Jesucrist.
Gorna yal na yasewii na lo re gu, nalet gu re kwaan nanzhaalt le gu, zee nakint yii na lo gu. Talbes nkin nii na nakap lo re xaa mbezh, lee nu nzhedizh kwenta myet yizhyo ne; nu list nzo na zhaal na kwaan re xaa snee mbezh.
Wli lee re be nzhi lo yizhyo ne, per nandilt be mod ndil xaa yizhyo ne.
Nadilt be kwaan re yiib yizhyo ne, sinka kwaan yalngezh cheen Dios ndil be, zee nzho mod lux be re pa nzho yalngezh cheen Maxuu,
nu snee nlux be rese xgab yiya nu rese yalnto kwaan nle zee nalabeyyt xaa Dios. Kwaanzee ndil be kwaan rese xgab yizhyo ne zee luux rese xgab kwaan nanakt cheen Jesucrist.
Gorna yilo gon gu xtizh nu, zee listla nzo nu ted nu rese xaa kwaan nanzaat yek gon xtizh Jesucrist bid.
Gwii gu xomod naka. Chelee tub xaa nzak nak xaa tub xaa Jesucrist, nzhaal ne xaa, noka re nu nak xaa Jesucrist.
Nu chol nto na yalxwa lo yalnabeyy kwaan mkayaa nu lo Jesucrist, nantont na, nel Xaa Nabeyy mzaa yalnabeyy ne lo na, zee le na zee nye zo gu lo xaa, nu tira nalet na tub kwaan nawent lo gu.
Nzho lak xaa nii lee yech kwaan mkee na nakap doo nii, per leezha nzo na lo gu nak na tub xaa nadoo nu nadoo nii na.
Per xaa kwaan nii kwaane, nzhaal ne xaa xomod nkee nu lo yech leezha nzo nu zit lo re gu, sbaaka le nu re kwaane gorna zo nu kwaan re gu.
Nankwaant nu wii nu xomod nzhak stub naz re xaa, xaa nto doo yalxwa, nel leezha nzhekla xaa wii xaa xomod nzhak wechxinn xaa, nle xaa tub kwaan nachan.
Per lee re nu nantot nu yalxwa tub mod nanzhaalt to nuya. Lee nu nzhaal to yalxwa mod mxaal Dios nu lo re gu.
Kwaanzee nanlet nu tub kwaan nanzhaalt le nu leezha nto nu yalxwa cheen re gu, nel re nu nak xaa mzaa wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist lo re gu yilotlaka.
Nu nantot nu yalxwa lo xchiin stub naz xaa. Lee re nu nzhekla kee zhiin lo re gu, zee mas wii gu lo Jesucrist nu zee mas roo xchiin nu lo re gu.
Nu sbaaka nzhekla nu cheech nu wdizh chul re yezh kwaan nzhi mas zit lazh gu. Per tira nantot nu yalxwa lo tub kwaan nanakt xchiin nu, kwaan mle stub xaa.
Chelee tub be nzhekla to yalxwa, to be yalxwa lo xcheen Xaa Nabeyy.
Leezha lee tub xaa nto yalxwa cheen leeka lee xaa nu xomod chul nle xaa, nanonta. Per leezha nto Xaa Nabeyy yalxwa cheen tub xaa, zeesi nona.
Xaa nawlit mkayaa yalnabeyy lo JesucristNachan snee nii na, per nzhaal nii naya, kwaanzee naab na zee yela gu gon guya.
Nzhak selos na kwent cheen re gu, nu yalselos ne nyaad naz lo Dios. Nel naka mod mza na gu zee chelya gu kwaan sa be, xaa nak Jesucrist; nu nzhekla na za na gu lo xaa mod tub ngwnaa me zer chaal xaabyi.
Per nzheb na, napa lee Maxuu kakade gu kwaan yalnzhak cheen xaa, modxa mkade xaa Ev, napa sbaaka kakade xaa re gu, zee laa gu mod nkela gu Jesucrist nu mod ngwii gu lo xaa.
Kwaanzee mkayaa re gu rese xaa nzhin lo gu, xaa nawlit nzaa kwent cheen Jesús, kwaan namzaat nu kwent lo gu. Nu kwaan dub lextoo gu mkayaa gu kwent nawlit cheen Mbi Naban, zee mkayaa gu stub wdizh kwaan nawlit, kwaan nzak gu nyaadno yalnaban. Tira nanagant mkayaa gu re kwaane.
Per ne na lal non na kwaan re xaa nreke gu tich, xaa nzak gu mkayaa grora yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist.
Nixa nagakt na wdizh wen na, per nlabeyy na xcheen Dios, nu kwaane tubka mlu nu lo re gu, lo re kwaan mle nu.
¿Cho kwaan nzak gu? ¿Che nawent mle na, mza na kwent cheen wdizh chul lo re gu, nu nangunaabt na nik tub kwaan lo re gu? ¿Che nzak gu, na nak tub xaa nanont nel mza na kwent cheen wdizh chul ne lo gu, nu nangunaabt na kix gu ka na?
Kwaane nak mod mkiib na demi lo re stub naz xaa Jesús, xaa mzaa demi lo na zee za na kwent lo re gu.
Nu leezha mkin na tub kwaan leezha mzo na lo re gu, nangunaabt na nik tub kwaan lo gu, zee nangakt na storb lo re gu. Nel lee re wech, xaa mroo naz yizhyo Macedonia, mzaa kwaan nkin na. Zee mle naya axta paro nzho moda lo na, zee nangakt na storb lo re gu, nu sbaaka le naya dubse nal.
Wlipa na ne Jesucrist. Nyakdoola na lee wdizh ne nzhazhin re yezh cheen Acaya, nu nalet na nik tub kwaan zee saaw na loya.
¿Chozhiin snee nzhedizh na? ¿Che nzak gu naka nel nankelat na re gu? ¡Dios ne, nkela na re gu!
Per seetaka le na kwaan kale na nal, zee nazat na lugar lo re xaa nzhekla to yalxwa lo mod nkee xaa xchiin Dios. Snee nyent mod yé xaa lal nkee rop nu xchiin Dios.
Rese xaa ba nawlit nak xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, nebse nkade xaa, nu nle xaa mod tub xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist.
Nu nanakt kwaane tub kwaan zer ded, che nanet gu leeka mer Maxuu nle mod tub mandad cheen Dios, xaa nzo lo xni;
kwaanzee lee re xmos xaa nzho mod le kwenta tub xaa nkee zhiin lo re kwaan nali. ¡Per xaa ne telisa kix Dios re kwaan nle xaa!
Re bid kwaan mded Pab kwent cheen JesucristBare na nii na lo gu stub welt, nanzhak nachant na; per chelee gu sbaa nle gu xgab, laa gu nii na lo gu kwenta tub xaa nzhak nachan yek, zee noka na nzho mod to chep yalxwa.
Leezha nto na yalxwa ne, naniit na mod tub xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Xaa Nabeyy; mod tub xaa nachan nzhedizh na.
¡Nel tant zyen xaa nto yalxwa mod xaa yizhyo ne zee noka na to chep yalxwa!
Nel nix doo nzhak lextoo re gu nkayaa gu xaa nzhak nachan. Nu nzak gu nzhak gu,
per axta nyela gu nixa nawent nle xaa lo gu: nle xaa gu xmos xaa, noka nkiib xaa re kwaan lo gu, noka nkade xaa gu, noka nto xaa yalxwa cheen gu, nu axta ngazya re xaa tagarlo gu.
¿Che xaa dii Israel nak xaa ba? Seeka na. ¿Che nak xaa ba dii cheen Abraham? Noka na.
¿Che nak xaa ba xaa nkee xchiin Jesucrist? Na mas nkee zhiin ke re xaa ba. (Leezha nii na kwaane, nii na mod nii tub xaa nzhak nachan yek.) Na nzhakee mas zhiin ke re xaa ba, nu nzhego xaa na lozhyib mas zyenra welt ke re xaa ba, mas zyenra welt nzhezaa xaaya yenn na kwaan bins, mas zyenra welt mer nget na kwent cheen Jesucrist.
Tub gaay welt mzaa bins re sawlazh na na, nu galbchiibyeega yaa bins mla xaa tich na kad welt.
Chon welt mzaayag xaa na, nu noka mzaake xaa na. Chon welt mer nglaw na leen nistoo leezha mlux bark, nu mer ngep na nis, nu tub welt axta tub yaal nu tub mbizh mdeed na bid leen nistoo.
Leezha nzha na re yezh: zyen doo welt mer nglaw na leen yuu, zyen doo welt mlewann xaa na, zyen doo welt mrenal re sawlazh na na, nu noka re xaa nanakt xaa sawlazh na. Nu noka mdeed na bid re yezh, nu naz wen, nu leen nistoo, nu lo re xaa nawlit nak xaa Jesús.
Zyen doo zhiin kwaan nagan nzhale na, zyen doo welt nangota na, nzhadeed na yalnlaan, yizhnzhek, zyen doo welt nanzhawt na, ndeed na bid lo nal, nyent ler gak na.
Nu lo re kwaane nzhora mas kwaan, yizata mbizh mas nle na xgab che wen nzha re xaa Jesús.
Chelee tub xaa ne nzak, noka na ne nzak; nu cheleeya nralnii tub xaa lo xcheen Dios, tira nawent nzhak lextoo na.
Nu chelee na to na yalxwa lo tub kwaan, to naya leezha nangezht na nel lee yalngezh cheen Dios nzo kwaan na.
Dios, xaa nak Xuz Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, xaa nzhaal gool re xaa lo yizata mbizh, ne xaa lee na nii kwaan wli.
Leezha mzo na yezh Damasco, lee tub xaa nak zhiin, xaa nkee zhiin lo rey Aretas, mxaal xaa re soldad zee zen xaa na,
per ngu lak xaa mla na kwaan chekwid naz bentant, kwaan nkee naz jwer roo yezh, nu snee mle na gan mxoon na lo re xaa.
Kwaan mlu Dios lo PabNik tub gan nalet na to na yalxwa cheenka na, per nzhaal nii na lo re gu re kwaan mlu Dios lo na nu re kwaan mkayaa na lo Xaa Nabeyy.
Nzhala tub chida liin mbe Dios na naz yiba. Nu nanet na, che mbi naban cheen na ngwa o noka kwerp cheen na, nebse Dios neya.
Per ne na nixa kwaan mbi naban cheen na o kwaan xkwerp na,
ngwa na Lach Chul Doo cheen Dios. Naz ba mbin na wdizh kwaan nik tub myet nyent mod nii, nu nanzheklat Dios nii naya.
Nzho mod to na yalxwa lo kwaane, per nyent mod to na leeka yalxwa cheen na. Nebse nii na, nak na mod tub xaa nangezht.
Chelee na nzhekla na to na yalxwa, nanakta tub kwaan nachan, nel kwaan wli kanii na. Per nalet naya zee nik tub xaa nalet xgab lee na nak mas xwara lo mod nle na o re kwaan nii na.
Zee natot na yalxwa lo rese kwaan mlu Dios lo na, nel cho kwerp cheen na mzob xaa tub kwaan mod tub yich, kwaan nteed na bid, kwaane nak mod tub mandad cheen Maxuu.
Chon welt ngunaab na lo Xaa Nabeyy zee kiib xaa kwaan nak mod yich ne cho na,
per lee Xaa Nabeyy né lo na: “Nebse yalnkela cheen na nkin lu, kwaan nlu na lo lu, nel lee yalgezh cheen na mas nlu lo re xaa nangezht”. Nu kwaanzee nto na yalxwa nel nangezht na, Dios nle yudar na, zee kwent cheen na luu yalngezh cheen Jesucrist.
Nu nyakla na leezha nangezht na, leezha nge re xaa lo na, nu leezha nkin na kwaan, nu leezha nrenal xaa na, nu leezha ndeed na bid kwent cheen Jesucrist; nel leezha mas nangezht na mas nlu nzo yalngezh cheen Dios kwaan na.
Pab nle xgab re xaa Jesús, xaa yezh CorintoMle na mod tub xaa nachan leezha mto na yalxwa lo gu, nel sbaa nzhekla gu le xaa lo gu, per kwaan wlipa nak nzhaal to gu yalxwa cheen na. Nel na nak tub xaa mas nanont ke re xaa kwaan mbezh mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, xaa nzak gu non doo; nixa na nak tub xaa tira nanont.
Nel leezha mzo na kwaan re gu mle na zyen kwaan gro, zee ne gu wlipa mkayaa na yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist. Myedoola na mle na re kwaan gro nu kwaan chul lo re gu.
Kwaan mle na lo re gu lal mle naya lo re stub naz xaa Jesús. Tubka kwaan nalalt mle na lo re gu, nanaabt na nik tub kwaan lo re gu. ¿Cho kwaan nzak gu? ¿Che nzhaal naab na perdon lo gu kwent cheen kwaane?
Nu nal listla na yal na lo re gu stub welt, zee gak chon welt yal na lo re gu, nu nixa welt ne nanaabt na nik tub kwaan lo re gu. Nanzheklat na ka na kwaan nkano re gu, lee na nzhekla nyera zo gu lo Dios. Mod xiin na nzak na gu. Nu lee xinn xaa nanzhaalt kwaan demi zaa lo xuz xaa, sinka xuz xaa nzhaal kwaan demi zaa xaa lo xinn xaa.
Kwaanzee lee na, kwaan dub lextoo na, lux na rese kwaan nkano na, zee chul yo re gu. Nixa sneeya, nzak na leezha mas nkela na re gu, lee re gu mas nanketla na.
Nixa namkiibt na demi lo re gu leezha mbal na lo re gu; per seesa nzho gu mbezh, lee na mle zee mla gu lo tramp.
<sup>(17-18)</sup> ¿Che wliya? Lo Tito nu lo stub wech ngunaab na zee yasewii xaa lo re gu. ¿Che mkade Tito gu? ¿O che nawlit lal nak rop nu lo re gu, leezha lal mle rop nu Tito xgab?
Tant nkedoola na gu. ¿Cho xgab nle gu? ¿Che nzak gu nzhekla nu gak nonra nu lo gu? Lee rop nu kanii delant lo Dios nel xaa Jesús nak nu, zee nyera zo gu lo Dios.
Nel nzak na gorna yal na lo re gu, napa nkin le na mod nanzheklat gu, nel nanzhit gu mod nzhekla na. Nzak na napa kadildiizh gu, napa kayak selos gu, napa kayii re gu, napa kayak gu meskin, napa nawent kanii gu tub gu stub gu, napa kayak gu tub xaa nkwaan diizh, napa kato gu yalxwa, napa karexcho re gu.
Noka nzak na napaka nton na ne na re gu gorna yal na lo re gu stub welt, gonn na nel nzha doo mbizh lee lak gu kale kwaan nawent. Nu seesa nzho lak gu zer laa re kwaan nawent kwaan kale: nchaal gu stub ngwnaa, nu nle gu re kwaan nawent kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen gu. Zee ton na ne na Dios mod kale gu.
Nzhaal zo gu nye lo DiosWelt ne gak yon welt yal na lo re gu. Leezha ngaazh be tub kwaan tich stub xaa Jesús, nzhaal yo chop o chon testig.
Ngulola mgalno na re xaa mle jwalt yilo lo rese gu, nu nal nixa zit nzo na, noka nzho mod galno na re xaa, mod mle naya leezha mbal na mrop welt lo re gu. Nal chelee na yal na lo re gu stub welt nalest la na ne na re xaa nle kwaan nawent,
nel lee re gu kakwaan tub kwaan luu wlipa lee Jesucrist nii kwaan na. Nu Jesucrist nanakt tub xaa nangezht lo re gu, lee xaa nlu yalngezh cheen xaa lo re gu.
Wli lee xaa mkee lo krus mod tub xaa nangezht, per nal mban xaa kwaan yalngezh cheen Dios. Nu leeka snee, lee re nu nak mod tub xaa nangezht kwenta lee xaa, per tubka yo nu kwaan lee xaa, kwent cheen yalngezh cheen Dios, zee le nu yudar re gu.
Nu bwii gu ne xomod nak gu, zee ne gu nen che wli nayiyot gu lo xcheen Jesucrist. ¿Che nanet gu lee Jesucrist mban leen lextoo be? ¡Per nambant xaa leen lextoo re gu chelee gu yiyo gu ngwii gu lo xaa!
Nu ne na, lee re gu ne, lee re nu nayiyot lo xcheen Jesucrist.
Nu naab nu lo Dios zee nalet gu kwaan nawent, nel nu nzhekla zee nzho mod le gu kwaan wen, nixa nzak gu tira nguyo nu lo re kwaane.
Nel nyent mod wdizh nu kwaan nawlit, nebse re kwaan wli nzhekla nu nzhedizh nu.
Kwaanzee nyakla nu leezha nangezht nu, nu lee re gu ngezh, zee seetaka naab nu lo Dios zee lee re gu nalira zo lo Dios.
Yilo yech ne kakee na lo gu gorna zeeraka yal na lo re gu, zee nagakt na tub xaa nakap doo lo gu kwaan yalnabeyy kwaan mzaa Xaa Nabeyy lo na, gorna zhin na lo gu. Lee yalnabeyy cheen na nanakt tub kwaan lux na gu, leeya nak tub kwaan le zee zo nyera gu lo Dios.
Dix gwluzhWech nu bzan, ngulola ngunii na rese kwaane. Nzhekla na yo gu chul nu bkwaan gu re kwaan le zee nali zo gu lo Dios, nu byaan gu le gu kwaan wen, zee chul kwi re gu, zee lee Dios xaa nkela be, zo kwaan re gu.
Guzh gu “dix” lo re wech nu lo re bzan, nu daw gu tub bit tagarlo xaa tub mod nali.
Nu rese xaa mle nambey Jesús, xaa nzhi nee, nxaal “dix” lo re gu.
Nzhekla na les lextoo Jesucrist ne rese gu, nu lee yalnkela cheen Dios zo kwaan rese gu, zee lee Mbi Naban cheen xaa tubka yo leen lextoo rese gu.Sbaa gaka.
<font color=teal>Yech kwaan mkee Pab lo re xaa yezh Galacia</font>Dix cheen PabNa nak Pab, nu nak na tub xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, nu nanakt na tub xaa mxaal o mleey myet yizhyo. Na nak tub xaa mleey mer Jesucrist nu Dios, xaa nak Xuz be, xaa mseban Jesucrist.
Na, nu rese wech xaa nzo kwaan na nee, kakee na yech ne lo re gu, xaa nak xaa Jesucrist, xaa nzho re yezh cheen Galacia.
Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa nak Xuz be, nu Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, luu xaa yalnkela cheen xaa lo re gu, le xaa zee kwi chul re gu.
Nu leeka Jesucrist mzaa Jesucrist ngut kwent cheen re jwalt cheen rese be, zee koo xaa be lo re kwaan naxinn lo yizhyo ne, re mbizh kwaan nzho be nal, mod nzhekla Dios, xaa nak Xuz be.
¡Nzhekla na gool rese xaa lo Dios rese mbizh! ¡Sbaa gaka!
Nyentra stub wdizh chulMdedyall doo na gorna ne na lee re gu mbin stub wdizh kwaan nzak gu nzaa yalnaban, ta mlaa gu Dios, xaa mrezh gu kwaan yalnkela cheen Jesucrist, nu mkayaa guya.
Per kwaan wli nak, nyentra stub wdizh chul kwaan nyaadno yalnaban. Nal nzho lak xaa nzhekla le yek gu chop nu nzhekla xaa chee xaa wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist.
Per chelee tub re nu o tub mandad cheen Dios zaa kwent cheen stub wdizh chul lo gu, la yalnayii cheen Dios tich xaa zee, nu xobde Dios xaa.
Nu kwaan ngunii nu yilo bare na nii naya lo gu stub welt: Chelee tub xaa zaa kwent stub wdizh chul lo gu, nu nanakta kwaan mzaa nu lo gu, la yalnayii cheen Dios tich xaa zee, nu xobde Dios xaa.
Nankwaant na nix gak lextoo re myet ne na, lee na nkwaan gak nix lextoo Dios ne na. ¡Nu chelee na nkwaan na yula re myet na, zee nanaktra na tub mos cheen Jesucrist!
Xomod mkayaa Pab yalnabeyy lo JesucristWech nu bzan, nzhekla na ne re gu kwaane: Lee wdizh chul kwaan nza na kwent, nanakta tub xgab cheen myet.
Namkayaat naya, nu nixa namseedt naya lo myet, leeya nak tub kwaan mseed Jesucrist na.
Nu lo re kwaan mlu xey nu, na ngok tub xaa mas mle rese kwaan né xaa; lo re xaa kwaan nzexen kwaan na, na ngok tub xaa nzheklara ngozhaw rese kwaan mle re xey nu, xaa yilo.
Per Dios mleey na leezha zeeraka gal na, nu kwaan yalnkela cheen xaa mrezh xaa na. Nu leezha mzhib gan lextoo xaa,
mle xaa mlabeyy na Xgann xaa, zee za na kwent cheen xaa kwaan nyalno yalnaban lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel. Nu namnabdizht na lo stub xaa zaa kwent cheen wdizh chul lo na;
nu nixa nangwanabdizht na lo re xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist yilo ke na, xaa nzho Jerusalén. Kwaan mle na nak, ta ngwa na yizhyo cheen Arabia, nu zeera mbare na naz yezh Damasco.
Chon liin gwluzh zeera ngwa na Jerusalén, zee mlabeyy na Pér, nu lo xaa mlaz na chiin mbizh.
Per nik stub xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist nangunet na lo, nebse lo Chag, wech Xaa Nabeyy.
Nu delant lo Dios nii na wli na kwaan kakee na lo gu.
Gwluzh zeera ngwa na naz yizhyo cheen Siria nu Cilicia.
Kwaanzee lee re xaa Jesús, xaa nzho yizhyo cheen Judea nanlabeyyt xaa na.
Nebse kwaan nzhayon re xaa ne nak: “Lee xaa kwaan mrenal be yilo, lee nal nzaa xaa kwent cheen wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist, leeka kwaan nzhekla xaa luux yilo”.
Nu nal nzholl re xaa lo Dios, nel mchee Dios mod nak na.
Mkayaa re xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesús PabStub chida liin gwluzh leezha mlu xni lo na, zee ngwa na Jerusalén stuba kwaan Bernabé, nu mbe nu Tito.
Ngwa nu nel mlu Dios lo na nzhaal ya na. Nu gorna nzola na Jerusalén, nguu na tub junt kwaan re xaa nabeyy lo xaa Jesús, techo re nu, nu mza na kwent lo re xaa, kwent cheen wdizh chul kwaan nza na lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel. Nu mle na kwaane nel nanzheklat na lee kwaan mlu na, nu re kwaan kale na, luux.
Per nixa Tito, xaa nzo kwaan na, namlet re xaa nabeyy jwers lo xaa yo xaa beyy cheen re nu, xaa Israel, nixa nanzhot xaa beyy cheen re nu, xaa Israel.
Per lak xaa nkade, nu nle mod xaa Jesús, xlaan mrep xaa lo re be, nze selach xaa nen cho kwaan nzho mod le be, nel msela Jesucrist be; nu zee mkwaan xaa mod le xaa zee kozhaw be kwaan nzhé re xey nu, zee gak be mod tub mos cheen re kwaan nzhé xey nu.
Per tira namzaat re nu yek nu gon xtizh xaa nel nanzheklat nu lee re gu laa wdizh chul, kwaan nak kwaan wli.
Per lee re xaa nak xaa nabeyy be, nik tub rason namzaatra xaa lo na. (Nu lo na nanont cho kwaan ngok xaa yilo, nel rese xaa lal nak lo Dios.)
Per ngune xaa lee Dios mleey na za na kwent cheen wdizh chul lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel, modxa mkayaa Pér zaa xaa kwent ne lo re sawlazh nu.
Nu leeka Dios, xaa mle yudar Pér zaa Pér kwent lo re sawlazh nu, nel nak xaa tub xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, leeka Dios zee, nle yudar na za na kwent lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel, nel na nak tub xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist.
Nu kwaanzee lee Chag, Pér nu Juan, re xaa non lo re xaa Jesús, mzeen xaa lee Dios mleey na kee na zhiin ne lo yalnkela cheen Dios. Nu snee mlu xaa mkayaa xaa nu mod xmig xaa, nel mzaa xaa yaa xaa lo rop nu Bernabé, nu mzeyal xaa ya nu lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel kee nu zhiin, nu lee re xaa kee zhiin lo re sawlazh nu.
Nebse ngunaab re xaa lo nu selazh nu re xaa prob, mer kwaan nzhekla doo na le na.
Pab mgalno Pér yezh AntioquíaPer gorna mzhin Pér yezh Antioquía, mgalno na xaa delant lo rese xaa, nel lee xaa kale tub kwaan tira nawent.
Nel gorna mzhin xaa mzelo xaa nzhaw xaa kwaan re xaa Jesús, xaa nanakt xaa Israel. Per gorna mzhin lak xaa mxaal Chag, xaa sawlazh nu, nanzheklatra xaa gaw xaa kwaan re xaa Jesús, xaa nanakt xaa Israel; nu mlaa xaa xaa, nel mzheb xaa ne xaa re xaa kwaan mbezh nzhaal yo rese xaa Jesús beyy cheen nu.
Nu mzhaal lak sawlazh na kwaan Pér lo kwaan kale xaa, nu axta noka Bernabé mkade xaa, mzhaal kwaan re xaa, xaa kwaan mbezh le tub kwaan nu nle stub kwaan.
Kwaanzee gorna ngune na nanzhat xaa nali mod nii wdizh chul, zee nzhé na lo Pér delant lo rese xaa: “Lu nak xaa Israel, nu nle lu mod tub xaa nanakt xaa Israel. ¿Chozhiin nabeyy lu lee re xaa nanakt xaa Israel yo mod rop be?
¿Che nzak lu, lee re be, xaa nak xaa Israel axta leezha ngol be, xwara ke re xaa nanakt xaa Israel, xaa nzeb jwalt?
Per noka ne be, nakayaat Dios nik tub xaa mod xaa nali lo Dios nel ngozhaw xaa ley cheen Ches; Dios kayaa xaa mod xaa nali nel ngwii xaa lo Jesucrist. Kwaanzee noka be ngwii lo Jesucrist, zee kayaa Dios be. Nu nanakta nel ngozhaw be ley cheen Ches, nel nik tub xaa nakayaat Dios nel ngozhaw xaa ley cheen Ches.
Nu kwaanzee, chelee be nzhekla be kayaa Dios be mod xaa nali nel ngwii be lo Jesucrist, zee lee lak xaa yé, nzeb be jwalt nel nangwiit be lo re kwaan nzhé re xey be. ¡Chol sbaa naka, Jesucrist nle zee zeeb be jwalt, nawlit kwaane!”
Ngulo mlux na re kwaan nzhé re xey nu, nu chol bare na dexkwaa naya stub welt, leeka na ngak xaa nzeb jwalt.
Tubka kwaan Jesucrist mkee na lo krus, nu nanakt na xaa mban, xaa mban nak Jesucrist, xaa kwaan nzho leen lextoo na nal. Nu lee yalnaban kwaan mban na leen xkwerp na nal, mban naya nel ngwii na lo Xgann Dios, xaa nkedoola na, nu ngut kwent cheen na.
Chol ngozhaw xaa ley cheen Ches, zee nzho mod kayaa Dios xaa, nzere xaa re kwaan chul kwaan sbaasa mzelazh Dios lo xaa, ¡nu tira nalet na kwaane! Sbaa nle xaa zee nanont ngut Jesucrist.
Cho kwaan mas non: ley o wii xaa lo Dios¡Xaa Galacia, xaa bxen! ¿Xomod mlaa gu mle nachan xaa yek gu? Klar doo mzaa nu kwent lo gu, xomod ngut Jesucrist, leezha mkee xaa xaa lo krus.
Nebse nzhekla na keb gu lo na: ¿Che mkayaa gu Mbi Naban cheen Dios, nel mbin gu kwaan nzhé ley cheen Ches, o nel mle gu krer wdizh chul kwaan mbin gu?
¿Chozhiin tant nachan gu? Mzelo gu mze gu xnaz Dios kwaan Mbi Naban, nu lee nal nzhekla gu zhin gu lo Dios kwaan yalngezh cheen myet yizhyo.
¿Che nik tub sirb namlet mded gu bid kwent cheen wdizh chul? ¡Wena, chol mleya sirb lo gu!
Leezha mzaa Dios Mbi Naban nu mle xaa re kwaan gro lo re gu, ¿chozhiin mle xaaya? Nanakta nel mle gu kwaan nzhé ley, mle xaaya nel mle gu krer wdizh chul kwaan mbin gu.
Snee mle Abraham, nel nkee lo Xkyech Dios, nzhé: “Abraham mwii lo Dios, kwaanzee Dios mkayaa xaa mod tub xaa nali”.
Nu kwaanzee nzhaal ne re gu, lee re dii cheen Abraham nak re xaa kwaan ngwii lo Dios.
Nu lo Xkyech Dios nzhéla lee Dios kayaa re xaa nanakt xaa Israel mod xaa nali lo xaa, re xaa kwaan ngwii lo Dios, nu nzhé xaa wdizh chul ne lo Abraham: “Kwent cheen lu, Dios le kwaan chul lo zyen doo xaa dubse yizhyo”.
Nu kwaanzee lee re xaa ngwii lo Dios chul yo xaa kwenta Abraham, xaa mwii lo Dios.
Rese xaa kwaan ngwii lo ley cheen Ches ded xaa bid nel Xkyech Dios nzhé: “Nxobde Dios re xaa kwaan nalet rese kwaan nkee lo yech cheen ley”.
Nu kwaanzee, klar doo niiya, nik tub xaa nakayaat Dios nel ngozhaw xaa ley cheen Ches, modxa nzhé Xkyech Dios: “Xaa nali nak xaa ngwii lo Dios”.
Per lee re xaa ngwii lo ley cheen Ches nangwiit xaa lo Dios, nel Xkyech Dios nzhé: “Xaa ngwii lo ley cheen Ches, nkin le xaa rese kwaan nkee lo ley cheen Ches”.
Jesucrist mdix re jwalt cheen be mod naab ley kwent lo be, nel mxobde Dios xaa kwent cheen re be, nel lee Xkyech Dios nzhé: “Dios nxobde rese xaa nzhet nkenga lo yag”.
Kwaanzee yo chul re xaa nanakt xaa Israel, mod mzaa Dios kwent lo Abraham yilo. Nu snee rese be, xaa ngwii lo Jesucrist, mkayaa Mbi Naban, modxa nzhé Dios xaal xaa.
Ley nu yalnkela cheen DiosWech nu bzan, nii na lo gu mod xaa yizhyo ne: Leezha nle xaa tub trat nu nzaa xaa firm cheen xaa lo yech, nik tub xaa nyent mod cheeya o kee stub kwaan loya.
Sbaaka mlaa Dios wdizh lo Abraham nu lo dii cheen xaa. Lee Xkyech Dios nanzaat kwent cheen: “rese dii cheen xaa”. Leeya nzaa kwent cheen: “tubka dii cheen xaa”, xaa nak Jesucrist.
Lee kwaan nii na nak kwaane: Dios mlaa diizh lo Abraham, nu nzhé xaa le xaaya. Kwaanzee, lee ley cheen Ches, kwaan nyaad tap gayoo galbchii liin gwluzh, nyent mod lux wdizh zee, nu kiib yalnon lo kwaan nzhé Dios lo Abraham.
Nel chelee kwaan nzaa Dios lo be, zaa xaaya nel ngozhaw be ley, zee nanaktraya tub kwaan nguné xaa zaa xaa sbaasa. Per lee Dios nzaaya sbaasa nel sbaa nzhé xaa lo Abraham.
Chozhiin mzaa Dios leyKwaanzee, ¿cho sirb nle ley cheen Ches? Gwluzh Dios mzaaya zee ngok ngeda kwent cheen re jwalt cheen myet. Nu nebse nzhaal diiya axta gorna yaad xaa nak “dii” kwaan nzhé Dios yaad. Re mandad cheen Dios mzaa ley lo Ches, zee gak xaa tub xaa nzo xsaww lo Dios nu lo re xaa Dios.
Per leezha nzhé Dios lo Abraham le xaa kwaan chul, mer lee xaa nzhéya, nu namkint xaa tub xaa mzo xsaww lo rop xaa, nel Dios nak tubka.
Kwaanzee, ¿cho kwaan nii na, lee ley cheen Ches nzho kontr cheen re kwaan ngunii Dios le xaa? ¡Telisa nawlita! Nel chelee ley nzho mod ngzaaya yalnaban, zee kayaa Dios be mod xaa nali lo xaa nebse kwent cheen ley.
Per kwaan nzhé Xkyech Dios nak rese xaa nak mod xaa nzho lozhyib kwent cheen jwalt. Zee lee re xaa kwaan ngwii lo Jesucrist kayaa kwaan nzhé Dios zaa Dios.
Leezha zeeraka yaad Jesucrist, leezha nyent mod wii be lo xaa, lee ley nkano re be mod tub xaa nzho lozhyib, nebse nkambaz be zhin Xaa Xaal Dios Nabeyy, zee nzho mod wii be lo xaa.
Kwaanzee nii na, lee ley cheen Ches nak kwaan mseed be mod madwin axta mzhin Jesucrist, nu snee gorna wii be lo xaa, kayaa Dios be mod xaa nali.
Per nal myaadla Jesucrist, nzho mod wii be lo xaa, nankintra reke be tich ley,
nel lee mod ngwii re be lo Jesucrist, le zee rese be nak xinn Dios.
Nel gorna mrubnis be ngok be tubka kwaan Jesucrist, nu nak be xaa mod tub ler.
Nu chelee be nak be xaa Jesucrist, zee noka nak be xaa dii cheen Abraham, nu nak be xaa kayaa re kwaan chul kwaan nzhé Dios zaa xaa.
Lee kwaan nzhekla na nii na nak kwaane: Leezha win xaa, zer kayaa xaa re kwaan nak cheen xuz xaa, lal nak xaa kwaan xmos xaa, nixa lee xaa nak bixwann rese kwaan.
Nel nzho xaa nabeyy lo xaa ne, nu nkanap xaa xaa nu re xcheen xaa, axta yixoob xaa liin kwaan nzhé xuz xaa, zeera nzho mod kayaa xaa re xcheen xuz xaa.
Nu seeka re be, leezha chut be, nle be rese kwaan nle re xey be.
Per gorna mzhin mbizh kwaan mleey Dios, mxaal xaa Xgann xaa, xaa mzan tub ngwnaa; nu ngol xaa mod tub sawlazh na zee kozhaw xaa ley cheen Ches.
Nu mdix xaa zee koo xaa be lo ley zee, re be xaa nzhake tich ley zee, snee lee Dios nzho mod kayaa re be mod xinn xaa.
Nu nel xinn Dios nak be, Dios mxaal Mbi Naban cheen Xgann xaa lextoo re be, nu lee Mbi Naban mbezh: “¡Pa!”
Nu kwaanzee nanaktra be tub mos, lee be nak xinn Dios, nu nel xinn Dios nak be, noka nzhekla xaa kayaa be re kwaan chul kwaan nguné xaa zaa xaa lo be.
Pab nzhé nanzhaalt bare xaa wii xaa lo ley stubaYilo, leezha nanlabeyyt gu Dios, nak gu mos cheen re kwaan nawlit nak Dios.
Per nal nlabeyy gu Dios o mas wen nal nlabeyy Dios re gu, ¿xomod bare gu lo re kwaan nle xey nu, kwaan nanont tant nu nyent sirb, nu gak gu xmosa stuba?
Lee re gu seetaka ngozhaw re mbizh, re mbee, nu liin kwaan nzak gu non.
¡Nu nzheb doo na napa lee re zhiin kwaan mle na lo re gu luux!
Wech nu bzan, naab na lo gu gok gu kwenta na, nel ngok na kwenta gu. Nik tub kwaan nawent namlet re gu lo na,
mod nela re gu. Leezha yilotlaka mza na kwent cheen wdizh chul lo re gu, mle naya nel ngok ne na.
Nu yalyizh zee ngok tub preb lo gu, nixa sneeya mkayaa re gu na, nixa ne na; nu mkayaa gu na mod tub mandad cheen Dios, nu mod mer Jesucrist.
¿Ma re kwaan chul kwaan mle gu zee? Nu xjabor gu nii na, chol nzho moda lo gu, zee axta zaalo gu ngoo gu ngzaa guya lo na.
Lee nal, ¿che ngok na xkontrad gu, nebse nel ngunii na kwaan wli lo gu?
Re xaa kwaan mbezh nkin yo xaa beyy cheen nu, nle doo xaa xgab re gu, per lee re xgab cheen xaa nanakt kwaan wen. Kwaan nzhekla xaa nak koxcho xaa be, zee zhaal gu kwaan lee xaa.
Wliya wen le xaa xgab stub naz xaa, per lee xgab cheen xaa nzhaal gak tub xgab wen, nu nzhaal tubka sbaa le xaa xgab; nu nagakta nebse leezha nzo na lo re gu.
Nii na lo re gu mod xiin na, stub welt ne doo nzhak lextoo na ne na re gu, mod tub ngwnaa, me mer gal xinn; nu tubka snee gak ne lextoo na axta gorna lee Jesucrist tira nabeyy lextoo gu.
¡Wena chol nzo na lo re gu nal gorne, zee nzho mod nii na lo re gu stub mod, nel nanet na cho kwaan le na kwaan re gu!
Kwaan nlu Agar nu SaraNé gu tub kwaan lo na, xaa nzhekla wii lo ley cheen Ches; ¿che zer ne gu cho kwaan nzhé ley zee?
Nzhéya Abraham mkano chop xgann; tub xaa mzan xmos xaa, nu stub xaa mzan sa xaa, me nanakt mos.
Lee xinn xaa, xaa mzan xmos xaa, ngol mod re myet yizhyo ne, per lee xinn xaa, xaa mzan sa xaa ngol zee mbarlo kwaan nzhé Dios lo xaa.
Rop ngwnaa ne nlu xomod nak rop wdizh kwaan mlaa Dios, Rese xinn Agar nak mos nel xnaa xaa ngok mos, kwenta re xaa ngwii lo ley kwaan mzaa Dios lo Ches yek yi Sinaí. Nu rese xaa ne, axta leezha nzhal xaa nak xaa kwenta mos.
Nu lee yi Sinaí kwaan nak cheen xaa Arabia, nak kwenta Agar, kwaan nak kwenta Jerusalén mbizh ne, nel lee re xaa nzho yezh ne nak mos cheen ley.
Per lee Jerusalén kwaan nzho naz yiba, nak mod xnaa be, kwaanzee nanakt be mos cheen ley.
Nel lee Xkyech Dios nzhé:Chul ble lextoo lu, lu ngwnaa me nit, me nanzhalt xinn;lu me nankanot mad, bxizh nel chul nzhak lextoo lu,lu me nanlabeyyt yalne cheen mad.Nel zyenra mad nkano ngwnaa, me mlaa sa, ke ngwnaa me nkano sa.
Wech nu bzan, be nak mod Chak; be nak re xaa kwaan nguné Dios gal.
Kenzha gu kwaan nzhé Xkyech Dios. Néya: “Btexonn mos kwaan xinn me, nel nyent mod kiiz lu kwaan lo xinn sa lu nu lo xinn xmos lu”.
Kwaanzee wech nu bzan, nanakt be xinn mos, lee be nak xinn me nanakt mos.
Jesucrist mle zee nagakt be tub mos cheen ley. Kwaanzee, nye zo be lo xcheen Jesucrist nu nagaktra be tub mos cheen ley, nel lee ley nak mod tub yog kwaan nga nzhib yenn be, nu kwaanzee nawiitra be lo ley stuba.
Pab mlu cho kwaan nzhaal le xaaBkenzha gu. Na Pab, nii na lo gu. Chelee gu ko gu gu beyy cheen nu, zee lee Jesucrist nanont lo gu.
Nu stub welt nii na lo rese xaa kwaan nzhekla yo re xaa beyy cheen nu, nkin le xaa rese kwaan nabeyy ley cheen Ches.
Re gu, xaa nzhekla kayaa Dios gu mod tub xaa nali nel nle gu kwaan nzhé ley cheen Ches, tira mbachii gu lo Jesucrist nu lo yalnkela cheen Dios.
Per re be ngwii lo Dios kwent cheen Mbi Naban, nu nkambaz be gak be tub xaa nali lo Dios.
Nel chelee be tubka nzo be kwaan Jesucrist, nanont yo xaa beyy o nayot xaa beyy cheen sawlazh na. Lee kwaan non nak le be rese kwaan kwent cheen yalnkela, zee nlu ngwii be lo Dios.
Wen nzha re gu. ¿Cho mle zee namkenzhatra gu wdizh chul kwaan wli?
Nu naleet Dios xaa kabezh gu mleya.
Mod mbezh xaa: “Chepse lebadur ntexoob dubse koob”.
Telisa ded xaa bid, re xaa kwaan nzhekla le chop xgab cheen gu, nexa cho xaa zee. Nu ne na lee Xaa Nabeyy, le zee lee re gu nacheet xgab cheen.
Wech nu bzan, chol ngle na jwers yo re xaa beyy cheen nu, xaa Israel, kwaan mle na yilo; nu chol sbaa ngle na nal, zee lee re sawlazh na nangrenalt na, nel zee lee kwent kwaan mkee Jesucrist lo krus, nangakt nik tub storb lo xaa.
Nu lee re xaa kwaan kachee xgab cheen gu, ¡oj tira ngle kapon xaa xaa!
Wech nu bzan, Dios mleey re gu zee nawiitra gu lo ley. Nakint kozhaw gu ley, per nanzhaalt le gu rese kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen gu. Nu nal wen kela gu nu ble gu yudar tub gu stub gu.
Nel dubse ley nzho mod nii beya kwaan tubka wdizh ne: “Bkela wechxinn lu modxa nkela lu leeka lu”.
Per chelee gu nkwaan gu diizh nu ndil leeka re gu kwenta ma nakap, nzho mod lux gu leeka re gu.
Nzhekla na kano gu yalnaban kwaan nzaa Mbi NabanKwaan nii na lo gu nak: Le be kwaan nzhekla Mbi Naban nu nalet be re kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen be.
Nel lee re kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen be nzha kontr cheen Mbi Naban, nu kwaan nzhekla Mbi Naban nzha kontr cheen re kwaan nzhekla kwerp. Tuba nzha kontr stuba, kwaanzee nyent mod le be kwaan nzhekla be.
Nu chelee Mbi Naban nabeyy lo be, zee lee ley nanabeyytra lo be.
Nu nanagant luu re kwaan nle re xaa, xaa nle re kwaan nzhekla xkwerp:nchaal xaa stub ngwnaa,nzoblazh xaa chaal xaa zyen ngwnaa,nzho re xgab nachan yek xaa,
ngwii xaa lo maj,nya xaa lo wezh,nayii xaa ne xaa stub xaa,ndildiizh xaa,nzhak selos xaa,tira nanagant yii xaa,nzhak meskin xaa,nle rol xaa re xaa,nu nle xaa zee nakwiwent stub naz xaa,
nzoblazh xaa,nzuzh xaa,nya xaa yalni pa nle xaa rese kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen xaa,nu stub naz kwaan nawent kwenta re kwaane.Nu bare na nii na lo gu, kwentaxa nguniila naya lo gu yilo, lee re xaa kwaan tubka nle re kwaane, nayizot xaa Pa Nabeyy Dios.
Per lee kwaan nle Mbi Naban lextoo xaa nak:nkela xaa,chul nzhak lextoo xaa,chul nzo xaa kwaan Dios,nyela xaa,chul nkayaa xaa stub xaa,wen nak xaa,nanlaat xaa Dios,
nadoo nak xaa,nanlet xaa re kwaan nzhekla kwerp.Nu nik tub ley nyent mod né nawent re kwaane.
Per lee re xaa nak xaa Jesucrist, nanletra xaa rese kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen xaa, nel mkeela xaaya lo krus kwaan Jesucrist, nu snee ngutla xaa lo re kwaan nak kwaan yizhyo ne.
Nu lee nal cheleeya kwaan Mbi Naban mban be, noka laa be nabeyy Mbi Naban be.
Natot be yalxwa, nakwaant be dil, nu nixa nazoblazht be cheen wechxinn be.
Ble gu yudar tub gu stub guWech nu bzan, chelee gu ne gu, lee tub wech gu mle tub kwaan nawent, re gu xaa nzo kwaan Mbi Naban, nzhaal le gu yudar xaa, zee le xaa kwaan wen; per ble gu yudar xaa tub mod nadoo. Nu bkanap gu gu, napa noka gu kale kwaan nawent.
Nu leezha lee tub xaa nzak non xaa, nu wlipa nanakta sbaa, leeka lee xaa kakade xaa.
Nu kad tub xaa nzhaal wii lo re kwaan nle xaa, nu chul gak lextoo xaa gorna ne xaa chul nle xaa, nu nanzhaalt wii xaa lo re kwaan nle stub naz xaa.
Nel kad tub xaa nzhaal le zhiin kwaan mzaa Dios lo xaa.
Lee xaa kwaan kaseed xtizh Dios, nzhaal le xaa yudar xaa kwaan nak xmaestr xaa.
Nakadet gu leeka gu, nik tub xaa nyent mod kitno Dios. Leezha ngo xaa bizh lo yo zee ntop xaa kwaan mgaan xaa.
Nu snee lee xaa nxeen re kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen xaa, lo re kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen xaa le xaa gan kwaan naxinn doo. Lee xaa kwaan nxeen re kwaan nzhekla Mbi Naban, lo kwaan nzhekla Mbi Naban le xaa gan yalnaban kwaan tira.
Kwaanzee nanzhaalt yizha be le be kwaan wen, nel chelee be nayachet lextoo be, zee top be yalgon mer tyemp nak cheena.
Kwaanzee, leezha nzho mod le be chul lo stub xaa, le beya, nu lo re xaa yilotlaka nzhaal le be chul, nak lo re wech be nu lo re bzan be, xaa nak xaa Jesucrist.
Lo re kwaan nzhaal zo list be¡Wii gu re letr ndok kwaan nkee na kwaan mer yaa na!
Nu lee re xaa kwaan nzhekla yo gu beyy cheen nu, nle xaaya nel nzhekla xaa kwi chul xaa kwaan re myet, zee narenalt re xaa xaa, kwent kwaan mkee Jesucrist lo krus.
Per nixa re xaa kwaan nzho beyy cheen nu nanlet rese kwaan nzhé ley. Nu nzhekla xaa lee re gu yo beyy ba, zee nzho mod to re xaa yalxwa nel mle xaa jwers lo re gu zee wee gu beyy ba cho kwerp cheen gu.
Nu lee na nanzheklat na to na yalxwa lo nik tub kwaan, nebse kwent kwaan mkee Jesucrist lo krus, Xaa Nabeyy be. Nel leeya mle, ngut na lo re kwaan yizhyo, zee nanabeyytra lo na.
Nu nanont yo xaa o nayot xaa beyy cheen re nu, kwaan non nak gak na tub xaa kub lo Jesucrist.
Nu nzhekla na nix kwi re gu nu kayaa gu yalnles cheen Dios, nel nle gu kwaane, nu wlipa xaa dii cheen Israel nak gu, nu nak gu xaa Dios.
Nu nalzhe naz delant, nanzheklatra na nik tub xaa kwaan diizh, nel lee re bde kwaan nkano kwerp cheen na, nlu lee na nak tub mos cheen Jesucrist.
Wech nu bzan, nzhekla na lee Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, zaa re yalnkela cheen xaa lo re gu.¡Sbaa gaka!
<font color=teal>Yech kwaan mkee Pab lo re xaa yezh Éfeso</font>Dix cheen PabDix re gu mig, xaa nzho yezh Éfeso.Na nak Pab, nu na nak tub mos cheen Jesucrist nel sbaa nzhekla Dios. Nu kakee na yech ne lo re gu xaa mle nambey Jesús, xaa nzho yezh Éfeso, xaa tubka ngwii lo Jesucrist.
Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa nak Xuz be nu Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, le zee kwi chul re gu nu luu xaa yalnkela cheen xaa lo re gu.
Diizh kwaan mzaa Jesucrist lo re xaa nak xaa xaaGool be lo Dios, xaa nak Xdios be nu xaa nak xuz Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, nel lee xaa mzaa re xcheen xaa re kwaan nze naz yiba lo re be, re kwaan nkin be zee gak be xaa xaa, kwent cheen kwaan mle Jesucrist.
Dios mleey be axta leezha zeeraka dexkwaa yizhyo, kwent cheen kwaan mle Jesucrist, zee gak be xaa xaa zee nzhul zo be lo xaa.
Nu kwaan yalnkela cheen xaa, mleey xaa be zee gak be xinn xaa kwent cheen kwaan mle Jesucrist, modxa nzhekla xaa.
Kwaanzee tubka nzhaal gool be lo Dios, nel tant nkela xaa be; nu kwent cheen Xgann xaa, xaa tant nkela xaa, mzaa xaa re kwaane lo be.
Nu leezha ngut Jesucrist zee mzi xaa be zee gak be xaa xaa, zee mchee xaa re jwalt cheen be, nel tant nkela xaa be,
zee tira mle xaa kwaane. Nu Dios kwaan yalnzhak cheen xaa,
mlu xaa re kwaan nzhekla xaa le xaa lo be, re kwaan ngulaan axta yilo. Sbaa mle xaa nel nkela xaa be, nel sbaa mlela xaa xgab le xaaya kwent cheen Jesucrist.
Leezha zhin mbizh kwaan mlela Dios xgab, le xaa zee lee Jesucrist nabeyy rese kwaan nzho lo yizhyo nu rese kwaan nzho naz yiba.
Axta yilo Dios mleeyla be zee kayaa be re kwaan nak xcheen xaa, kwent cheen kwaan mle Jesucrist mod nzhola yek xaa le xaa. Nu mle xaaya mod nzhekla xaa,
zee lee re nu, xaa mwii lo xaa yilotlaka, le zee gool rese xaa lo xaa.
Nu noka re gu leezha mbin gu kwent cheen wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist, kwaan wli nak, leeka kwaan nzaa kwent cheen yalnaban kwaan tira, nu leezha mwii gu lo Jesucrist, gorzeetlaka mkayaa gu tub sey kwaan nak Mbi Naban kwaan nzhé Dios xaal xaa.
Pab naab lo Dios zee labeyy re xaa chul nak DiosNu kwaanzee, gorna ngune na lee gu ngwii lo Jesucrist, nu nkela gu re xaa Jesús, xaa nambey,
tubka nza na dixkix lo Dios, noka naab na lo xaa kwent cheen re gu.
Nel lee xaa nak Xuz be nu nzo xaa lo xni, nu lee xaa nak Xdios Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be. Nu tubka naab na lo xaa zee yo yek gu, zee luu xaa lo gu xomod nak xaa, zee labeyyra gu xaa.
Naab na zee lee Dios le kaxni yek re gu, zee ne gu cho kwaan mrezh xaa gu nkambaz gu. Nel nkambaz be kayaa be rese kwaan chul doo kwaan zaa Dios lo be, xaa nambey.
Nu noka zee labeyy be gro doo nak yalngezh cheen xaa, lo re kwaan nle xaa kwent cheen be, xaa ngwii lo Jesucrist. Nu yalngezh ne nak kwaan mlu Dios leezha
mseban xaa Jesucrist nu mle xaa zee zob xaa lad li lo xaa naz yiba.
Nu mzob xaa xaa zee nabeyy xaa lo rese yalngezh, nu lo rese yalnabeyy, nu lo rese xaa non, nu lo rese kwaan nzho lo yizhyo ne nu lo rese kwaan zhin.
Mle xaa zee nabeyy Jesucrist lo rese kwaan, nu noka zee nabeyy xaa re xaa ngwii lo xaa.
Nel lee re xaa ngwii lo Jesucrist nak mod kwerp cheen Jesucrist, nu Jesucrist nabeyy re xaa nak xaa xaa, mod tira nabeyy xaa rese kwaan.
Dios mzaa yalnaban kwaan tira lo beYilo rese be nak mod tub xaa ngut, nel nle be re kwaan nawent,
nel nle be re kwaan nle re myet yizhyo ne, nu nle be re kwaan nzhekla Maxuu, xaa nabeyy re mbi mal, xaa kwaan nzaa balor lextoo re xaa nanzhont xtizh Dios.
Nu leeka sbaa ngu re be yilo, mle be re kwaan nzhekla xkwerp be, nu re kwaan mle be xgab, re kwaan nle zee nzhaal la yalnayii cheen Dios tich be, kwenta laya tich re stub naz xaa.
Per Dios nak tub xaa wen doo nak nu mlesla xaa ne xaa be nel nkela xaa be,
zee mzaa xaa yalnaban lo be tubka kwaan Jesucrist, nixa nak be mod tub xaa ngut nel mle be re kwaan nawent. Sbaa mle Dios nel nkela Dios be zee mzaa xaa yalnaban lo be.
Nu noka nak be mod tub xaa mseban Dios modxa mseban xaa Jesucrist, nu mle xaa zee zob be kwaan lee xaa naz yiba.
Mle xaa kwaane, zee kwent cheen Jesucrist, le xaa tub mod nadoo lo be nu zee kedoola xaa be axta re mbizh gwluzh.
Nu mlu Dios yalnkela cheen xaa lo be leezha mzaa xaa yalnaban kwaan tira lo be, xaa ngwii lo Jesucrist. Nu kwaane nanakt tub kwaan mle be gan, leeya nak tub kwaan sbaasa mzelazh Dios lo be.
Nu nixa nanakta tub kwaan mle be gan lo re kwaan nle be, kwaanzee nik tub be nanzhaalt to yalxwa lo kwaan nle be.
Nel Dios nak xaa mdexkwaa be, nu mzaa yalnaban kwaan kub lo be kwent cheen Jesucrist, zee le be kwaan wen, mod nak xgab cheen xaa.
Jesucrist mle zee tubka gak rese be lo DiosNu nayenlazht re gu xomod nak gu yilo, re gu xaa nanakt xaa Israel. Lee re nu, xaa Israel, nchoog nu tik yed cho nu kwaan nak beyy cheen nu, nu mbezh nu: “Lee re gu nak dii nanzhot beyy”.
Bzelazh gu yilo nanzot gu kwaan Jesucrist, nu nanakt gu xaa Israel, nu nanzhot gu lo wdizh kwaan mlaa Dios lo re nu, xaa Israel, gu nzho lo yizhyo ne, nu nanlabeyyt gu Dios, nu nixa nankambazt gu kayaa gu nik tub kwaan lo xaa.
Zit mzo gu lo xaa. Per lee nal gax nzo gu lo xaa kwent cheen xren Jesucrist, kwaan mxo xaa; nu nal tubka nak gu kwaan Jesucrist.
Jesucrist nak xaa nle zee chul kwi be, nel tubka mle xaa re nu, xaa Israel, nu re gu, xaa nanakt xaa Israel, gorna mlux xaa yalnayii kwaan nle nrexcho myet, kwaan nak mod tub bla, kwaan nsaaw lo xaa.
Nu gorna ngut Jesucrist mle xaa zee nanabeyytra ley cheen Ches lo be, kwaan mnabeyy lo rese nu, xaa Israel, nu mchaal xaa rop naz be nu mle xaa be tubka, snee zee kwi chul re be.
Nel mkeela Jesucrist lo krus, zee mluux xaa dil zee nix kwi rese be, nu snee mle xaa be zee nak be mod tubka kwerp lo Dios.
Jesucrist myaad mzaa kwent cheen wdizh chul, zee chul kwi rese be, gu xaa mzo zit lo Dios nu re nu, xaa Israel, xaa nzo gax lo Dios.
Nel kwent cheen Jesucrist, tub be stub be nzho mod bii lo Xuz be kwaan tubka Mbi Naban.
Kwaanzee nal, lee re gu nanaktra gu mod xaa stub yezh, mod xaa nzho xkyizhyo stub xaa, tubka nak gu kwaan re xaa mle nambey Jesús, nu xinn Dios nak gu.
Re be nak mod tub yidoo kwaan kaza xaa, kwaan nkano simyent kwaan mzob re xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, nu kwaan re xaa kwaan mzaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa yilo, nu Jesucrist nak mod ke kwaan mas xwa lo yidoo ne.
Kwaanzee lee be nak mod tub yoo kwaan mza Jesucrist, kwaan nzho Mbi Naban cheen Dios leen.
Dios mxaal Pab zee zaa xaa kwent lo re xaa nanakt xaa IsraelNzhoo na lozhyib nel mzaa na kwent cheen Jesucrist lo re gu, xaa nanakt xaa Israel.
Telisa nela gu lee Dios, lo yalnkela cheen xaa, mzaa xaa zhiin ne lo na.
Dios mlu tub kwaan ngulaan lo na, modxa mza na chep kwent lo gu yilo.
Nu gorna lab gu kwaan kakee na nzho mod ne gu re kwaan ngulaan cheen Jesucrist.
Leeya nak tub kwaan namlut xaa lo re xaa yilo, per nal Dios mluya kwaan Mbi Naban cheen xaa lo re nu, xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesucrist, xaa nambey nak, nu lo re xaa kwaan nzaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa.
Lee kwaan ngulaan nak kwaane: Lee wdizh chul nle zee lee re xaa nanakt xaa Israel, kayaa leeka re kwaan chul kwaan nkayaa re nu, xaa Israel, nel tubka kwerp nak be, nu lal non rop naz be lo wdizh kwaan mlaa Dios kwent cheen Jesucrist.
Nu Dios mle zee za na kwent cheen wdizh chul ne, zee mzaa xaa zhiin ne lo na kwaan yalngezh cheen xaa nel nkela xaa na.
Nu mlu xaa yalnkela cheen xaa lo na leezha mzaa xaa zhiin ne lo na, nixa na nak xaa mas nanont lo re be, xaa mle nambey Jesús. Per mzaa xaa lo na zee za na kwent cheen re kwaan chul doo cheen Jesucrist lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel.
Nu Dios, xaa mdexkwaa rese kwaan, mxaal na, zee luu na re kwaan ngulaan nzha doo liin.
Nel nzhekla Dios luu yalnzhak cheen xaa lo re mbi kwaan nzho yiba, xomod mle xaa kwaan re xaa Jesús.
Nu axta yilo mlela Dios xgab cho kwaan le xaa kwaan Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be.
Nu nel xaa Jesús nak be nzho mod bii be lo Dios, nu ne be chul kayaa xaa be.
Kwaanzee naab na lo gu, nazhebt gu nel kadeed na bid, nel nzhekla na chul yo gu.
Pab naab kwent cheen re xaa ÉfesoKwaanzee nkichxub na nu nzhedizhno na Xuz be,
xaa mle zee rese be nkano le xaa, xaa nzho lo yizhyo nu xaa nzho naz leen yiba.
Naab na lo xaa zee lo re kwaan chul cheen xaa, le xaa zee nye zo gu leen lextoo gu kwaan yalngezh cheen Mbi Naban,
zee lee Jesucrist yo leen lextoo gu nel ngwii gu lo xaa. Noka naab na zee nye zo gu lo yalnkela cheen Dios mod tub yag kwaan nech nzho lox.
Nu snee nzho mod labeyy gu leeka kwaan labeyy stub naz xaa Jesús, xaa nambey, nel naro doo nak yalnkela cheen Jesucrist.
Nu naab na zee labeyy gu yalnkela cheen xaa, tub yalnkela kwaan gro doo kwaan nyent mod la yek re myet, nu snee zee nzho mod tira gak gu xaa xaa.
Nu lee nal, nzholl na lo Dios, xaa kwaan nkano yalngezh; lee xaa nzho mod le zyenra kwaan naab be lo xaa, nu re kwaan nzho yek be naab be lo xaa, kwent cheen yalngezh cheen xaa, kwaan nkee zhiin leen lextoo be.
¡Gool rese xaa Jesús lo Dios nal nu tubka, kwent cheen kwaan mle Jesucrist! ¡Sbaa gaka!
Tubka nak be kwaan Mbi NabanNzhoo na lozhyib kwent cheen Xaa Nabeyy, kwaanzee naab na lo gu; ble gu re kwaan mod nzhaal le guya nel Xaa Nabeyy mrezh gu yo gu sbaa.
Natot gu yalxwa,nadoo gok gu,byela gu ne gu tub gu stub gu, mod nzhaal kela gu tub gu stub gu,
nu tubka blaa gu nabeyy Mbi Naban lextoo rese gu, zee chul kwi gu.
Nel rese be nak mod tubka kwerp cheen Jesús, mod tubka nak Mbi Naban, nu tubka kwaan nkambaz be, leezha mleey Dios be gak be xaa xaa.
Nzho tubka Xaa Nabeyy be, nu nzho tubka xaa ngwii be lo, nu kwaan tubka le xaa mrubnis be;
nu nzho tubka Dios, xaa nak Xuz rese be; lee xaa nabeyy rese kwaan, nu nle xaa zee reke rese kwaan, nu rese pa nzo xaa.
Per kad tub be nzhakayaa kwaan nzhekla Jesucrist zaa lo be, lo yalnkela cheen xaa.
¿Nu cho kwaan nii kwaane “nguxoob xaa”? Kwaane nii yilotlaka mla xaa axta pa mas nech lo yizhyo.
Nu leeka xaa kwaan mla naz xan yizhyo, leeka xaa nak cho nguxoob pa mas ya nzeb lo yiba, zee nabeyy xaa lo rese kwaan.
Nu mselazh xaa kwaan lo rese xaa xaa.Mzaa xaa lo lak xaa zee kayaa xaa yalnabeyy lo xaa,nu mzaa xaa lo zlak xaa zee zaa xaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa,nu mzaa xaa lo zlak xaa zee zaa xaa kwent cheen wdizh chul lo re xaa zer labeyya,nu mzaa xaa lo zlak xaa zee gak xaa xaa kanap re xaa Jesús,nu mzaa xaa lo zlak xaa zee gak maestr zee luu xaa xtizh Dios.
Nu snee mle xaa zee re be, xaa mle nambey Jesús, kano kwaan nkin be kee be xchiin Dios, nu nye zo be lo Dios,
axta gorna rese be, xaa ngwii lo Jesucrist, kwi wen, nu axta labeyy wen be Xgann Dios, nu axta gorna nye zo be lo Dios, nu axta gorna tira nabeyy Jesucrist leen lextoo be.
Kwaanzee nagaktra be mod xaawin, xaa nanyet nzo. Nanzhaalt le be krer xtizh re xaa nzhekla kade be, re xaa nzhekla luux be; zee nagakt be mod tub kano kwaan ngitno nistoo.
Per nzhaal nii be re kwaan wli kwaan yalnkela, nu nzhaal nyera zo be lo Jesucrist, xaa nak xaa nabeyy lo rese be.
Nel lee re be nak mod tub kwerp nu Jesucrist nak mod yek be nu nle xaa zee gak be tubka kwerp. Nu nzhekla xaa zee dub kwerp cheen xaa wen gak, zee kad tub pa chul kee zhiin, zee chul nzhirooya lo yalnkela cheen xaa.
Yalnaban kwaan kub kwaan zaa JesucristNu kwaane nak kwaan nii na lo gu kwaan yalnabeyy cheen Xaa Nabeyy: Nayotra be mod re xaa nanakt xaa Dios, xaa kwaan nle xgab re kwaan nanont,
tira mkaw yek re xaa ba. Re xaa ne nankanot yalnaban kwaan nzaa Dios, nel ned lextoo xaa zee nanlabeyyt xaa xomod nak Dios.
Nu re xaa ne tira nangwiitra xaa lo re kwaan nle xaa, nebse nle xaa re xgab nachan kwaan nzho yek xaa, nle xaa rese kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen xaa, nu nle xaaya kwaan dub lextoo xaa.
Per leezha mseed gu cheen Jesucrist, namseedt gu le gu sbaa.
Telisa mbin gu kwaan wli nu mseed gu kwaan wli cheen Jesucrist, zee nayot gu sbaa.
Laa be mod mle be yilo, kwaan tira nawent nak.
Nzhaal chee be mod le be xgab,
nu gak be tub xaa kub, nel Dios mdexkwaa be zee wlipa zo be nali nu nzhul lo xaa.
Kwaanzee nakadetra be, nzhaal nii be duzna kwaan wli lo wechxinn be, nel rese be nak mod tubka kwerp.
Chelee be yii be, nanzhaalt yii be dub zhe, zee nalet be tub kwaan nawent,
nu sbaa nanzaat be diizh lo Maxuu.
Lee xaa nlewann nalewanntra xaa, sinka nzhaal kee xaa zhiin kwaan yaa xaa, zee nzho mod kano xaa tub kwaan selazh xaa lo re xaa kwaan nkin kwaan.
Nu naniit be wdizh nawent, nebse nzhaal nii be wdizh wen, kwaan nle yudar stub xaa kwaan nkenzha xtizh be, zee nye zo xaa lo Dios.
Nalet be zee gak nales lextoo Mbi Naban cheen Dios, nel lee xaa nzho leen lextoo be zee gakbeyy lee be nak xaa Dios axta mbizh kwaan zaa xaa yalnaban kwaan tira lo be.
Laa be:re kwaan nawent,re xyan,re yalnayii,dil,re mod nzhekla be gawyix be sa myet be.
Per nzhaal:wen gak belesla be ne be tub be stub be,yenlazh be kwaan nawent kwaan mle stub xaa lo be, modxa mchee Dios re jwalt cheen be, kwent cheen kwaan mle Jesucrist.
Xomod nzhaal yo re xaa nak xinn DiosNzhaal le be mod nle Dios, nel xinn Dios nak be.
Kela be re myet, modxa mkela Jesucrist be nu mzaa xaa xaa ngut xaa kwent cheen re be, mod tub gon o mod tub ma nteed xaa lo Dios, nu ngoka tub kwaan nyula Dios.
Re be nak xaa Jesús, xaa nambey, nu nanzhaalt:wdizh be re kwent kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen be,nu nixa nawdizht be kwent cheen re kwaan beed,nu nixa nazoblazht be.
Nu nixa nazaat be kwent cheen re kwaan beed,nixa re wdizh kwaan nanont,nixa nakita be kwaan re wdizh nachan;per nzhaal zaa be dixkix lo Dios.
Nel nela be loka xaa nle:re kwaan beed,re kwaan nawent,yalnzoblazh,ngwii xaa lo re maj,rese xaa nle re kwaane narept xaa Pa Nabeyy Jesucrist nu Dios.
Kwaanzee nanzhaalt zhaal be kwaan re xaa snee nle.
Yilo lee re be nzo lo yalnakaw, per nal nzola be lo xni nel tubka nak be kwaan Xaa Nabeyy, kwaanzee le be kwaan nzhaal le be nel lo xni nzo be,
nel kwaan nroo naz lo xni nak: gak be wen, nali zo be lo Dios, nu le be duzna kwaan wli.
Nu tubka kwaan be kwaan nzhekla Xaa Nabeyy.
Nu nalet be re kwaan nle re xaa kwaan nzo lo yalnakaw, mas wen zaa be kwent cheena zee zeen re xaaya.
Nu axta nzhaal ton be zaa be kwent re kwaan nle re xaa xlaan;
per gorna lee rese kwaane lu lo xni, nlabeyy re xaaya,
nel lo xni nzhakbeyy rese kwaan, mod nzhé re xaa:Guxche, nel lu nak mod tub xaa naxna,bzoli, nel lu nak mod tub xaa ngut,zee lee Jesucrist le zee kaxni yek lu.
Nu kwaanzee, wii be lo re kwaan nle be, nu nayot be mod tub xaa nachan, yo be mod tub xaa nzho yek.
Rese mbizh le be re kwaan wen, nel rese mbizh ne ded kwaan nawent.
Nu nagakt be xaa ned, sinka kwaan be kwaan nzhekla Xaa Nabeyy.
Nazuzht be, nel kwaane nle zee luux be leeka be, mas wen laa be nabeyy Mbi Naban lextoo be.
Mas wen yé be lo tub be stub be xomod wen nak Dios, zee gool be salm nu kant kwaan dub lextoo be lo Xaa Nabeyy.
Nu lo rese kwaan, zaa be dixkix lo Dios, xaa nak Xuz be kwaan yalnabeyy cheen Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be.
Xomod nzhaal yo re sawlizh xaaRese be nzhaal gon xtizh tub be stub be, nu snee nlu be nzhon be xtizh Jesucrist.
Re ngwnaa nzhaal gon me xtizh sa me, modxa nii Xaa Nabeyy lo me.
Nel lee xaabyi nak xaa nabeyy lo ngwnaa, modxa nabeyy Jesucrist lo re xaa xaa, nel Jesucrist mloo re xaa xaa lo yalgut, nu mle xaa zee gak xaa mod kwerp cheen xaa.
Nu sbaa mod nzhon re xaa Jesús xtizh Jesús, sbaaka nzhaal gon ngwnaa xtizh xmbyi me lo rese kwaan.
Re xaabyi nzhaal kela xaa sa xaa, modxa mkela Jesucrist re xaa nak xaa xaa, nu mzaa xaa leeka lee xaa ngut kwent cheen re xaa xaa, zee chul yo re xaa xaa.
Kwaane mle xaa zee koxcho xaa re xaa nak xaa xaa, nu mle nzhul xaa re xaa xaa lo re jwalt cheen xaa kwaan nis leezha mkayaa xaa xtizh Dios.
Nu sbaa mle Jesucrist zee lee re xaa xaa gak mod tub ngwnaa kwaan ka xaa; zee nzhul, nu nali nu chul gak me.
Sbaaka nzhaal kela xaabyi sa xaa modxa nkela xaa leeka kwerp cheen xaa, nel lee xaa kwaan nkela sa leeka lee xaa nkela xaa.
Nel nik tub xaa nanayiit ne leeka xkwerp, sinka nkela xaaya nu nkanap xaaya, modxa nkela Jesucrist re xaa xaa,
nel nak re be tubka kwerp cheen xaa.
“Kwaanzee lee xaabyi roo lo xuz xaa nu lo xnaa xaa nu chelya rop sa xaa, zee rop xaa gak tubka kwerp”.
Mza na kwent cheen tub kwaan gro kwaan ngulaan axta yilo, kwent cheen Jesucrist nu re xaa xaa.
Nu sbaaka nzhaal kela xaabyi sa xaa, kwentaxa nkela xaa leeka lee xaa, nu sbaaka lee ngwnaa nzhaal gon me xtizh xaabyi me.
Lee re madwin nzhaal gon mad xtizh xuz mad nu xtizh xnaa mad, nel nak mad xinn Xaa Nabeyy, nu kwaane mxaal Xaa Nabeyy, leeya nak tub kwaan nali.
<sup>(2-3)</sup> Nel snee nzhé ley cheen Ches: “Nazeret lu diizh lo xuz lu nu lo xnaa lu, zee yo wen lu nu xche ban lu lo yizhyo”. Kwaane nak wdizh yilotlaka kwaan mzaa Dios kwent, zee chul ded xaa gona.
Nu lee re xaa nak xuz mad nanzhaalt chal xyan xaa mad, sinka nzhaal seed xaa mad gak mad tub mad wen, nu nzhaal seed xaa mad mod nzhekla Xaa Nabeyy.
Rese xaa nak mos, nzhaal gon xaa xtizh xaa nabeyy lo xaa lo yizhyo ne, nzhaal nali gak xaa lo xaa, nu nzhaal zheb xaa ne xaa xaa, kwentaxa nzhon xaa xtizh Jesucrist.
Nu nanzhaalt kee xaa zhiin nebse leezha kawii xaa nabeyy lo xaa zee chul zo xaa kwaan lee xaa, nzhaal kee xaa zhiin mod nzhaal kee mos cheen Jesucrist zhiin kwaan dub lextoo xaa, nu snee nle xaa kwaan nzhekla Dios.
Nzhaal kee xaa xchiin xaa nabeyy kwaan dub lextoo xaa, mod nzhaal kee xaa xchiin mer Xaa Nabeyy, nu nalet xaaya mod nkee xaa xchiin myet.
Nel kad tub xaa, nixa mos nak xaa nu nixa xaa nabeyy nak xaa, kayaa xaa lo Xaa Nabeyy tub kwaan wen nel wen mle xaa.
Nu rese xaa nabeyy nanzhaalt yii xaa lo xmos xaa, nel lee Xaa Nabeyy nzho naz yiba nu nabeyy lo ropse xaa; nu lal non ropse lo Xaa Nabeyy.
Re kwaan mzaa Dios dil be kwaan MaxuuLee nal nii na lo gu, gok gu tub xaa ngezh kwaan yalngezh cheen Xaa Nabeyy.
Nu ble xchiin gu kwaan mzaa Dios lo gu zee nzho mod kanap gu gu, zee nzho mod zo nye gu lo re yalnkade cheen Maxuu. Leeya nak kwenta re kwaan nzheno tub soldad lo dil.
Nu nakadilt be kwaan tub myet, lee be kadil kwaan yalngezh cheen re mbi mal kwaan nzho naz ya, nu kwaan re mbi mal kwaan nabeyy lo yizhyo ne, kwaan nzho lo yalnakaw nu nle re kwaan nawent.
Kwaanzee, le xchiin be kwaan mzaa Dios lo be zee nzho mod kanap be be, zee nzho mod ye be ded be re mbizh nawent, zee gorna ngulo mded dil nali zo be mod tub soldad xaa nye nzo.
Kwaanzee nye zo be mod tub soldad.Leezha nii be kwaan wli, kwaane nak mod yed kwaan nzii soldad lextoo soldad.Leezha nzo be nali lo Dios, kwaane nak mod yiib kwaan nsaaw laz soldad.
Leezha zaa be kwent cheen wdizh chul, kwaan nle zee nix kwi re myet, kwaane nak mod yelyed kwaan nkee nii soldad.
Leezha ngwii be lo Jesús, kwaane nak mod tub lee yiib kwaan nzho yaa soldad, nu sbaa nsaaw be tir kwaan nkee wez kwaan ki yek, kwaan nkee Maxuu yenn be.
Leezha nselazh be nkano be yalnaban kwaan tira, kwaane nak mod bchog nzob yek soldad. Noka nzhaal zen be espad cheen Mbi Naban kwaan nak xtizh Dios.
Tubka wdizhno be Dios, nel Mbi Naban nle yudar nii be. Nu tubka list zo be kwezh be lo Dios kwent cheen re xaa Jesús, xaa nambey.
Nu noka naab gu lo Dios, zee zaa xaa re wdizh kwaan nzhaal nii na, nu zaa xaa balor lextoo na, zee nzho mod za na kwent cheen wdizh chul, tub kwaan ngulaan axta yilo.
Kwaan kaden nkadoo na nu nzhoo na lozhyib, nel nza na kwent cheen wdizh chul, nixa na nak tub xaa mxaal Dios nii kwent cheen xaa. Naab gu lo Dios zee yo balor lextoo na za na kwent cheen wdizh chul ne mod nzhaal za naya.
Dix gwluzhWech Tíquico, xaa nali nak nu tubka nkee xchiin Xaa Nabeyy, yiid xaa lo gu zaa xaa kwent cheen na, re kwaan kadeed na.
Kwaanzee xaal na xaa lo gu, zee zaa xaa kwent xomod nzho re nu nee, zee zaa xaa balor lextoo gu.
Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa nak Xuz be, nu Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy lo be, le zee nix kwi re be nu le zee kela tub be stub be, nu le zee tubka ngwii rese be lo xaa.
Nu naab na lo xaa zee luu xaa yalnkela cheen xaa lo rese be, xaa nkela Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, kwaan dub lextoo be.Sbaa gaka.
<font color=teal>Yech kwaan mkee Pab lo re xaa yezh Filipos</font>Yech kwaan mxaal Pab lo re xaa FiliposNa Pab rop Timoteo, xmos Jesucrist, kakee na yech ne lo rese xaa mle nambey Jesús, xaa nzho yezh Filipos; nu lo re xaa gol xaa nabeyy lo re xaa Jesús; nu lo re xaa nle yudar re xaa prob.
Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa nak Xuz be nu xuz Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, luu xaa yalnkela cheen xaa lo rese gu nu le xaa zee kwi chul re gu.
Pab ngunaab lo Dios kwent cheen re xaa JesúsRese welt gorna nselazh na re gu nza na dixkix lo Dios.
Nu gorna naab na lo Dios kwent cheen rese gu tubka nyakdoola na
nel tubka nkee re be xchiin Jesucrist, axta mbizh kwaan mzelo gu ngwii gu lo Jesucrist, nu axta mbizh nalzhe tubka nkee re be zhiin.
Nela na lee Dios mzelo nle re kwaan chul cheen xaa lo re gu, nu sbaaka lux xaa xchiin xaa lo gu axta gorna bare Jesucrist stuba.
Nzhaal doo le na xgab re gu nel nkela na re gu, nel lo rese be mlu Dios yalnkela cheen xaa. Mxaal xaa na nkee na xchiin xaa nu namlaat re gu na lo rese kwaan. Kwaanzee nixa nzhoo na lozhyib tubka nzo re gu kwaan na, nu nixa lo xaa nak zhiin nzo na, tubka nza na kwent kwaan wli cheen Jesucrist, seetaka nzo re gu kwaan na.
Nu ne wen Dios nkedoola na re gu kwaan yalnkela cheen Jesucrist.
Zee ne gu xomod kweey gu kwaan wen lo re kwaan nawent, zee sbaa gak gu tub xaa nambey, nu tub xaa nakanotra jwalt axta mbizh kwaan bare Jesucrist.
Nu noka naab na lo Dios zee le Jesucrist gak gu tub xaa nali lo xaa, zee rese myet gool lo Dios nu nii xaa re kwaan chul lo Dios.
Tubka nzo na kwaan JesucristWech nu bzan, nzhekla na ne re gu lee re bid kwaan kadeed na mle zee zyen doo myet mkayaa wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist.
Nu axta re soldad, xaa Roma, xaa nkanap re kwaan nee, nu re stub naz myet nela xaa lee na nzhoo lozhyib nel mzaa na kwent cheen wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist.
Nu zyen doo re wech nanzhebtra nzaa kwent cheen wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist, nel ngune xaa xomod nzhoo na lozhyib.
Wli kwaane: Rol xaa nzaa kwent cheen wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist nel nzhekla xaa gak nonra xaa lo na, nu nel nawent nzhak lextoo xaa ne xaa na, nu lee stub naz xaa nzaa kwent cheen wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist nel nzho kwaan wen lextoo xaa.
Nu zrol xaa nzaa kwent cheen Jesucrist kwaan yalnkela, nel ne xaa lee Dios mleey na zee nzhoo na nee, zee yé na lo re myet lee kwent cheen Jesucrist nak kwaan wli.
Per lee stub naz xaa nzaa kwent cheen Jesucrist, nel nanalit nzhak lextoo xaa, nu nel nzhekla xaa gaazh xaa re kwaan nawent tich na, nal nzhoo na lozhyib.
Per tira nanonta, nexa xomod nzhak lextoo re xaa ne xaa na, chol wen nzhak lextoo xaa nu chol nawent nzhak lextoo xaa ne xaa na, per kwaan nyakla na nak nel nzaa xaa kwent cheen Jesucrist.Nu seesa yaklara na,
nel nela na lee re kwaan kanaab gu lo Dios nu re mod nle Mbi Naban cheen Jesucrist yudar na, le zee koo re xaa na.
Nzhekla doo na zee nalet na nik tub kwaan zee seton na leeka na. Sinka nzhekla na kano na balor leen lextoo na zee lee Jesucrist gak non lo re myet kwent cheen na, nala nu tira; nexa chol mbanaka na nu chol ngutla naya.
Chelee na seesaka mban na mbanaka na kwaan Jesucrist, nu chelee na yet na le na gan yalnaban kwaan tira.
Per chelee na seesaka mban na lo yizhyo ne, seetaka nzho mod za na kwent wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist lo re myet; kwaanzee nanet na xana kwaan wenra, yalgut o yalnaban.
Kwaanzee nagan doo labeyy na cho kwaan wenra lo rop kwaane. Nzhekla na yet na, nel nzhekla na nya na zo na lo Jesucrist naz leen yiba, kwaan nak kwaan mas chulra lo na.
Per nzak na wenaka mban na, nel seetaka nkin re gu na.
Nu nela na seesa zbanra na, zee zo na lo re gu, zee nzho mod le na zee zo nyera re gu, zee nzho mod nera gu xomod nak re xcheen Dios zee mas yaklara gu wii gu lo Jesucrist.
Kwaanzee gorna yasewii na lo re gu stub welt, zee nix doo gak lextoo re gu gool gu lo Jesucrist kwent cheen na.
Nebse kwaan nzhaal le re gu nak le gu re kwaan wen kwaan nxaal wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist, zee nii wen stub naz xaa lo Jesucrist. Nexa chol yal na lo re gu nu chol nayalt na lo re gu, per nzhekla na gon na lee re gu tubka lal nye nzo, nu tubka lal nle re gu xgab, zee nalet re xaa nangwiit lo wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist gan lo re gu.
Nu tira nazhebt gu ne gu re xaa nayii ne gu, nel kwaan ba nak tub nseyn lee re xaa ba telisa lux yalnaban cheen, nu lee re gu kano yalnaban kwaan nzaa Dios.
Nel mzaa Dios diizh ngwii gu lo Jesucrist nu noka ded gu bid kwent cheen Jesucrist.
Nu leeka bid kwaan kaded gu nal nak re bid kwaan mwii gu mdeed na yilo, nu nak re bid kwaan kayon gu kadeed na nal.
Nebse Jesucrist nak xaa non lo rese xaaNel nzaa be balor lextoo tub be stub be nel Jesucrist nabeyy leen lextoo be; nel kwaan yalnkela cheen xaa nseleyy xaa tub be stub be; nel leeka Mbi Naban nzho lextoo be kwaan ngu lextoo Jesucrist; nel nkano be yalnkela, nu nlesla be ne be tub be stub be;
kwaanzee, blera gu gak nix doo lextoo na nel tubka nak xgab cheen rese gu, nu leeka yalnkela kwaan nkano tub gu nkano stub gu. Tubka xgab nkano rese gu, nu tubka kwaan nle re gu.
Nik tub welt nalet be xgab nebse re be, nu nixa natot be yalxwa zee nii chul re xaa lo be, sinka le wen be lextoo be nu le be xgab xwara re myet ke be.
Nanzhaalt le be nebse kwaan nzhekla be sinka noka nzhaal le be kwaan nzhekla stub naz re wechxinn be.
Tubka le be xgab modxa mle Jesucrist xgab.
Nel nixa lal nak rop xaa Dios,per namtot xaa yalxwa ke lee xaa nak lal kwaan Dios.
Mlaa xaa rese kwaan nak xcheen xaa,nu mlaa xaa yalnabeyy cheen xaa,nu ngok xaa mod tub mos,nu ngol xaa kwenta myet lo yizhyo ne.
Nu nel mod myet ngol xaa,zee mlib xaa lextoo xaa gon xaa xtizh Dios,nu mbin xaa xtizh Dios axta ngut xaa,nu axta yalnto doo ngut xaa lo krus.
Kwaanzee gorna lee rese mbi nu rese xaa nzho leen yiba nu lo yizhyo nu xan yizhyo gon le Jesús,rese xaa kichxub lo Jesús.
Rese mbi nu rese myet yé lee Jesucrist nak Xaa Nabeyy,nu gool xaa lo Dios xaa nak xuz xaa.
Gok gu xni lo yalnakawKwaanzee, nii na lo rese gu xaa nkela na, nixa leezha nzo na kwaan re gu, nu nixa nal zit nzo na lo re gu, modxa mbin gu xtizh Dios, sbaaka nzhaal tubka le xchiin gu yalnaban kwaan mzaa xaa lo be nel nzheb be ne be xaa.
Nel Dios nak xaa nle zee nzhal re xgab wen yek be, nu lee xaa le yudar be, zee nzho mod le beya mod nyula xaa.
Rese kwaan le be kwaan dub lextoo be, nu nalenedt be lextoo be le beya, nu nadildiizht beya.
Zee nayizhalt nik tub jwalt lo re be, le be kwaan nzhaal le re xinn Dios, zee nzhul na be gorna zo be xsaww lo re myet xaa nzeb jwalt, nu lo re xaa nakap. Zee gak be mod xni kwaan nzaa re mbal ma nzob naz yiba; sbaaka tubka nzhaal zaa be xni lo re xaa nzhi lo yalnakaw.
Kwaanzee tubka zaa be kwent cheen xtizh Dios kwaan zaa yalnaban kwaan tira. Zee gorna bare Jesucrist yaad stub welt, zeesi nix doo gak lextoo na ne na re gu, nu noka zeesi nzho mod yé na namkeet na zhiin sbaasa.
Nu nyakdoola na, nel tubka ngwii gu lo Jesucrist nu kwaan nkee gu zhiin lo Jesucrist nak mod tub gon kwaan zaa gu lo Dios. Kwaanzee, noka na, chelee re xaa gut xaa na zee lee xren na gak mod tub gon xis ub kwaan nxo re ngwleyy lo Dios. Sbaa tubka lal zaa be gon lo Dios nu tubka lal yakla be.
Nu byakdoola re gu, nu nix doo gok lextoo re gu tubka kwaan na.
Pab mzaa kwent cheen Timoteo rop EpafroditoChelee Xaa Nabeyy nzhekla, zee xaal na Timoteo lo re gu, zee gorna bare xaa nix doo gak lextoo na gon na kwent kwaan zaa xaa cheen re gu.
Nel nankanot na stub xaa kwaan lal le rop nu xgab nu tub xaa wlipa nle xgab re gu.
Per lee stub naz re myet nebse re xcheen xaa nle xgab, per nanlet xaa xgab re kwaan nak xcheen Jesucrist.
Per ngunela re gu xomod nak Timoteo nu mlula xaa xomod wen nak xaa gorna mle xaa yudar na mzaa nu kwent cheen xtizh Dios, mle xaa yudar na kwentaxa nle tub xaa yudar xuz xaa.
Kwaanzee nle na xgab xaal na Timoteo lo re gu, leezha yilo ne na cho re kwaan deed na.
Noka nle na xgab lee Xaa Nabeyy le yudar na zee naxchetra yal na lo re gu.
Nzak na wen xaal na wech be Epafrodito lo re gu stub welt, xaa myedoola mkee rop nu zhiin, xaa mxaal re gu le yudar na lo re kwaan mkin na.
Nzhekla doo xaa ne xaa lo re gu, nu nle doo xaa xgab nel mbin gu lee xaa ngok ne.
Nu wli ngok ne xaa, nu axta mer nget xaa; per mlesla Dios ne xaa, nu noka mlesla Dios ne na, nel chelee xaa nget xaa lo yalyizh ba mas ngak nales lextoo na.
Kwaanzee nal lijer doo xaal na xaa lo re gu, zee nix doo gak lextoo gu ne gu lo xaa, snee lee na nagak nalestra tant lextoo nal.
Nu gok nix doo lextoo re gu bkayaa gu xaa, nu wen gok gu lo xaa, nu lo re xaa nak kwenta lee xaa,
nel mer nget xaa kwent mkee xaa xchiin Jesucrist. Mer nglux xaa yalnaban cheen xaa nel mle xaa yudar na, lo re kwaan nyent mod ngyiid re gu ngle gu yudar na.
Kwaan non nak labeyy xaa JesucristNu nal rese gu wech nu bzan, nix doo gok lextoo gu nel xaa Jesucrist nak gu. Nu nanyachet lextoo na nii na re kwaan nguniila na yilo, nel leeya nak tub kwaan nzho mod kanap gu lo re xgab nawent.
Bkanap gu gu lo re xaa nak kwenta tub mbak ma nakap doo, nel mbezh re xaa nzhaal choog re xaa tik yed cho xaa zee yo xaa beyy cheen re nu, xaa Israel, zee nzho mod le xaa gan yalnaban kwaan tira. Bkanap gu gu lo re xaa snee nle, nel nawent nak kwaan kale xaa.
Per lee re be nak xaa wlipa nkano beyy cheen Dios nel nzho Mbi Naban cheen Dios leen lextoo be, xaa nle zee nzholl be lo Dios; nu nyak doo lextoo be nel Jesucrist mle zee nak be xaa xaa. Nu nangwiit be lo re kwaan nle be,
nel nik tub xaa nyent mod nya lo Dios kwent cheen re kwaan nle xaa. Nu chol sbaa naka, ¡na nak xaa xwara lo rese xaa!
Xonaka mbizh nzha ngol na mchoog xaa tik yed cho na, kwaan nak beyy cheen re nu, xaa Israel; na nak mer tub xaa Israel; nu na nak dii cheen Benjamín; nu na nak mer xinn xaa hebreo xaa mleey Dios; noka ngok na fariseo, xaa ngozhaw doo ley cheen Ches.
Tant nzhekla na le na kwaan wen zee mrenal na re xaa mreke tich Jesucrist, nu nyent mod gaazh xaa nik tub kwaan tich na nel mle na rese kwaan nkee lo ley cheen Ches.
Per rese kwaane, kwaan ngok non lo na yilo, tira nanontra lo na nal nel nreke na tich Jesucrist.
Nu ne na nik tub kwaan ba nanont nu rese kwaan ba nak kwenta yix wen per kwaan nonra nak mlabeyy na Jesucrist Xaa Nabeyy na, nu nel ngwii na lo Jesucrist zee mlaa na rese kwaan mzak na wen yilo. Nu nal nebse nzhekla na tubka zo na lo Jesucrist,
Kwaan nzhekla na nak mas labeyyra na Jesucrist, nu kano na yalngezh cheen yalnroban cheen xaa. Nu listla nzo na deed na bid modxa mded lee xaa bid, nu axta listla nzo na yet na modxa ngut xaa,
zee noka na roban lo yalgut.
Nu naniit na ngulola mle na gan gak na kwenta Jesucrist; per nza na jwers zee le na gan gak na mer mod nzhekla Jesucrist gorna mleey xaa na gak na xaa xaa.
Rese gu wech nu bzan, naniit na ngulola mle na gana; per kale na kwenta tub xaa nrexonn tub karrer, nyenlazh na re kwaan mlake naz tras nu nzhexoon na naz delant.
Nza doo na jwers zee le na gan karrer, zee le na gan kwaan zaa Dios lo na gorna mbezh xaa na, zee kayaa naya naz leen yiba kwent cheen Jesucrist.
Rese be xaa nye nzo lo xtizh Dios lal nzhaal le re be xgab; nu chelee zlak gu nle xgab stub mod, Dios zle yudar gu zee laya yek gu.
Zee tubka le be kwaan wen lo re kwaan ngulola mseed be.
Rese gu wech nu bzan, tubka le gu kwentaxa mle na, nu wii gu lo re xaa nle kwentaxa mseed na xaa.
Nel zyen doo welt nzha nii na kwaane lo re gu, nu nal nzhon na nza na kwenta lo re gu, zyen doo xaa nayii ne krus cheen Jesucrist nel nanlet xaa kwaan wen.
Lee dios cheen xaa nak re kwaan nzoblazh xaa, nu lee yalxwa cheen xaa nak yalnto cheen stub naz re myet, nebse kwaan yizhyo nle xaa xgab. Per mbizh gwluzhtlaka tira yet xaa.
Per lee be nak xaa yiba, nu nkambaz be yaad Jesucrist Xaa Nabeyy be, xaa yaad naz leen yiba, xaa zaa yalnaban lo be.
Lee xaa chee xkwerp be kwaan naguun kwaan nkano be nal, zee gaka kwenta xkwerp lee xaa kwaan nak kwaan chul doo. Nu nzho mod le xaaya nel kano xaa yalngezh nabeyy xaa lo rese kwaan.
Gok nix lextoo guRese gu wech nu bzan, nkedoola na re gu nu nzhekla na yasewii na lo re gu nel lee re gu mle zee nix doo nzhak lextoo na selazh na re gu. Nu rese gu xaa nyenn na nzhekla na zee nye nzo gu lo Xaa Nabeyy.
Bzan na, Evodia nu Síntique, naab na lo gu, bri wen gu mod nzhekla Xaa Nabeyy.
Noka naab na lo lu, xaa tant mle yudar na lo zhiin ne, ble yudar rop ngwnaa ba zee kwi wen rop me, nel rop me nu Clemente mzo lo na gorna mza na kwent cheen xtizh Dios, nu noka mzo stub naz xaa kwaan na. Nu Dios mkee le re xaa lo yech cheen yalnaban kwaan tira.
Tubka nix doo gok lextoo gu bwii gu lo Xaa Nabeyy, nu bare na nii naya lo gu stub welt, gok nix doo lextoo gu.
Nu noka gok nadoo gu zee wii re myet lo gu zee ne xaa lee gu nak tub xaa nadoo, nel lee Xaa Nabeyy nyaadla gax.
Per nik tub kwaan nanzhaalt le gu xgab, sinka guzh gu rese kwaan lo Dios nu gunaab gu rese kwaan nkin gu lo Dios, nu bzaa gu dixkix lo xaa lo rese kwaan.
Nel Dios nle zee chul doo gak lextoo gu, nu nixa nyent mod ne re myet xomod ngok chul lextoo gu. Nel snee nkanap Dios re xgab cheen gu, nu nkanap xaa lextoo gu, nel xaa Jesucrist nak gu.
Ble gu xgab kwaan wenKwaan gwluzhtlaka nii na lo re gu wech nu bzan, nzhaal le be xgab:nebse kwaan wli,nu nebse kwaan xwa,nu nebse kwaan nali,nu nebse kwaan nzhul,nu nebse kwaan chul,nu nebse kwaan non,nu loka kwaan nzhaal gool be lo,nu rese kwaan wen doo nak.Rese kwaan ba nak kwaan nzhaal le be xgab.
Ble gu re kwaan mseed na gu, nu re kwaan mkayaa gu lo na, nu re kwaan mbin gu ngunii na, nu re kwaan ngune gu mle na. Ble guya zee lee Dios, xaa nzho mod le chul lextoo gu, zo lo re gu.
Gon kwaan mzaa re xaa yezh Filipos lo PabNix doo nzhak lextoo na, nu za na dixkix lo Xaa Nabeyy nel mle gu yudar na stub welt, nu ne na tubka nzhekla gu le gu yudar na, per ngu tub tyemp nyent mod ngle gu yudar na.
Nazat na kwent ne nel nkin na kwaan; nel mseed na nix doo nzhak lextoo na lo kwaan nkano na.
Nyen na leezha nyenta, nu nyen na leezha nzho zyena, nu nyen na gorna ngazhe lextoo na, nu nyen na leezha nlaan na, nu nyen na nkano na zyen kwaan nu nyen na leezha nik tub kwaan nankanot na.
Rese kwaan nzho mod le na, nel Jesucrist nak xaa nzaa jwers lo na.
Per lee re gu wen mle gu yudar na leezha mkin na kwaan.
Gorna mzelo na mza na kwent cheen wdizh chul cheen yalnaban kwaan tira lo gu nu gorna mroo na yizhyo Macedonia, nebse re gu xaa yezh Filipos, mzaa gon lo na.
Nu noka leezha nzo na yezh Tesalónica, mxaal gu gon lo na chop welt leezha nkin naya.
Nankwaant na nebse kayaa na kwaan zaa gu, sinka nzhekla na kayaa gu rese kwaan chul cheen Dios, mod tub xaa nkayaa xinn xdemi nel mle gu yudar na.
Kwaanzee lee Dios, xaa tubka nzo kwaan be, zaa rese kwaan nkin gu lo gu. Nu nzho mod zaa Dios re kwaan chul lo gu nel nkano xaa rese kwaan, nu zaa xaaya lo gu nel xaa Jesucrist nak gu.
Zee tubka gool be lo Dios, xaa nak Xuz be. ¡See gaka!
Guzh gu “dix” cheen na lo re xaa mle nambey Jesús, xaa nzhi baa. Nu noka re wech xaa nzo kwaan na nee nxaal “dix” lo re gu.
Re xaa Jesús, xaa nambey nak, xaa nzho li César nu re stub naz xaa Jesús nxaal “dix” lo re gu.
Nzhekla na lee Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, luu xaa yalnkela cheen xaa lo rese gu.Sbaa gaka.
<font color=teal>Yech kwaan mkee Pab lo re xaa yezh Colosas</font>Dix cheen PabDix re gu.Na nak Pab, xaa mkayaa yalnabeyy lo Jesús, nel sbaa nzhekla Dios. Kakee na yech ne tubka kwaan wech Timoteo.
Kakee naya lo re gu, xaa tubka ngwii lo Jesucrist, xaa mle nambey gu, xaa nzho yezh Colosas. Nzhekla na lee Dios, xaa nak Xuz be, luu yalnkela cheen xaa lo gu nu le xaa zee kwi chul re gu.
Kwaane naab Pab lo Dios kwent cheen re xaa JesúsKad welt leezha nzhedizhno nu Dios, xaa nak Xuz Jesucrist Xaa Nabeyy be, naab nu kwent cheen gu. Nu nzaa nu dixkix lo Dios,
nel mbin nu xomod ngwii gu lo Jesucrist, nu xomod nkela gu re xaa Jesús, xaa nambey.
Nu noka nzaa nu dixkix lo Dios, nel nkambaz gu re kwaan nakladiizh kayaa gu naz leen yiba. Nu re gu nkambaz kwaane nel mkenzha gu wdizh chul kwaan wli nak.
Nu leeka wdizh chul kwaan mkenzha re gu, nzharech dubse yizhyo, nu zyen doo xaa nzhaxen lo xcheen Dios, leeka mod nzhaxen re gu axta mbizh kwaan mbin gu wdizh chul ne, nu ngune gu wli nkela Dios gu.
Nu lee wdizh chul ne mlu Epafras lo gu. Lee xaa nak tub xmos Jesucrist tubka kwaan re nu, nu nkela nu xaa, nu tubka nkee xaa zhiin kwaan re nu.
Nu lee xaa nak xaa mzaa kwent cheen gu lo re nu, xomod nkela gu re xaa Jesús kwaan yalnkela kwaan mzaa Mbi Naban lo gu.
Nu kwaanzee lee re nu, axta mbizh kwaan mzaa xaa kwent cheen gu lo nu, tubka naab nu lo Dios zee luu xaa rese kwaan nzhekla xaa le gu, nu zaa xaa yalnzhak lo gu zee la re xcheen xaa yek gu.
Nu snee nzho mod yo gu mod nzhaal yo gu, nel xaa Xaa Nabeyy nak gu, zee le gu rese kwaan nyula xaa, kwaan nak kwaan wen, zee wenra labeyy gu Dios.
Nu naab nu zee kwaan yalngezh kwaan gro cheen Dios le xaa zee gak ngezh gu, zee yela gu ded gu rese kwaan, nu chul gak lextoo gu,
nu tubka zaa gu dixkix lo Xuz be kwaan dub lextoo gu, nel mle xaa zee kayaa be re kwaan nak xcheen xaa, nu zo be lo xni chul cheen xaa tubka kwaan re xaa Jesús, xaa nambey nak,
nu nel mloo xaa be lo xaa nabeyy lo yalnakaw nu mbe xaa be pa nabeyy Xgann xaa, xaa nkedoola xaa.
Nu kwent cheen kwaan mle Xgann xaa, mzi xaa be zee gak be xaa xaa, nu mchee xaa re jwalt cheen be.
Jesucrist nak xaa nabeyy rese kwaanJesucrist nak lal kwenta Dios, xaa nanyunt, nu nak xaa Xgann Dios, nu axta yilo ngu xaa leezha zeraka dexkwaa Dios nik tub kwaan.
Nu kwaan Jesucrist mdexkwaa Dios rese kwaan nzho leen yiba nu kwaan nzho lo yizhyo ne, kwaan nyun nu kwaan nanyunt, nu noka mdexkwaa xaa re yalnabeyy nu re yalngezh. Rese mdexkwaa Jesucrist zee gaka xcheen xaa.
Jesucrist nak xaa yilo lo rese kwaan, nu lee xaa nak xaa nabeyy zee naluuxt rese kwaan.
Nu noka Jesucrist nak Xaa Nabeyy lo rese xaa xaa, mod nabeyy yek myet lo xkwerp myet. Nu lee xaa nak mer xaa non nel lee xaa nak xaa yilotlaka mroban, zee lee xaa gak Xaa Nabeyy lo rese kwaan.
Nel nyula Dios lee Jesucrist nak lal kwenta lee xaa,
nu kwaan Jesucrist mle Dios zee chul kwi rese kwaan kwaan lee xaa, rese kwaan nzhi lo yizhyo nu rese kwaan nzho naz leen yiba, nel Jesucrist mxo xren lo krus.
Yilo lee re be ngok xaa zit nzo lo Dios nu ngok be xkontrad Dios, lo re kwaan nle be nu lo re xgab cheen be,
per nal Dios mle zee kwi wen be kwaan lee xaa kwent cheen mod ngut Jesucrist. Nu mle xaa kwaane zee mlexcho xaa be gak be xaa xaa, zee gak nzhul be, nu nambey be, nu zo be nali lo xaa,
chelee be tubka ngwii be lo Jesucrist, nu tubka nye zo be lo xaa, nu chelee be tubka kwaz be kayaa be re kwaan nzaa wdizh chul kwent. Kwaane nak kwaan nza na kwent, nu kwaan mbin gu nu kwaan mbin re xaa dubse yizhyo.
Dios mleey Pab zee kee xaa zhiin lo re xaa JesúsNu nyakla na ndeed na bid kwent cheen re gu, nel kadeed na bid kwaan nzho jwalt ded Jesucrist kwent cheen re xaa xaa, re xaa nak mod kwerp cheen xaa.
zee labeyy gu rese kwaan ngulaan axta nzha zyen doo liin, per nal mlu xaaya lo rese be, xaa mle Jesús nambey.
Nu lo be mlu Dios rese kwaan chul kwaan ngulaan, nu nzaa xaaya lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel. Kwaan ngulaan ne nak: Jesucrist nzho leen lextoo re be, kwaanzee nkambaz be nya be pa chul cheen Dios.
Nu kwaanzee lee re nu nzaa kwent cheen Jesucrist rese pa nya nu, nu mbezh nu lo re xaa kwaan re yalnzhak cheen Dios, nu nseed nu re xaa zee nali zo xaa lo Jesucrist.
Nu kwaan dub lextoo na nkee na zhiin ne, nu nzho mod le naya nel lee yalngezh cheen Jesucrist nzho leen lextoo na.
Nu nzhekla na ne gu xomod kadil na kwent cheen re gu, nu kwent cheen re xaa nzho yezh Laodicea, nu kwent cheen re xaa zer labeyy na,
zee yo balor leen lextoo rese gu, nu gak gu tubka nel nkela gu tub gu stub gu, zee nzho mod kano gu yalnzhak cheen Dios, zee labeyy gu kwaan mkaxlaan Dios yilo, kwaan nak Jesucrist;
nu lo lee xaa ngulaan re yalnzhak, kwaan non doo nak.
Nu nii na kwaane lo gu zee nik tub xaa nakadet gu kwaan re wdizh gaya nak.
Nu nixa nanzot na kwaan kwerp cheen na lo gu, nzo xgab cheen na lo re gu, nu nyakla na ne na lee re gu chul nzho gu nu nali ngwii gu lo Jesucrist.
Yalnaban kub kwaan zaa JesucristNu sbaa mod mkayaa be Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, nal nzhaal tubka reke be xnaz xaa,
kwaanzee nzhaal zo be nye lo xaa, mod tub xan yag kwaan nech doo nzho lox, nu tubka wii be lo xaa modxa mseed be, nu tubka zaa be dixkix lo Dios.
Nu kanap be leeka be, zee nalaat be kade re xaa be kwaan xgab cheen myet kwaan nawlit, nel naleet kwent cheen Jesucrist nzaa re xaa ne, lee xaa nzaa kwent cheen re krens cheen re xey xaa, kwaan nak cheen mbi mal, re mbi kwaan nabeyy lo yizhyo ne.
Nel mod nak Dios nak Jesucrist, xaa mzhin ngok myet,
nu nik tub kwaan nanzho jwalt lo be nel tubka nak be kwaan Jesucrist, nu lee xaa nak Xaa Nabeyy lo rese yalnabeyy kwaan nzho lo yizhyo ne nu kwaan nzho naz leen yiba.
Nu noka nel tubka nak be kwaan Jesucrist, nkano be tub beyy, per nanakta tub beyy kwaan nak choog myet tik yed cho myet, lee beyy ne nak ngut be lo re jwalt cheen be nu naka mod ngut be tubka kwaan Jesucrist,
nel gorna mrubnis be, mod xaa ngubyo kwaan Jesucrist nak be, nu noka mroban be kwaan lee xaa nel mwii be lo yalngezh cheen Dios kwaan mseban xaa.
Nu yilo re gu nak mod tub xaa ngut kwent cheen re kwaan nawent kwaan mle gu nu nanzhot gu beyy cheen re nu, xaa Israel, per nal Dios mzaa stub yalnaban kwaan kub lo re be tubka kwaan Jesucrist, xaa kwaan mchee re jwalt cheen be.
Nu Dios mkiib re jwalt cheen be, kwaan ngaazh ley cheen Ches tich be; nu mlux xaaya gorna mkee xaa Jesucrist lo krus pa ngut xaa.
Nu Dios mle gan lo rese yalnabeyy nu lo rese mbi mal, nu mloo xaa xkyalnto re mbi mal delant lo rese myet, nu mkiib xaa re yalngezh lo re mbi mal gorna mle xaa gan.
Kwaan be re kwaan nak kwaan yibaKwaanzee nalet be xgab kwaan nii stub xaa lo be, lo re kwaan nzhaw be nu lo re kwaan nzho be, o nel nanzhollt be lo Dios mod nle re xaa sawlazh na lo re yalni kad liin, o kad mbee yeen, o kad zhe sab.
Per rese kwaane nak nebse mod tub xbzhin cheen re kwaan wli cheen Jesucrist, re kwaan yaad.
Nu nalaat be kiib re xaa re kwaan nakladiizh kayaa be lo be. Lee re xaa mbezh nkin wii be respet nu gool be lo re mandad cheen Dios. Nu nle xaa mod mlu Dios tub kwaan lo xaa nu nto xaa yalxwa lo re xgab cheen xaa.
Re xaa ba nanlaat nabeyy Jesucrist leen lextoo xaa. Per lee Jesucrist nak mod yek tub xkwerp myet, kwaan nak re be; nu lee xaa nle zee tubka kwerp cheen xaa nak re be, nu zee nkanoya re kwaan nkina, zee kad tub paya chul nkee zhiin, zee chul nzhirooya modxa nak xgab cheen Dios.
Re be ngut tubka kwaan Jesucrist, zee nanzhaalt nabeyyra re kwaan mle re xey be, xaa yilo lo be. Nu kwaanzee, ¿chozhiin mod tub xaa yizhyo ne nzho gu, nel ngwii gu lo re kwaan mbezh xaa?
Kwaan nak kwenta kwaane: “Nanzhaalt gaw lu kwaan ba”. “Nanzhaalt gak nix lextoo lu gaw lu kwaan ba”. “Nixa nanzhaalt gal lu choya”.
Per rese xgab ne nak cheen myet yizhyo, nu leeya lux.
Lee re myet yizhyo ne mbezh lee kwaane nlu mod tub kwaan wen, nu ngozhaw xaa re kwaan nabeyy re xey xaa, nu nle xaa mod tub xaa nadoo, nu nted doo xaa bid kwerp cheen xaa. Per tira nanont kwaan kale xaa, nel nyent mod saaw re kwaane kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen xaa le.
Nu nel tubka mroban be kwaan Jesucrist, nzhaal kwaan be kwaan nak kwaan naz yiba, paro nzob Jesucrist lad li lo Dios, pa nabeyy xaa.
Nu nzhaal le be xgab re kwaan yiba nu naletra be xgab re kwaan yizhyo ne,
¡Jesucrist nak yalnaban cheen be! Nu gorna yaad xaa stub welt, nya be pa nabeyy xaa pa nla xni.
Mod ngok be yilo nu mod nak be nalKwaanzee naletra be re kwaan nak kwaan yizhyo ne:Nalet be re kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen be,nalet be re kwaan beed,nazoblazht be le be re kwaan nzhekla kwerp cheen be,nalet be re xgab nachan kwaan nzho yek be,nu nazoblazht be rese kwaan nzho lo yizhyo kwaan nak mod ngwii xaa lo re maj,nel sbaa nangwiit xaa lo Dios.
Nu rese kwaane nle zee nxaal Dios yalnayii cheen xaa lo re xaa sbaa nle,
modxa mle be yilo leezha mle be mod nle re xaa yizhyo.
Per nal laa be rese kwaane:yalnayii,re xyan kwaan nzho yek be,re wdizh nawent kwaan nii be lo stub naz xaa,nu re wdizh kwaan beed,
nu re yalnkade.Nel mlaa be mod ngok be yilo nu re kwaan nawent kwaan mle be yilo;
nu nal mban be lo stub yalnaban kwaan kub, nu lee yalnaban ne kale kub Dios yizata mbizh, zee nzho mod labeyyra be xaa, zee gak be kwenta lee xaa.
Nu lo yalnaban kub ne, nanontra nen che nak xaa sawlazh na o nanakt xaa, che nzho xaa beyy o nanzhot xaa beyy cheen re nu, che nak xaa xaa zit, che nak xaa tub mos o nanakt xaa tub mos, kwaan non nak Jesucrist, nu chelee xaa nabeyy xaa leen lextoo be.
Dios mleey be zee gak be xaa xaa, nel nkela xaa be nu mle xaa nambey be lo xaa. Kwaanzee liib be lextoo be:zee lesla be ne be wechxinn be,nu gak be nadoo,natot be yalxwa,nakwaant be dil,
nu yela be ne be tub be stub be,nu yenlazh be re kwaan nawent kwaan mle xaa lo be, modxa mchee Xaa Nabeyy re jwalt cheen be.
Nu kwaan mas nonra lo re kwaane nak: Nzhaal kela be wechxinn be, nel lee yalnkela nle zee le be duzna kwaan wen.
Nu nak be mod tubka kwerp cheen Jesucrist, nel nabeyy xaa leen lextoo be, kwaanzee nzhaal kwi wen rese be, nu nzhaal zaa be dixkix lo Dios.
Laa be tubka nabeyy xtizh Jesucrist leen lextoo be, zee kwaan re yalnzhak cheen Dios nzho mod le be zee nye gak lextoo stub be. Nu nzhaal gool be salm nu kant, nel nzhekla be zaa be dixkix lo Dios.
Kwaanzee rese kwaan nle be nu rese kwaan nii be, nzhaal le beya kwaan yalnabeyy cheen Jesús, Xaa Nabeyy be, nu zaa be dixkix lo Dios, xaa nak Xuz re be kwent cheen Jesucrist.
Xomod nzhaal yo re sawlizh beLee re ngwnaa nzhaal gon me xtizh sa me, nel kwaane nak kwaan nzhaal le tub me nkela Xaa Nabeyy.
Lee re xaabyi nzhaal kela xaa sa xaa nu nayiit xaa lo sa xaa.
Lee re xaawin nzhaal gon xaa xtizh xuz xaa nu xtizh xnaa xaa, nel snee nyula Xaa Nabeyy.
Nu lee re xaa nak xuz mad nanzhaalt le xaa rixyan mad, zee nagakt nalest lextoo mad.
Rese xaa nak mos, nzhaal gon xaa xtizh xaa nabeyy lo xaa lo yizhyo ne. Nu tubka nzhaal kee xaa zhiin nu nakeet xaa zhiin nebse leezha kawii xaa nabeyy lo xaa, zee chul zo xaa kwaan lee xaa, nzhaal kee xaa zhiin kwaan dub lextoo xaa, nel nzheb xaa ne xaa Xaa Nabeyy, xaa nzho naz leen yiba.
Kwaanzee rese kwaan le be nzhaal le beya kwaan dub lextoo be, mod tub xaa nkee zhiin lo Xaa Nabeyy nu nalet beya mod tub xaa nkee zhiin lo myet.
Nel nela be, lee Xaa Nabeyy zaa re kwaan chul cheen xaa lo be, nel nkee be zhiin lo Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be.
Per lee xaa kwaan nle kwaan nawent, leeka kwaan nawent kwaan mle xaa yex ka xaa, nel nyent mod le Dios nonra tub xaa ke stub xaa.
Nu lee re xaa nabeyy lo mos nzhaal gak xaa tub xaa nali, nel noka lee xaa nkin zaa kwent lo Xaa Nabeyy, xaa nzob naz yiba.
Nu nayizhat be tubka wdizhno be Dios, tubka wii be lo xaa nu tubka zaa be dixkix lo xaa.
Nu noka naab gu lo Dios zee xal xaa naz zee nzho mod zaa nu kwent cheen Jesucrist kwaan ngulaan yilo, nu kwent cheen kwaane nzhoo na lozhyib.
Nu naab gu lo Dios zee nzho mod klar nii naya, mod nzhaal le naya.
Nu kwaan yalnzhak nii be lo re xaa zer labeyy Xaa Nabeyy, nu leezha nzho moda lo be zaa be kwent ne lo xaa.
Nu leezha wdizh be kwaan tub xaa nzhaal wdizh be tub mod nadoo, per kwaan nii be nzhaal gak mod zed, nu noka nzhaal ne be xomod keb be tub kwaan lo xaa nabdizh tub kwaan lo be.
Dix gwluzhNu lee wech be Tíquico, yiid lo gu zaa kwent cheen na, nu re kwaan kale na. Nkela na xaa, nu lee xaa nali nak nu nkee xaa zhiin lo Xaa Nabeyy.
Nu kwaan lee xaa nxaal na wech be Onésimo, xaa nak tub sawlazh gu. Rop xaa zaa kwent lo gu re kwaan kaded nee.
Lee wech be Aristarco, xaa nzho kwaan na lozhyib nxaal “dix” lo re gu. Nu noka Mark xich Bernabé nxaal “dix” lo re gu, nu mod ngunii na lo gu bkayaa gu Mark kwaan dub lextoo gu chelee xaa yiid xaa yiselach xaa lo gu.
Nu noka nxaal Chuch “dix” lo re gu, xaa noka le Just. Nu nebse rop xaa ne nak xaa sawlazh na, xaa kwaan nkee zhiin kwaan na lo xchiin Xaa Nabeyy nu gro doo nseleyy xaa na.
Noka Epafras, tub xaa lazh gu, nxaal “dix” lo re gu. Lee xaa nak tub xmos Jesucrist nu tubka naab xaa lo Dios zee lee re gu nye nu nali nzo lo Dios, modxa nzhekla Dios.
Nu nzho mod za na kwent, lee Epafras naab doo lo Dios kwent cheen re gu, nu kwent cheen re xaa kwaan nzho yezh Laodicea, nu kwent cheen re xaa kwaan nzho yezh Hierápolis.
Nkela na Luk, xaa nak doktor, nu lee xaa nxaal “dix” lo re gu nu noka Demas nxaal “dix” lo re gu.
Guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo re wech nu lo re bzan, xaa nzho yezh Laodicea. Nu noka guzh gu “dix” cheenta lo Ninfas, nu lo re xaa kwaan nkasa nzhon xtizh Dios garli me.
Nu gorna yilo lab gu yech ne, bxaal guya lo re xaa Jesús, xaa nzho yezh Laodicea, zee noka re xaa laba; nu zee zaa xaa stub yech kwaan mkee na lo xaa lo gu, zee lab guya.
Nu guzh gu kwaane lo Arquipo: “Bkee zhiin kwaan mzaa Xaa Nabeyy lo lu”.
Na nak Pab, nu nkee na “dix” ne lo gu kwaan xletr na kwaan kakee na kwaan mer yaa na. Nu bselazh gu lee na nzhoo lozhyib. Nu nzhekla na luu Dios yalnkela cheen xaa lo re gu.Sbaa gaka.
<font color=teal>Yech yilo kwaan mkee Pab lo re xaa yezh Tesalónica</font>Dix cheen PabDix re gu.Na nak Pab; nu Silban nu Timoteo nzo kwaan na nee. Kakee na yech ne xaal na lo re gu, xaa Jesús, xaa nzho yezh Tesalónica. Dios nak Xuz be, nu Jesucrist nak Xaa Nabeyy be. Nzhekla na luu Dios yalnkela cheen xaa lo gu zee chul kwi rese gu.
Nzaa nu dixkix lo Dios kwent cheen xomod ngwii gu lo DiosLeezha nii nu lo Dios tubka nzaa nu dixkix lo xaa nel nye nzo gu lo xaa.
Nu tubka nselazh nu nzaa nu dixkix lo Dios, xaa nak xuz be, nel tubka ngwii gu lo xaa, nu kwaan dub lextoo gu nkee gu xchiin xaa, nel nkela gu xaa, nu xomod nye nzo gu lo Jesucrist Xaa Nabeyy be, nu tubka nkambaz gu bare xaa.
Kwaanzee wech nu bzan, ne be Dios mleey gu nel nkedoola xaa gu.
Nu leezha mzaa nu kwent wdizh chul lo gu, nanebtse ngunii nuya kwaan wdizh, nel noka mle Mbi Naban kwaan gro lo gu, zee ne gu wli re kwaan nguné nu lo gu. Nu noka ne gu nali mod nzhale mle nu leezha myaad nu lo re gu, nel mle nu zee mkayaa gu re kwaan wen.
Nu lee re gu ngok kwenta nu, nu kwenta Xaa Nabeyy be. Nu nixa mded doo gu bid, lee Mbi Naban mle zee nyakdoola gu mkayaa gu wdizh chul.
Nu snee mlu gu lo re xaa Jesús, xaa nzho re yezh cheen Macedonia nu re yezh cheen Acaya, mlu gu lo xaa nen xomod nzhaal wii xaa lo Jesús.
Kwaanzee re gu mle zee lee wdizh chul cheen Xaa Nabeyy nzhayon zyen doo myet re yezh, nu nanebt re yezh cheen Macedonia nu re yezh cheen Acaya noka stub naz re yezh, sbaa lee re xaa ngune xomod ngwii gu lo Dios nu nankintra zaa nu kwent lo re xaa xomod mkayaa gu xtizh Dios.
Nel rese xaa ba nzaa kwent lo nu xomod wen doo mkayaa gu nu, leezha myaad nu lo gu, nu xomod ta mlaa gu re maj kwaan nambant, kwaan nawlit nak Dios, nu mzelo gu mwii gu lo Dios, xaa mban, xaa wlipa nak Dios, nu mzelo gu mkee gu xchiin xaa.
Noka nzaa re xaa ba kwent xomod nkambaz re gu bare Jesucrist naz yiba, xaa nak Xgann Dios. Dios mseban xaa. Nu nebse lee xaa nzho mod la re be lo yalzi kwaan xaal Dios.
Zhiin kwaan mkee Pab yezh TesalónicaWech nu bzan, nela gu lee zhiin kwaan mkee nu lo gu mrekeya.
Noka nela gu xomod mted re xaa yezh Filipos nu bid, nu xomod mzaa xaaya yenn nu, per nixa mnayii re xaa ngune nu, Dios mlo balor lextoo nu zee mzaa nu kwent wdizh chul cheen xaa lo gu.
Wli doo kwaan mzaa nu kwent lo gu, nu nixa nangut yalnkade lo xgab cheen nu, zee kade nu gu.
Dios mleey nu, nu mzaa xaa zhiin ne le nu, zee zaa nu kwent wdizh chul cheen xaa, kwaanzee nzaa nu kwenta. Nu nankwaant nu nix gak lextoo re myet ne nu, lee nu nkwaan gak nix lextoo Dios ne nu, xaa nlabeyy lextoo rese be.
Noka nela gu nik tub welt nambedizht nu nadoo lo gu zee zaa gu demi lo nu; Dios ne kwaane.
Nu nixa namkwaant nu zee wdizh wen re myet nu, nixa re gu; nu nixa nzho mod ngnaab nu kwaan nkin nu lo gu, nel mer Jesucrist mzaa yalnabeyy lo nu,
per lee nu nadoo doo ngok nu lo re gu mod tub ngwnaa, me nkano madoo.
Tant mkeladoo nu gu, nanzheklat nu zaa nu kwent nebse wdizh chul lo gu, noka nzhekla nu zaa nu leeka nu lo gu, nel tant nkeladoo nu gu.
Rese gu wech nu bzan, selazh gu xomod mkee nu zhiin leezha mzo na lo gu, zee mle nu gan kwaan ndaw nu. Zhe nu yaal mkee nu zhiin zee nangokt nu storb lo re gu, leezha mzaa nu kwent wdizh chul cheen Jesús lo re gu.
Noka nela gu xomod mzaa nu konsej lo gu nu xomod mseleyy nu kad tub gu, modxa nle xaa lo xinn xaa.
Nu noka mseed nu re gu xomod nzhaal le be rese kwaan nel xaa Dios nak be, xaa mleeyla be zee kayaa be paro nabeyy xaa, pa chul cheen xaa.
Kwaanzee tubka nzaa nu dixkix lo Dios, nel leezha mzaa nu kwent wdizh chul lo re gu, nu mkayaa guya mod xtizh Dios nu nambint guya mod xtizh myet. Nu leeya wlipa nak xtizh Dios nu nkeeya zhiin lextoo gu, xaa nzhona.
Wech nu bzan, rese gu ne leezha mrenal leeka re sawlazh gu gu, myela gu leeka mod myela re xaa Jesús, xaa nzho yizhyo Judea, nel leeka re sawlazh nu xaa Israel, mrenal re xaa ba,
nu noka mbit xaa Jesús, Xaa Nabeyy be, modxa mbitaka xaa re xaa mzaa kwent kwaan nzhé Dios lo lee xaa yilo, nu leeka re xaa ne mloo re nu lazh nu, nel nayii doo xaa ne xaa rese xaa nanakt xaa Israel. Tira nanyulat Dios re xaa snee nle,
nel nanlaat xaa zaa nu kwent wdizh chul lo re xaa nanakt xaa Israel, zee noka re xaa le gan yalnaban kwaan tira. Nu snee leeka re xaa ba kazhibra jwalt tich xaa. Kwaanzee nal lee yalnayii cheen Dios kalala tich re xaa ba.
Pab nzhekla ya Tesalónica stub weltWech nu bzan, xep gwluzh leezha pensa mtexonn xaa nu lo re gu, nu nixa nangwiit nu gu per tubka nzelazh nu gu, nu nzhekla doo nu yiid nu lo re gu stub welt.
Zyen doo welt nzhekla na ngal na lo gu, nu rese nu ngu doo yek ngid lo gu, per nanglaat Maxuu ngid nu.
Per kwaan nle nix doo lextoo nu nak re gu. Nel leezha bare Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, to nu yalxwa nel nye nzo gu lo xaa, xaa kwaan nkambaz be.
Wlipa na, re gu nak kwaan nle chul lextoo nu.
Pab mxaal Timoteo lo re xaa yezh Tesalónica<sup>(1-2)</sup> Nu nzhekla doo nu ne nu nen xomod nzho gu, kwaanzee mxaal nu wech Timoteo lo re gu, nixa laa xaa techo nu yezh Atenas. Nu Timoteo nak tub xaa nkee xchiin Dios, nzaa xaa kwent wdizh chul cheen Jesucrist. Kwaanzee mxaal nu xaa, zee le xaa yudar gu zee mas nyera zo gu lo Jesús,
(-)
zee nik tub gu nalaat Dios leezha nzhin re yalzi lo gu. Nel nela gu nzhaal ded re be kwaane.
Nu sbaa né nu lo re gu leezha nzhika nu kwaan re gu, lee re mbizh kwaan ded be bid mzhin gaxla, nu sbaa ngoka mod nela re gu.
Kwaanzee, naxektra na kwaz na nu nzhekla doo na ne na xomod nzhi gu ngwii gu lo Jesús, kwaanzee mxaal na Timoteo, zee nzho mod ne na xomod nzhi gu. Nel mle doo na xgab napa lee Maxuu ngkiil gu zee nglaa gu wii gu lo Dios, zee lee re zhiin kwaan mle na lo gu nalexchiint.
Lee nal mbarela Timoteo nyaad ngwa lo re gu, nu nguné xaa nen xomod tubka ngwii gu lo Jesús nu xomod nkela gu tub gu stub gu. Noka né xaa nen xomod nselazh gu re nu, nu nzhekla doo gu zhaal be stuba, leeka mod nzhekla re nu.
Kwaanzee wech nu bzan, nixa kaded doo nu bid, per chul doo mseleyy gu re nu gorna mbin nu lee re gu tubka ngwii lo Jesús.
Nu gorna mbin nu lee re gu nye nzo ngwii lo Xaa Nabeyy, kwaane nle zee nix doo ngok lextoo nu.
Kwaanzee nyentra wdizh kwaan yé nu nzaa nu dixkix lo Dios kwent cheen gu, nel gu mle nix doo nzhak lextoo nu lo Dios.
Zhe nu yaal kanaab nu lo Dios zee yiid nu lo re gu stuba, zee seedra nu gu, zee nyera zo gu wii gu lo Dios.
Pab nzaa dixkix lo DiosNu nal naab na lo Dios, xaa nak Xuz be nu lo Jesucrist, Xaa Nabeyy be, zee nzho mod yiid nu lo gu stuba.
Noka kanaab nu zee lee Xaa Nabeyy le roora yalnkela cheen gu, zee masra kela gu tub gu stub gu, nu sbaaka kela gu stub naz re xaa, modxa nkela nu gu,
zee snee nyera zo gu lo Dios, zee nambey gak gu lo Xuz be Dios, gorna bare Jesús, Xaa Nabeyy be, kwaan rese xaa nali lo xaa.
Xomod nzhekla Dios yo beKwaanzee nal wech nu bzan, naab nu lo gu nu nabeyy nu lo gu kwaan yalnabeyy cheen Jesús, Xaa Nabeyy be: Ble gu kwaan nyula Dios mod kaleka guya axta nal, modxa mseed nu re gu.
Nel ne wen gu xana re kwaan mnabeyy nu le gu kwaan yalnabeyy cheen Jesús, Xaa Nabeyy be.
Kwaan nzhekla Dios nak zo be nali lo xaa, nu nik tub be nachaalt stub cho nanakt sa be.
Kwaanzee kad tub be nzhaal kanap be xkwerp be zee gaka kwaan nzhul nu nambey lo Dios.
Kwaanzee nalet be mod nle re xaa nanakt xaa Jesús, re xaa nle rese kwaan nzhekla xkwerp.
Kwaanzee nik tub be nanzhaalt le kwaan nawent ne lo wechxinn be, nel Xaa Nabeyy ted re xaa leya bid, modxa ngunéla nuya lo gu yilo.
Kwaanzee loka xaa nanzaat yek gon re kwaan nguné nu, nalet lo myet nanzhont xaa diizh, sinka lo Dios, xaa mzaa Mbi Naban lo re be, nanzhont xaaya.
Nankintra kee nu lo gu xomod nzhaal kela gu tub gu stub gu, nel leeka Dios mseed gu nzhaal kela gu tub gu stub gu.
Nu sbaaka nkela gu rese xaa Jesús, xaa nzho yizhyo Macedonia. Per wech nu bzan, naab doo nu lo gu zee masra ble guya kad mbizh.
Nu modxa mxaal nu lo gu: Nzhaal yo chul gu, nu narept gu paro nakabezht xaa gu, sinka bkee gu zhiin zee le gu gan kwaan gaw gu,
nu snee nik tub kwaan nayojwalt lo gu, zee nankint naab guya lo stub naz xaa, nu sbaa lee re myet wdizh wen re gu.
Xomod bare Jesucrist stubaNu nal wech nu bzan, nzhekla nu ne gu cho kwaan gak kwaan re xaa Jesús, xaa ngutla, zee nagakt nalest lextoo gu modxa nales doo nzhak lextoo re xaa nakwazt kayaa nik tub kwaan gorna yet xaa.
Na nii kwaan nela rese be: Lee Jesús ngut nu mroban stub welt, leeka sbaa seban Dios re xaa ngutla, xaa nak xaa Jesús.
Nu kwaanzee nii nu lo re gu leeka wdizh kwaan mzaa Xaa Nabeyy lo nu; lee re be, xaa mbanaka axta leezha bare Xaa Nabeyy, nayanert be zhin lo Xaa Nabeyy ke re xaa ngutla.
Nel leezha bare Xaa Nabeyy lo yizhyo ne, lee xaa nii nye doo kwaan yalnabeyy cheen xaa, nu noka tub mandad cheen Dios nye doo kozhe, nu noka lee trompet cheen Dios kwezh, zee lee re xaa ngut, xaa mwii lo Jesucrist, roban yilotlaka,
zeera lee re be, xaa mbanaka, lis xaa zhaal kwaan re xaa mroban lo xkaw, nu snee tira zo re be kwaan lee xaa.
Kwaanzee zaa be balor lextoo tub be stub be kwaan re wdizh ne.
Kwaanzee wech nu bzan, lee mbizh o gor kwaan gak re kwaane, nankintra kee naya,
nel ne wen re gu, lee mbizh kwaan bare Xaa Nabeyy zhin mod tub wann, xaa nzhin yaal, gor nyent cho nle xgaba.
Gorna lee re myet yé: “Wen nzho be nik tub kwaan nankint le be xgab”, gorzee ta zhin mbizh ded xaa bid. Kwaane gak mod yalne kwaan nzak tub ngwnaa, me gal xiin, nu nyent mod laa xaa lo kwaane.
Per wech nu bzan, nanzot be lo yalnakaw, zee lee mbizh kwaan bare Xaa Nabeyy zhin lo be mod nzhin tub wann, kwaan nankambazt be.
Per rese be nak xaa nzo zhe nu nzo be lo xni cheen Dios, nanakt be xaa nzo yaal, xaa nzo lo yalnakaw.
Kwaanzee nanzhaalt la mkaal lo be lo kwaane mod lo stub naz xaa, sinka kanap be be, list zo be.
Lee re xaa nzha, yaal nzha xaa; nu re xaa nzho nzoo, yaalka nle xaaya.
